Incandelo 24 — Ngoku Nangonaphakade — Ukulunga Okuhlala Kuhleli Konqulo Lokwenyaniso
“ Unqulo , ukuba luneenyaniso zasezulwini , wanela nje kukulubona ube sowuncoma . ” — UWilliam Cowper , imbongi eliNgesi yenkulungwane ye -⁠ 18
AKUKHO nto lunokunconywa ngayo unqulo lobuxoki .
Luye lwafaka uluntu kwiinkulungwane ezingama - 60 zosizi nenkxwaleko .
Ukuxoka kwalo , ukukhohlisa kwalo , ukuba yingcuka eyambethe ufele lwegusha kwalo , neendlela zalo ezilizothe zilwenze lwalisikizi emehlweni kaThixo nawabantu .
Ekubeni lucezela kude kwiinyaniso zasezulwini , unqulo lobuxoki luyichasile inyaniso nokulunga kwayo .
Kungekudala imikhosi kaThixo etshabalalisayo ngokungacengi solalaphi iza kuluphosa unqulo lobuxoki emhadini wentshabalalo kanaphakade .
Kamsinya emva koko , inxalenye eseleyo yenkqubo kaSathana nayo iya kwehlelwa kwasesifanayo .
Kodwa unqulo lokwenyaniso , kwanabo baluqheliselayo , luya kuhlala luhleli .
Olunjani ngoko uvuyo ekuya kuba lulo ngokubonakaliswa kokulunga kwalo okuhlala kuhleli ukusa kumlinganiselo esingenakuwuthelekelela namhlanje !
Kokuphi Oko Kulunga ?
Zininzi izinto olulunge ngazo unqulo lokwenyaniso .
Nazi ezimbalwa zazo .
Kutheni ungaziniki ixesha lokuhlolisisa iindinyana zeBhayibhile ezicatshuliweyo ezingqina ukuba ezi ngenelo zikanaphakade zisekelwe eBhayibhileni ?
Phakathi kwezinto ezininzi ezihlala zihleli olulunge ngazo unqulo lokwenyaniso kukho ezi :
▪ Lusekelwe kwinyaniso kaThixo ongenakuphazama , ogama lakhe linguYehova , esinokukholosa ngaye ngokupheleleyo . ​ —⁠ INdumiso 83 : ​ 18 ; Isaya 55 : ​ 10 , 11 .
▪ Luvulekele nabani na onentliziyo ethobekileyo , alugcinelwanga iinkcuba - buchopho kuphela . ​ —⁠ Mateyu 11 : ​ 25 ; 1 Korinte 1 : ​ 26 -⁠ 28 .
▪ Alunanto yakwenza nesizwe esithile , imeko engokwasentlalweni enesigxina kwezoqoqosho . ​ —⁠ IZenzo 10 : ​ 34 , 35 ; 17 : ​ 24 -⁠ 27 .
▪ Lunikela ithemba elinesiseko esiqinisekileyo lokuphila kwihlabathi elinoxolo nonqabiseko ekungekho lusizi kulo , ukugula , iinkxwaleko nokufa . ​ —⁠ Isaya 32 : ​ 18 ; ISityhilelo 21 : ​ 3 , 4 .
▪ Lunikela ulwalathiso ngendlela amalungu alo anokuphila ngayo njengabazalwana abanyanisekileyo bazwenibanzi , bemanyene kwimfundiso esisiseko , kwihambo nasemoyeni . ​ —⁠ INdumiso 133 :⁠ 1 ; Yohane 13 :⁠ 35 .
▪ Kumntu wonke ​ —⁠ indoda , ibhinqa nomntwana⁠ — ​ lunikela ithuba lokuba nesabelo ngokukhutheleyo emsebenzini kaThixo , esiba nenjongo ebomini . ​ —⁠ 1 Korinte 15 : ​ 58 ; Hebhere 13 : ​ 15 , 16 .
▪ Lusilumkisa ngeengozi ezifihlakeleyo , lusiyalela indlela esifanele siziphathe ngayo ukuze sizuze iingenelo . ​ —⁠ IMizekeliso 4 : ​ 10 - 13 ; Isaya 48 : ​ 17 , 18 .
Yaye kutheni le nto kunokuthiwa ezi ngenelo zezikanaphakade ?
Kungenxa nje yokuba ziya kuhlala zikho logama nje lusekho unqulo lokwenyaniso ​ —⁠ ngonaphakade .
Ukuvala Umsantsa
Singatsho ukuthi ukufa kulolunye lwezona ntshaba zinkulu zenyaniso , ekubeni abantu ngokufuthi bengcwatywa kunye nenkcazelo ekungekho bantu abangabanye abayaziyo .
Iinkcazelo ezichanileyo zeziganeko zakutshanje ngokwentelekiso ​ —⁠ ngokomzekelo , ukugwintwa komongameli - mbuso waseUnited States uJ .
F .
Kennedy ngowe - 1963⁠ — ​ zisengumbandela ekuphikiswana ngawo .
Zibonisa ntoni izibakala ?
Ngubani kanye kanye owaziyo ?
Abaninzi abasenokwazi sele belele kobandayo .
Yaye ukuba oku kuyinyaniso ngesiganeko esenzeke kwiminyaka nje engama - 26 edluleyo , kuthekani ngeziganeko ezenzeka kumakhulukhulu okanye kwanakumawakawaka eminyaka eyadlulayo ?
Ukongezelela , ababhali - mbali nabo bangabantu , banolwazi olulinganiselweyo yaye basebenza phantsi kwemiqobo yokungafezeki kobuqu ibe kusengenzeka ukuba bavukwe likhethe .
Kungenxa yeso sizathu le nto umntu onengqondo ephangaleleyo esenza kakuhle ngokuphepha ukumisela umthetho - siseko ngezinto angenagunya kuzo , ezinjengengxelo ephefumlelwe nguThixo .
Ukubhala ngembali yonqulo kuvelisa iingxaki ezifanayo , ekubeni ngokufuthi abasemagunyeni bengavumelani nezibakala .
Kungcelele oluthi “ Ikamva Lonqulo Ngenxa Yoko Kwenzeke Kulo Kwixa Elidluleyo , ” uVukani !
uye wazama ukunikela izibakala ezinobungqina obubambekayo ngokusuka kwiincwadi ezithile , kodwa kumele kuvunywe ukuba okwangoku kukho izinto ezithile esingazaziyo nje kwaphela .
Ngokomzekelo , ngaba amaqela awayezibanga engamaKristu awayekho ebudeni nasemva kwamaXesha Obumnyama anamathela ngokwenene ukusa kuwuphi umkhamo kubuKristu bokwenyaniso ?
Ngokubhekisele kula maqela , unjingalwazi wembali yecawa uA .
M .
Renwick uthi : “ Kusafuneka kwenziwe uphengululo olukhulu olungokwembali ukuze kufunyanwe eyona ngxelo ichanileyo nendlela loo ntlaninge yamaqumrhu eyayilugqala ngayo unqulo . ”
Ngokutsho kwalo kaRenwick , “ kwixesha elidlulileyo ababhali - mbali bebexhomekeke kakhulu kwiingxelo zeentshaba zamaqela aye ajibilika kuzo ukuze baphande ngemfundiso yawo esisiseko nangemilinganiselo yokuziphatha . ”
Kambe ke , kwanokuxhomekeka kakhulu kwiingxelo zabahlobo babo kwakusenokuphumela kwingcamango etenxileyo .
Ngoko kwanasemva kophengululo olukhulu olungokwembali , ngokunokwenzeka kusaya kubakho imibuzo emininzi eya kuhlala ingaphendulwanga .
Kuthekani ngeBhayibhile ?
Njengencwadi ephefumlelwe nguThixo equlethe imbali yonqulo , inyanisile kuyo yonke into eyithethayo .
Kodwa ithetha okuncinane kakhulu ngeendidi ezahlukeneyo zonqulo lobuxoki ezakha zakho .
Kuyaqondakala ukuba imele ibe injalo , ekubeni yayilungiselelwe ukusebenza njengencwadi yesikhokelo yonqulo lokwenyaniso , kungekhona olobuxoki .
Kwanangokubhekisele kunqulo lokwenyaniso , iBhayibhile ayisixeleli yonke into .
Isinika inkcazelo eyaneleyo yokufanisa unqulo lokwenyaniso ngokunempumelelo , kodwa ngamathuba athile iyazishiya iinkcukacha .
Ngoxa ukwazi ezi nkcukacha kusenokubangela imivuyo yaye kukokomdla , okwangoku azibalulekanga .
Kwakhona , kukho amaxesha eziganeko iBhayibhile engathethiyo ngawo .
Ngokomzekelo , ayithethi nto ngoko kwenzekayo ebudeni bethuba elingaphezu kwama - 400 eminyaka eliphakathi kokugqitywa kweZibhalo zesiHebhere , ezibizwa ngokuqhelekileyo njengeTestamente Endala , nokufika kukaYesu .
Ibe ukususela ekugqityweni kweBhayibhile , sele kudlule iminyaka ephantse ibe li - 1 900 .
Ngoko kangangeenkulungwane ezimalunga ne - 18 , asikhange sibe nangxelo ziphefumlelweyo ngobuKristu .
Yile nto ke kanye ebangele ukuthandabuzeka ngabathile abazibanga bengamaKristu , njengoko wakhe watsho umbhali uRenwick .
Sekunjalo , kuyabonakala ukuba noko bebekho abantu abathile ukuhla ukutyhubela iinkulungwane ababebambelele kubuKristu bokuqala .
Noko ke , kusekho imibuzo engekaphendulwa ephathelele iintshukumisa nokunyaniseka ekusenokwenzeka ukuba babenako abantu abathile bamhlamnene .
Kuthekani ngezinye zeenkokeli zenkqubo yoHlaziyo ?
Xa kuthethwa ngalo mbandela kuthekani ngamadoda anjengoConfucius noMuhammad ?
Nangona iinkqubo zonqulo lwanamhlanje zinokuhlolisiswa ngokuchanileyo ngesizinzi seziqhamo zalo , ngokufuthi oko akunakwenziwa kubantu ngabanye ​ —⁠ ngokukodwa ukuba kudala bafayo .
Noko ke , ukuba kwihlabathi elitsha likaThixo , kunokuba kukuthanda koMdali ukuba kuphinde kubhalwe iincwadi zembali ​ —⁠ kuquka nezo zembali yonqulo⁠ — ​ oko kunokwenzeka .
Oku kungenxa yenye inkalo yokulunga konqulo lokwenyaniso ​ —⁠ isiqinisekiso sokuba abafi baza kuvuswa . ​ —⁠ Yohane 5 : ​ 28 , 29 ; IZenzo 24 :⁠ 15 .
Khawufan ’ ucinge nje ngovuyo esiya kuba nalo ngokufumana iimpendulo ezichanileyo kwimibuzo yethu ngokuthetha nabantu abavusiweyo abazenza ngokoqobo izinto esiye safunda ngazo kwiincwadi zembali .
Khawuthelekelele xa sele ukwazi ukufakela iinkcukacha ezishiyiweyo , njengegama likakumkani waseYiputa owafa kuLwandle Olubomvu nowathwaxwa ngezibetho ezehlela elo lizwe .
Ukuba ngaminazana ithile kuya kuze kufuneke kubhalwe ingxelo enjalo , iya kubhalelwa ukuzukisa nokuthethelela ngonaphakade umseki wonqulo lokwenyaniso , uYehova uThixo .
Akukho mathandabuzo mayela noku .
Phofu ke , umbuzo osaseleyo ngulo : Ngaba uya kuba lapho ukuze uyifunde ?
Ukuncoma Akwanele
Ukulunga okuhlala kuhleli konqulo lokwenyaniso akusoloko kulula ukukubona njengoko amazwi kaCowper acatshulwe kwingabula zigcawu yeli nqaku kubonakala ngathi abonisa njalo .
Ngoko ke , inkupho yokuqala yeZion’s Watch Tower and Herald of Christ’s Presence yanikela la magqabaza kwiminyaka eli - 110 eyadlulayo : “ Inyaniso , njengentyatyambo encinane ebukekayo ekhula entlango , ingqongwe yaye phantse ibe iminxwe lukhula oluninzi lokungendawo .
Ukuze uyifumane ufanele uhlale uwavulile amehlo akho ukhangela .
Ukuze ububone ubuhle bayo ufanele ulususe ukhula lokungendawo nemithana enameva engabantu abaneentamo ezilukhuni ngakwimicimbi yonqulo .
Ukuze uyifumane umele uzithobe . ”
Siyathemba ukuba ungcelele oluthi “ Ikamva Lonqulo Ngenxa Yoko Kwenzeke Kulo Kwixa Elidluleyo ” luye lwabanceda abafundi bamaphephancwadi ethu ‘ ukuba balususe ukhula lokungendawo nemithana enameva engabantu abaneentamo ezilukhuni ngakwimicimbi yonqulo ’ ukuze bakuqonde ngokupheleleyo nangakumbi ukulunga okuhlala kuhleli konqulo lokwenyaniso .
Kodwa ukuqonda akwanele .
Asikuko nokuba sihlab ’ emxholweni isaci samaTshayina esithi : “ Imfundiso engena ezindlebeni kodwa ingangeni entliziyweni ifana nokuphupha usitya isidlo sasemini . ”
Ukuze singenelwe ngokobuqu kwizinto olulunge ngazo unqulo lokwenyaniso ​ —⁠ singaphuphi nje ngazo⁠ — ​ kubalulekile ukuba oko sikufundayo kufikelele intliziyo yethu , kungekuphela nje iindlebe zethu .
Funda ngocoselelo ibhokisi enomxholo othi “ Ukufanisa Unqulo Lwakho Njengolwenyaniso Okanye Lobuxoki . ”
Yandula ke uzibuze oku : ‘ Ngaba ngoku ndiyavuma ukuba ngokubhekisele kubukhosi behlabathi bonqulo lobuxoki , umfo kaVoltaire wayechan ’ ucwethe xa walubiza unqulo ngokuthi “ lutshaba loluntu ” ?
Ngaba ukuvandlakanya le mbali yonqulo kundincedile ekufaniseni unqulo lokwenyaniso , ibe ngaba ndiyazi ukuba lunokufumaneka phi kweli xesha sele lixhatshwe yinja kwimicimbi yabantu ?
Ukuba kunjalo , ngaba ndifuna ukuba njengomntu ochazwe ngumbhali wezincoko waseFransi uJoseph Joubert wenkulungwane ye - 18 , “ ofumana kulo uvuyo lwakhe nomsebenzi wakhe ” ? ’
Kwanga bonke abo baphendula ngokuthi ewe kule mibuzo ingentla bangaqhubeka bengenelwa ngokufunda uVukani !
neempapasho ezingamaqabane akhe .
Siyakumema ukuba ulandele icebiso lobulumko elinikelwe yiZion’s Watch Tower ekhankanywe ngasentla : “ Musa ukwaneliseka yintyatyambo enye yenyaniso .
Ukuba leyo inye ibiyanele ngezingekho ezinye .
Yithi gqolo uqokelela , ufuna ezingakumbi . ”
Ewe , yithi gqolo uqokelela , zingisa ekufuneni ​ —⁠ funa iingenelo ezingakumbi zonqulo lokwenyaniso !
[ Ibhokisi ekwiphepha 26 ]
Ukufanisa Unqulo Lwakho Njengolwenyaniso Okanye Lobuxoki
▪ Unqulo lokwenyaniso luphembelela abanquli balo ukuba babe nentambo engaqhawukiyo yothando nomanyano oloyisa imiqobo yemida yobuhlanga .
Unqulo lobuxoki aluphembeleli uthando olunjalo .
Kunoko , ngokuxelisa uKayin , amarhamente alo aphuma iphulo ukuya kubulalana kwiimfazwe zezizwe ngezizwe . ​ —⁠ 1 Yohane 3 : ​ 10 -⁠ 12 .
▪ Unqulo lokwenyaniso alugxuphuleki kwiipolitiki zabantu yaye lukhangele kuMdali ukuba acombulule iingxaki zehlabathi ngorhulumente woBukumkani bakhe .
Unqulo lobuxoki lulandela umzekelo kaNimrodi owakha iNqaba yaseBhabheli .
Luzifaka ngentloko kwezobupolitika , lukholosa ngoothixo bezobupolitika eligxuphuleka kwimicimbi yabo , yaye ngaloo ndlela luzakhela isiseko sentshabalalo yalo . ​ —⁠ Daniyeli 2 : ​ 44 ; Yohane 18 : ​ 36 ; Yakobi 1 :⁠ 27 .
▪ Unqulo lokwenyaniso lumgqala uYehova njengoThixo wenyaniso , ongokuphela konokusihlangula kwingcinezelo .
Unqulo lobuxoki , njengolo lwaluqheliselwa kwiYiputa nakwiGrisi yamandulo , lumisela intlaninge yoonomgogwana boothixo basentsomini abangafanelekanga nje xa bebonke . ​ —⁠ Isaya 42 :⁠ 5 ; 1 Korinte 8 : ​ 5 , 6 .
▪ Unqulo lokwenyaniso luthembisa ubomi obungunaphakade bolonwabo emhlabeni .
Unqulo lobuxoki ​ —⁠ ngokomzekelo , ubuBhuda⁠ — ​ lubujonga ubomi basemhlabeni njengento enganqwenelekiyo nesiza kuthi sikhululeke kuyo kubomi basemva kokufa olungaqinisekanga ngabo . ​ —⁠ INdumiso 37 : ​ 29 ; ISityhilelo 21 : ​ 3 , 4 .
▪ Unqulo lokwenyaniso , ngencwadi yalo engcwele , iBhayibhile lwenza abantu babe nokholo olomeleleyo ; lubanika ithemba eliqinisekileyo luze lubashukumisele kwizenzo zothando lokwenene ngoThixo nommelwane .
Unqulo lobuxoki , phezu kwazo nje iincwadi ezingcwele olunazo , ubukhulu becala alunamsebenzi kangako nokwenza ezi zinto . ​ —⁠ 1 Yohane 5 : ​ 3 , 4 .
▪ Unqulo lokwenyaniso luphawulwa ngabaveleli abathobekileyo .
Unqulo lobuxoki luphawulwa ngeenkokeli ezizigwagwisayo , ezingoozwilakhe , ezikulungeleyo ukugqwetha inyaniso nezifuna ukuba zizifumanele okuthile kwezobupolitika okanye kwimicimbi yehlabathi . ​ —⁠ IZenzo 20 : ​ 28 , 29 ; 1 Petros 5 : ​ 2 , 3 .
▪ Unqulo lokwenyaniso , oluyindlela yokuzithoba ngokufanelekileyo kuThixo , lusebenzisa ikrele lokomoya , kungekhona elokoqobo .
Kwelinye icala , unqulo lobuxoki luyalalanisa kwimfundiso esisiseko yenyaniso , lusaphula ingqibelelo kwizinto ezifuna ubundilele bobuKristu , yaye luxhalabele ngakumbi izilangazelelo zabantu kunezikaThixo . ​ —⁠ 2 Korinte 10 : ​ 3 -⁠ 5 .
▪ Unqulo lokwenyaniso lushukumisa iintliziyo zabangakholwayo ukuze banqule uThixo wokwenyaniso .
Unqulo lobuxoki lufaka igxalaba kwimekobume yokuthandatyuzwa kweemfundiso ezisisiseko zonqulo , yokuziqulunqela iingcamango zobuqu ngemithetho - siseko yonqulo , yokulandela ingqiqo , neyokuthi phithi zizinto zehlabathi . ​ —⁠ Luka 1 : ​ 17 ; 1 Korinte 14 : ​ 24 , 25 .
▪ Unqulo lokwenyaniso , njengoko luqheliselwa ngamaNgqina kaYehova , luyachuma ngokomoya kunanini na ngaphambili .
Unqulo lobuxoki , lunkone ligazi , luthwaxwa kukungondleki ngokomoya nakukuhla kwenani labantu abaluxhasayo . ​ —⁠ Isaya 65 : ​ 13 , 14 .
Liyintoni ke ikamva lonqulo ngenxa yoko kwenzeke kulo kwixa elidluleyo ?
Unqulo lobuxoki alunakamva .
Phuma kulo !
Phethukela kunqulo lokwenyaniso .
Luya kuhlala lukho ngonaphakade .
Imbono YeBhayibhile
Ngaba Ukho Ngokwenene UMtyholi ?
XA WAWUNGUMNTWANA , ngaba wawuboyika ubumnyama ?
Mhlawumbi wawucinga ngesigebenga esincathame phantsi kwefestile yakho , silindele ukukuxhiphula kubazali bakho .
Ngoku njengomntu okhulileyo , onako ukufunda inkcazelo eyinyaniso nokucinga ngokusengqiqweni ngakumbi , uloyiko lwakho lobuntwana lubonakala luyinto ehlekisayo .
Bambi abahlalutyi bathi : “ Ngoko , kutheni singahlabeli mgama nje size simgqale uMtyholi ekuluhlu olufanayo ​ —⁠ engasenguye owokwenene ngaphezu kokuba esisigebenga esithelekelelwa ngumntwana ? ”
Ngaba akakho uMtyholi ongowokwenene ?
Oko koko kanye enye incwadana yonqulo ikuqinisekisayo isithi : “ IBhayibhile ayithethi nento le ngesigebenga esikhohlakeleyo esinjalo ” ibe , “ Kwigama elithi uMtyholi nelithi uSathana . . . sinengcamango yesono nobungendawo obuzuzw ’ ilifa kwimveli yobuntu . ”
Okanye kunjengokuba umfundisi - ntsapho weSikolo Secawa eUnited States wakubeka ngale ndlela oku : “ Okuphela kwabatyholi abakhoyo ngabantu . ”
Ngaba oku kubonakala kulula gqitha ​ —⁠ mhlawumbi kulula ngokugqithiseleyo ?
Ukucacisa Indlela Yomntu Yokuziphatha
Ukuba thina bantu singabakuphela kwabatyholi abakhoyo , ngoko ke kutheni phantse sonke sibonakalisa inkxalabo ngempilontle yeentsapho zethu ?
Ngokomzekelo , njengabantu ngabanye inkoliso yabantu ilungiselela iintsapho zayo ukudla ; abathi ngabom bazigalelele ityhefu , ibe bayaziphepha iingozi ezisongela ubomi babo .
Akukho nto inobusathana kuloo nto !
Sekunjalo , xa aba bantu banye besenza izinto njengezizwe , nto ithile ithintela imbono yabo ngempilontle abayixhalabele bonke .
Njengezizwe , bavumela izixa ezikhulu zokutya kubole kunokuba bondle abantu abakumazwe abo abalambayo .
Bangcolisa imekobume yomhlaba .
Bayazixhobisa ukuze batshabalalisane ​ —⁠ kwimfazwe yenyukliya .
Onjani wona ummangaliso , isimo sengqondo sokuzitshabalalisa !
Yintoni ephembelela ukumfameka okunje ekuziphatheni koluntu ?
Ngaba sisimo sengqondo sehlokondiba labantu ?
Ngaba ligcudwana nje leenkokeli ezingaqiqiyo ?
Ngokuqinisekileyo kukho okungaphezu koko okubandakanyekileyo .
YiBhayibhile kuphela emchazayo lowo ‘ umfamekise ingqiqo yeli phakade ’ elilihlabathi liphela elingakholwayo .
Ngubani lowo ?
‘ Ngulowo kuthiwa nguMtyholi , uSathana ke , lowo ulilahlekisayo elimiweyo liphela . ’
Ulawula uluntu olulungelelanisiweyo ngokuphumelela kangangokuba iBhayibhile imbiza ngokuba ‘ nguthixo ’ wale nkqubo yeli hlabathi . ​ —⁠ 2 Korinte 4 :⁠ 4 ; ISityhilelo 12 :⁠ 9 .
Lo ‘ thixo ’ akalozim nje elizifihla ngaphantsi kwefestile yakho .
Kodwa uliqhawe lezobupolitika elinamandla , isidalwa sokomoya esingabonakaliyo , esathi , sikatyile kwilinge laso lokufuna ukunqulwa nguYesu samthembisa ukumnika zonke izikumkani zehlabathi .
Kubonakala ukuba , uSathana wayekhe walinikezela elo gunya kwabanye ngaphambi kukaYesu Kristu , kuba incwadi yeBhayibhile kaDaniyeli ityhila ukuba njengamabamba , izithunywa zezulu ezinemvukelo zathi zamkela igunya phezu kobukhosi behlabathi ​ —⁠ ezazibizwa ngokusesikweni ngokuba ‘ ngumthetheli wamaPersi , ’ ‘ nomthetheli wakwaYavan . ’ ​ —⁠ Daniyeli 10 : ​ 20 , 21 .
Ngaloo ndlela uSathana uye wayila intlangano enkulu ​ —⁠ kokubini ‘ njengomphathi wehlabathi [ elibonakalayo ] ’ ‘ nanjengomphathi weedemon [ ezingabonakaliyo ] . ’
Le ngqiqo yokuba , uMtyholi ukhokela intlangano yehlabathi liphela , icacisa okuninzi .
Isizathu Sokuba Abe Ukhokela Iintlangano
Kanye njengokuba ingqwayingqwayi yeqela lezaphuli - mthetho ezilungelelanisiweyo isenokuvelela imisebenzi emininzi engekho mthethweni ​ —⁠ iziyobisi , ubunongogo , ubusela , ukungcakaza , ukurhweba ngokungekho mthethweni , njalo njalo⁠ — ​ ngaphandle kokuzibonakalisa yena ubuqu kubo bonke abaphantsi kwakhe , uSathana ngoko usebenzisa intlangano ethile ukulawula abantu abaninzi ngakumbi kunokuba ebeya kwenjenjalo ngokwakhe eyedwa .
Ukwenza njani oku ?
Ngaphandle kokubandezela abantu ngabanye , yena needemon baziphatha izihlwele zabantu ngokungathi yimihlambi yeenkomo .
Akukho mfuneko yokwalathisa ngamnye ngokobuqu .
Kulula nje ukujika inkokeli yomhlambi ibe inkoliso iya kulandela .
Wandula ke anikele ingqalelo kwabaphambukayo .
Ewe , uMtyholi ungowokwenene ngokupheleleyo , kodwa ukufaniswa kwakhe kokwenyaniso akunanto yakwenza kangako nenkohliso esiyibona kwimifanekiso ehlekisayo okanye kwiingcamango ezimfiliba zabefundisi bezakwalizwi .
Ngaba zimfiliba ?
Ewe , kunjengokuba incwadi ethi Satan , A Portrait iphawula isithi : “ Ukukholelwa kuSathana kube yinto engacacanga ” kwinkulungwane ye - 19 , ibe abefundisi bezakwalizwi “ baye balinga ukucacisa uSathana njengento ethile kunokuba abe sisidalwa esiphilayo sokomoya . ”
Ngubani Oxela Inyaniso EngoMtyholi ?
Ukukuthandabuza kweenkonzo zanamhlanje oko iBhayibhile ikutshoyo ngoMtyholi kufaka isandla kwibutho elikholelwa kwizinto ezibonakalayo eliye alaqiniseka ngoThixo ngokwakhe .
URuth Ansher kwincwadi yakhe ethi The Reality of the Devil , uthi “ Namhlanje , uMtyholi uye wathi shwaka ibe . . . uThixo ngokwakhe uye walala emqokozweni . ”
Ngokuthandabuza imbono yeBhayibhile , “ iingcaphephe ” zanamhlanje zonqulo ziye azayigqala inyaniso ekhanyisa oko kwenzeke kwixesha elidlulileyo .
Kunjengokuba umbhali wemidlalo waseRoma uEugène Ionesco wavuma kwiphephandaba laseJamani esithi : “ Imbali ibiya kuba yengenakuqondwa ukuba besiya kuyikhuphela ngaphandle ingcamango yeedemon . ” ​ —⁠ Welt am Sonntag , kaSeptemba 2 , 1979 .
Ngaba kukho nabani na onenkalipho yokuphakamisa inyaniso engendima kaMtyholi kumanqam anamhlanje ehlabathi ?
Ngokucacileyo , ukho !
Qwalasela “ Isibhengezo sokumela uYehova nxamnye noSathana ” esamkelwa ngamxhelo - mnye kwindibano yowe - 1928 .
