Umbhaleli kaVukani !
waseItali unikela ingxelo yokuba “ isiko lokutshata nokufudukela kwikhaya labazali bomtshakazi okanye abomyeni liye labangela iingxaki kwiintsapho ezininzi , ibe kumaxesha amaninzi umfazi oselula utsala nzima ngokufuthi ngenxa yesimo sengqondo sikaninazala sokuba ngugqada - mbekweni nokuba ngogunyazisayo . ”
