Ofanele Ukwazi Ngezithunywa Zezulu
“ Abaphengululi bezonqulo abamalunga nama - 3 000 kangangeentsuku ezine babehlanganisene eNew York kwiveki ephelileyo ukuze baphulaphule iingxelo ezingaphezu kwama - 500 ezingemibandela esusela kwindima yoburharha kwiintshumayelo ukusa kwimbaluleka yenkqubo yonqulo kumaPentekoste .
Akukho nabani na owakhankanya izithunywa zezulu . ” ​ —⁠ iDaily News , kaDisemba 26 , 1982 .
NAMHLANJE , kwiminyaka esibhozo kamva , abefundisi abakathethi nto ngezithunywa zezulu .
Ngoba ?
Ngaba mhlawumbi aba bathunywa basezulwini bagqalwa nje njengenxalenye yentsomi yamandulo ?
Okanye ngaba bakho ngokwenene ?
Ukuba kunjalo , yintoni omele uyazi ngabo ?
Ngaba Zikho ?
Izithunywa zezulu ‘ azingomandla ’ nje kuphela okanye “ iintshukumo zendalo iphela , ” njengoko ezinye izithandi zobulumko zisitsho .
Zikho ngokwenene ngokokude zikhankanywe izihlandlo ezingamakhulukhulu eLizwini likaThixo , iBhayibhile .
Kwiilwimi zeBhayibhile zantlandlolo , amagama aguqulelwe ngokuthi “ izithunywa zezulu ” ( mal·ʼakhʹ , ngesiHebhere ; agʹge·los , ngesiGrike ) ngokoqobo athetha “ uthile ohambisa umyalezo ” okanye ngokulula “ umthunywa . ”
La magama abonakala phantse izihlandlo ezingama - 400 kwiBhayibhile iphela , maxa wambi ebhekisela kubantu , kodwa ngokuqhelekileyo kubathunywa abangumoya .
Isithunywa sezulu esabonakala kumfazi kaManowa owayeludlolo simxelela ngokukhawulwa konyana wakhe , uSamson , sabonakala ngokwenene kuye .
Kwaba njalo nangezithunywa zezulu ezithathu ezabonakala kuAbraham nomfazi wakhe uSara , nezinye ezibini ezakhupha uLote , nesinye esahlala phantsi komthi omkhulu saza sathetha noGidiyon .
Ngexesha lokuzalwa kukaYesu , ngequbuliso kwavela isithunywa sezulu kwiqela labalusi siphakathi kokukhanya okuqaqambileyo , nokubengezelayo . ​ —⁠ Luka 2 : ​ 8 , 9 .
Ezo zithunywa zezulu zazingabantu bokwenene .
Zazingeyongqikelelo okanye amandla angengowamntu .
Zazalisekisa injongo ezazimele ziyizalisekise njengabathunywa abavela kuThixo , yaye ezo ngxelo ziye ngokufanelekileyo zabhalwa eBhayibhileni ukwenzela ingenelo yethu namhlanje .
Ngaloo ndlela , iBhayibhile ityhila iinkcukacha ezibalulekileyo omele uzazi mayela nezithunywa zezulu , ezithi ezinye zazo zingqubane neengcamango ezingokwesithethe .
Zinjani Ngenkangeleko ?
Mhlawumbi usenokuba nombono wezithunywa zezulu zinjengabafazi abahle okanye njengezibothobothwana , zezidalwa ezinamaphiko ezifana nomntwana , zitsho ngoncumo oluhle zivethe ezimhlophe , zibetha iihadi ezincinane , yaye zindanda emoyeni .
Ukuba kunjalo , ufanele wazi ukuba lo ngumbono ophosakeleyo ovela kwiingcamango zabahedeni , ezinjengeentsomi zamaGrike .
Okanye ezo ngcamango zamkelwa emva kokuba kugqityiwe ukubhalwa kweBhayibhile .
Kwimibono yeBhayibhile efuziselayo , izidalwa zomoya ezinjengeeserafi , neekerubhi zinamaphiko . ​ —⁠ Isaya 6 : 2 ; Hezekile 10 : 5 ; ISityhilelo 14 :⁠ 6 .
ILizwi likaThixo lizichaza izithunywa zezulu njengoomoya abanamandla kakhulu , yaye umoya awubonakali .
‘ Yayisisithunywa sikaYehova ’ esathi ngobusuku obunye sabulala ama - Asiriya ali - 185 000 kwikampu yotshaba lwamaSirayeli !
Xa izithunywa zezulu zathi zazibonakalisa kubantu zazisoloko zivela zingamadoda anxibe ngokupheleleyo , azizange zivele zinjengabafazi okanye abantwana zingazange zibe kwimo engaphantsi kweyomntu .
Zazivela phi ezi zidalwa zomoya zinamandla ?
IBhayibhile ithi “ zadalelwa kuye [ uYesu ] zonke izinto , ezisemazulwini nezisemhlabeni , ezinokubonwa nezingenakubonwa . ”
Ngalo Nyana ulizibulo , uYehova uThixo akanelanga nje ukudala izithunywa zezulu kudala ngaphambi komntu kodwa wakwazenza zazizinto eziphilayo ezingaphezulu kunomntu . ​ —⁠ Yobhi 38 : ​ 4 , 7 ; 2 Petros 2 :⁠ 11 .
Ngaba Zinazo Iimpawu Zobuntu ?
Njengabantu , izithunywa zezulu zineemvakalelo .
Emva kokubona ukudalwa komhlaba , sixelelwa ukuba izithunywa zezulu ‘ zamemelela , ziduma . ’
IBhayibhile ikwasityhilela ukuba ‘ kubakho uvuyo emehlweni ezithunywa zikaThixo ngomoni omnye oguqukayo . ’
Ngokuqinisekileyo , akukho “ mandla ” angengowamntu anokuba nolu vuyo lukhulu luchazwe kwezo ndinyana .
Nezithunywa zezulu zinemilinganiselo .
Izibakala ezithile ezingoKristu nekamva zatyhilwa kubaprofeti abangabantu kungekhona kwizithunywa zezulu .
ILizwi likaThixo lisixelela ukuba ‘ ezi zizinto izithunywa zezulu ezinqwenelayo ukuqondela kuzo . ’
Mayela nomhla ochanileyo uThixo awumisileyo wokuza kweNkosi , uYesu wathi : “ Kodwa akukho bani uwaziyo loo mhla nelo lixa ; azazi nezithunywa zamazulu , nguBawo yedwa . ” ​ —⁠ Mateyu 24 :⁠ 36 .
Ngoko , kwakhona , eBhayibhileni kubonakala amagama ezithunywa zezulu ezibini , uMikayeli noGabriyeli .
Ngaba oku akongezeleli kubungqina bokuba zingabantu ngabanye abahlukeneyo ?
Njengabantu ngabanye , azizange zilungelelaniswe , njengekhompyutha okanye irobhoti , ukwenza izinto ngendlela ethile .
Kunoko , izithunywa zezulu ziphiwe amandla okuqiqa yaye zinenkululeko yokuzenzela izigqibo zobuqu ngokuziphatha .
Ngaloo ndlela , njengezithunywa ezinenkululeko yokukhetha indlela yokuziphatha , izithunywa zezulu ezithile zakhetha ukumvukela uThixo zaza zaba nguSathana needemon zakhe . ​ —⁠ Genesis 6 : ​ 1 -⁠ 4 ; Yuda 6 ; ISityhilelo 12 : ​ 7 - 9 .
Ngaba Zifanele Zinqulwe ?
Nangona sisenokubuqonda njengobuyinyaniso ubukho bezithunywa zezulu , kungekhona intsomi , simele sikuphephe ukugabadela .
Zimbi iintlangano zonqulo ziye zazibalaselisa ngokungafanelekanga izithunywa zezulu , nangona ukunqulwa kwezithunywa zezulu kugwetywa yiBhayibhile .
Icawa yamaKatolika iye yamguqulela uMikayeli noGabriyeli ekubeni zizinto zokunqulwa .
Yaye kwiicawa zobuOthodoki zaseMpuma , izithunywa zezulu zibaluleke kakhulu kwilitani ( umthandazo wezicelo owenziwa ngumfundisi baze abantu bamane betshintshana ukuphendula ) .
Okunjani kona ukungqubana nesilumkiso esanikelwa sisithunywa sikaYehova xa umpostile uYohane wawa ezinyaweni zaso , sathi : “ Lumka , ungenjenjalo ; ndingumkhonzi kunye nawe . ” ​ —⁠ ISityhilelo 19 :⁠ 10 .
Kutheni le nto kukho ukudideka okungaka mayela nezithunywa zezulu ?
USathana , ozimilisa “ okwesithunywa sokukhanya , ” ‘ uzimfamekisile iingqiqo zabangakholwayo . ’
Ngaloo ndlela , bekungayi kuba sengqiqweni na ukulindela ukuba abaninzi namhlanje babe bebeya kubambelela kwezabo iimbono mayela nobukho nobunjani bezithunywa zezulu kunokwamkela oko iLizwi likaThixo likutshoyo ?
Ewe , nangona abefundisi namhlanje besenokungathethi nto ngezithunywa zezulu , uThixo uyasiqinisekisa ngengxelo yeBhayibhile ukuba zikho ngokwenene yaye zinikela inkonzo ebekekileyo njengabathunywa bakaYehova . ​ —⁠ Hebhere 1 : ​ 7 , 14 ; 6 :⁠ 18 .
