Ngaba Ndifanele Ndibhaptizwe ?
USUSANA owayeneminyaka elishumi elinesithathu ubudala wayesele eza kubulawa sisifo somhlaza ngethuba laxa wayesiya okwesihlandlo sokugqibela kwindibano yamaNgqina kaYehova .
Wayengazi ukuba wayeza kufa kungaphelanga neentsuku ezilishumi emva koko .
Noko ke , kwanesifo somhlaza ngokwaso sasingenakumthintela ekuzalisekiseni umnqweno wakhe awayewuxabise ngokonakona : ukubhaptizwa njengeNgqina likaYehova elizahluleleyo nelingumfundi kaYesu Kristu .
USusana wayengomnye wamawaka abantu abaselula phakathi kwamaNgqina kaYehova kwiminyaka yakutshanje abaye balivuyela ilungelo lokubhaptizwa .
Kodwa mhlawumbi uyifumanisa ingcamango yokuthabatha ikhondo elinjalo lenkalipho njengento eyoyikisayo .
Asikuko ukuba akukholelwa kwiinyaniso ezisekelwe eBhayibhileni oye wazifundiswa .
Usenokuba uya rhoqo kwiintlanganiso zamaKristu yaye usenokuba nesabelo ngokuthe rhoqo ekwabelaneni nabanye ngeenyaniso zeBhayibhile .
Kanti , xa kufikelelwa kumbandela wokwahlulela ubomi bakho kuThixo , usenokuthandabuza .
Ngoko , lubaluleke kangakanani ubhaptizo ?
Yaye kutheni ulutsha oluninzi lukuphepha ?
Unqulo Olungenalo Uzahlulelo
KwiNgqobhoko , umbuzo wobhaptizo ngokufuthi ulutsha luwuphendulelwa ngabazali balo .
Wambi amahlelo akhuthaza abazali ukuba baphehlelele abantwana beseziintsana .
Yaye kwanaxa isithethe sonqulo sokubhaptizwa silungiselelwe nabantu abakhulu , ulutsha ngokuqhelekileyo lulindelwe ukuba lulandele unqulo lwabazali balo njengomendo walo wobomi , kungekuko ukuzikhethela .
Noko ke , okubangel ’ umdla kukuba , kuhlolisiso olwenziwe yiGallup eUnited States lwatyhila ukuba ngoxa “ phantse bonke abakwishumi elivisayo ( ama - 96 ekhulwini ) bekholelwa ukuba uThixo ukho , ” kuphela ngama - 39 ekhulwini athandaza ngokufuthi .
Yaye kuphela ngama - 52 ekhulwini akholelwayo elunqulweni olulungeleleneyo .
Ngaloo ndlela uDiane oselula umisela umzekelo woku xa esithi : “ Ndiyakholelwa kuThixo nakwezinye izinto ezinxulumene naye , kodwa ndikholelwa ngakumbi ekuzameni ukuba ngumntu olungileyo kunokufunda yonk ’ into eseBhayibhileni . ”
Ewe , unqulo lusenokuba ngamandla angacacanga , ngokungakumbi , xa lunyanzelwe kuthile ngabazali bakhe .
Uhlolisiso olwenziwa kwiqela elithile labantwana abangamaKatolika abaziinjubaqa lukubonisa ngokubhekele phaya oku .
Isiqingatha sabo sasihamba icawa .
Inkoliso yabo yayizazi iimfundiso ezisisiseko zenkolo yabo .
Yaye phantse ama - 90 ekhulwini abo ayengavumelani nokuba .
Kanti , ngaphezu kwesibini kwisithathu sabo babengamasela !
Incwadi ethi The Adolescent yaphawula oku : “ Esinye isizathu sisenokuba ukubandakanyeka kwala makhwenkwe elunqulweni kwakuyinto nje engenamsebenzi .
Onke ayezalwe engamaKatolika ; ukuzinikela kwawo okokuqala ayekwenzelwe ngabazali bawo .
Unqulo lwawo lwalungelulo olwawo . ”
Ubhaptizo ​ —⁠ Isizathu Sokuba Lube Yimfuneko KumaKristu
Ngoko , ngesizathu esilungileyo , iBhayibhile ifuna ukuba ibe nguwe ​ —⁠ kungekhona abazali bakho⁠ — ​ ozenzela isigqibo sobuqu sokuzahlulela kuThixo .
* Usenokuthi , ‘ Ichan ’ ucwethe , kodwa ukuba ukuzahlulela kobuqu kuyinto ephakathi kwam noThixo , kutheni ndifanele ndibhaptizwe nje ? ’
Kuba ubhaptizo lubandakanya ‘ ukusindiswa komphefumlo wakho . ’
UThixo ucinga ‘ ngokubaphindezela abangamaziyo uThixo , nabangazilulameliyo iindaba ezilungileyo zeNkosi yethu uYesu Kristu ; bona abo baya kuva ukubethwa , intshabalalo engunaphakade ke leyo . ’
Bonke ubungqina bubonisa ukuba le ntshabalalo iya kufika ngomhla wethu .
*
Kanti , ukuthanda kukaThixo kukuba “ bangasindiswa bonke abantu . ”
Ufuna ukuba usinde ekupheleni kwale nkqubo yezinto uze uphile ngonaphakade kumhlaba oyiParadisi !
Kodwa unokuzifanisa njani njengalowo uzilulamelayo iindaba ezilungileyo ?
Ukukholelwa nje kwiinyaniso zeBhayibhile oye wazifundiswa akwanele , kunganele nokuhamba nje nabazali bakho ukuya kwiintlanganiso zamaKristu .
( Thelekisa uYakobi 2 : ​ 19 . )
Abo bafuna ukusindiswa bafanele bazahlulele kuThixo baze benze ukuthanda kwakhe .
Umpostile uPawulos kumaRoma 12 : 1 uthi : “ Ndiyanivuselela ngoko , bazalwana , ngeemfefe zikaThixo , ukuba niyinikele imizimba yenu ibe lidini eliphilileyo , elingcwele , [ “ nizahlulele , ” The New English Bible ] elikholekileyo kuThixo : inkonzo yenu ke leyo yasengqondweni . ”
Kodwa ukuzahlulela akunakuhlala kungumcimbi wangasese .
Ngapha koko , umfundi wangasese unokuzinikela kangakanani , azahlulele kangakanani ?
( Thelekisa uYohane 19 : ​ 38 . )
Ngaba ubuya kumthemba umhlobo ofuna ubuhlobo benu bube yinto yangasese ?
Ngoko , ngobulumko , uThixo ufuna ukuba bonke ‘ benze uvumo lwasekuhleni ukuze basindiswe . ’
Oku kuqala ngobhaptizo .
Ngelo xesha , ubani uluvuma ngomlomo ukholo lwakhe .
Emva koko , kulandela ubhaptizo lwamanzi .
Noko ke , liyintoni ixabiso lokuntywiliselwa kukabani emanzini ?
Ubhaptizo asikuko ukuthiwa nkxu nje ; kukungcwatywa okungokomfuziselo .
Xa untywiliselwa ngaphantsi kwamanzi obhaptizo , oko kugxininisa kuwe ukuba uye wafa kwikhondo lobomi bakho langaphambili .
Ngaphambili , amabhongo akho obuqu , usukelo lwakho neminqweno yakho yayisiza kuqala ebomini bakho .
Kodwa uYesu wathi abafundi bakhe babeya ‘ kuzincama . ’
Ngoko xa unyuswa emanzini , uyakhunjuzwa ukuba ngoku uphilele ukuze wenze ukuthanda kukaThixo .
Esi senzo senkalipho nesasesidlangalaleni siyindima ebalulekileyo yokubekwa uphawu olukufanisa njengalowo ofanelekele ukusinda ! ​ —⁠ Hezekile 9 : ​ 4 -⁠ 6 ; thelekisa eyoku - 1 kaPetros 3 :⁠ 21 .
‘ Ndoyika Ukuba Ndiya Kususwa Kubudlelane ’
Ukuba ubhaptizo lubaluleke kangako , ngoko , kutheni ulutsha oluninzi lungafuni ukubhaptizwa ?
UVukani !
wabuza kwalo mbuzo mnye kwiqela lolutsha olungamaKristu .
Enye intombazana yathi : “ Abaninzi bavakalelwa kukuba baya kuba nenkululeko engakumbi ukuba ababhaptizwanga .
Bavakalelwa kukuba ukuba bangena engxakini , abanakubekwa tyala kangako . ”
Osemtsha ogama linguRobert waphinda la mazwi ngokugqabaza athi : “ Ndicinga ukuba abantu abasebatsha abaninzi bayathandabuza ukubhaptizwa ngenxa yokoyika ukuba eli linyathelo lokugqibela abangenakurhoxa kulo .
Bavakalelwa kukuba ukuba benza okuthile okuphosakeleyo , baya kugxothwa ebandleni . ”
Kuyinyaniso ukuba ubani akanakurhoxa akuba ezahlulele kuThixo .
( Thelekisa INtshumayeli 5 :⁠ 4 . )
Umntu ozahlulela kuThixo uthabatha imbopheleleko enzulu .
Unyanzelekile ukuba ‘ ahambe ngokuyifaneleyo iNkosi , ase kuko konke ukuyikholisa . ’
Ubani obandakanyeka kwisono esinzulu uzibeka esichengeni sokugxothwa ebandleni lobuKristu . ​ —⁠ 1 Korinte 5 : ​ 11 -⁠ 13 .
Kanti , ubani akanakuqiqa ngelokuba lo gama nje ubani engabhaptizwanga , unokwenza unothanda .
Kuba “ kowaziyo ukwenza okuhle , angakwenzi , kulowo kusisono ” ​ —⁠ ebhaptizwe okanye engabhaptizwanga !
Ubani unokukuphepha ukususwa ngokusesikweni ebandleni , kodwa ubani akanakuwuphepha umgwebo kaYehova .
UPawulos uyalumkisa , “ Ningazikhohlisi !
UThixo akanakwenziwa isidenge ngumntu . Umntu uya kuvuna kanye loo nto ayihlwayeleyo . ” ​ —⁠ Galati 6 :⁠ 7 , TE .
Ngokufuthi uloyiko lokususwa kubudlelane enyanisweni lufihla umdla wangasese wokwenza ububi .
Ibhinqa eliselula eligama linguNatalie ngokuphandle lathi : “ Ndakhuliselwa kwihlabathi likaSathana yaye ndiyayazi into eliyiyo .
Kodwa abantu abaselula abaninzi bafuna ukuya kulo baze bazivele ngokwabo ukuba linjani na . ”
Kunokuba uvumele iminqweno ephosakeleyo ikwenze uthandabuze ukubhaptizwa ​ —⁠ okanye uyenze ikhulele ekubeni zizenzo eziphosakeleyo⁠ — ​ kutheni ungafumani uncedo , mhlawumbi ngokuwuthetha lo mcimbi nomzali okanye umKristu okhulileyo ? ​ —⁠ Yakobi 1 : ​ 14 , 15 .
Ngokwenene , inkululeko uSathana ayithembisayo iyinkohliso nje kuphela .
Kunjengokuba umpostile uPetros wathi ngabathile ababelahlekisiwe ngomhla wakhe : “ Bebathembisa nje inkululeko , bona ngokwabo bangabakhonzi bokonakala ; kuba lowo athi ubani eyiswe nguye , ukhonzisiwe nokukhonziswa kuye . ”
Ngaba ngenene kuyinkululeko ukuba ukucinga kwakho , nesimo sakho sengqondo nendlela oziphatha ngayo ilawulwa ngabanye ?
Ngaba ngokwenene yinkululeko ukubandakanyeka kwizenzo ezikhokelela kwisifo , ukuhlazeka yaye ekugqibeleni , ekufeni ? ​ —⁠ IMizekeliso 5 : 8 - 14 .
Oselula waseJapan ogama linguHitoshi wayejamelane nale mibuzo ifanayo .
Wayekhuliswe ngabazali abangamaKristu yaye ukhumbula oku : “ Ngoxa abanye babedlala , kwakufuneka ndiye ezintlanganisweni .
Ndandifuna inkululeko engakumbi .
Ndandicinga ukuba ndandilahlekelwa kokuthile . ”
Ewe , njengomdumisi uAsafu , ‘ wabamonela ’ abenzi bobubi .
Kodwa emva kokucingisisa ngokunzulu ngalo mcimbi , iimvakalelo zikaHitoshi zaguquka .
Uthi : “ Ndaqonda ukuba ubomi bam babuya kuba njani ngaphandle kwenyaniso ​ —⁠ ndandizibona ndiphila iminyaka engama - 70 okanye engama - 80 emva koko ndife .
Kodwa uYehova uthembisa ubomi obungunaphakade ! ”
Ngaloo ndlela uHitoshi wazahlulela kuThixo waza wabhaptizwa . ​ —⁠ Thelekisa INdumiso 73 : 19 - 28 .
Ngaba ushukunyiselwa ukwenza okufanayo ?
Oselula ogama linguDavid washukunyiselwa ukwenjenjalo .
Ubalisa oku : “ Ukubhaptizwa ngoxa ndandiselula kwandikhusela . . . .
Bambi abakwishumi elivisayo abangabhaptizwanga ebandleni babeziva bekhululekile kwigunya labadala yaye ngenxa yoku babambiseka ekuziphatheni okubi .
Kodwa ndandisoloko ndikhumbula ukuba ndandibahlulele ubomi bam kuThixo . ”
Noko ke , mhlawumbi akuqinisekanga enoba ngenene ukulungele kusini na ukuthabatha eli khondo .
Inkcazelo yokukunceda iya kunikelwa kwinqaku elilandelayo .
