‘ Ngaba UThixo Ndimenze Umhlobo Wam ? ’
Noko ke , mhlawumbi eyona mbambano ibalulekileyo ibandakanya ulwalamano lwakho noThixo .
Khumbula : Uzahlulela kungekhona kumsebenzi okanye kwinto ethile , okanye kungekhona nakwintlangano , kodwa kuThixo .
Ngaba uThixo ukhangeleka engowokuthelekelelwa , engengowokwenene ?
Okanye ngaba uye wafikelela ekumazini nasekumthandeni njengoMntu ?
Ukuba kunjalo , uya kuzifumana uthetha naye ngokufuthi , hayi ngokuzenzekelayo , kodwa ngokusuka entliziyweni . ​ —⁠ INdumiso 62 :⁠ 8 .
Kwakhona phantse uya kuzifumanisa unyanzeleka ukuthetha nabanye ngoThixo .
