Yaye ngokuzingisa kufundisiso lobuqu , kumthandazo , nasekunxulumaneni nabantu bakhe , uya kuthi ekuhambeni kwexesha uzive usondele ngakumbi kuThixo .
Ubhaptizo luya kuba ngumphumo ozenzekelayo ‘ wokusondela kuThixo ’ okunjalo . ​ —⁠ Yakobi 4 :⁠ 8 .
