Ndiyazi ukuba kunjani na ukuziziliza ukwenza oku .
Kodwa ndifuna ukuthi kuyeyona nto imangalisayo onokuyenza .
Khawuthelekelele nje , ukwazi ukuba uYehova uyakholiswa nguwe nokuba ‘ akayi kukha akuyekele okanye akushiye ’ !
Ukuba nabani na ebeya kundibuza enoba ufanele azahlulele na kuYehova , bendiya kuthi ewe !
Kodwa oko musa ukukwenzela ukukholisa omnye umntu .
Kwenze kuba ukufuna . ”
