Ngokutsho kweJournal of the American Medical Association , “ intlaninge yabantu abaxhalatyiswe kukusetyenziswa kwezilwanyana ekwenzeni uphando lwezonyango inokwahlulahlulwa ibe ngamaqela amabini : ( 1 ) ngabo baxhalabele impilontle yezilwanyana abangayichasanga into yokwenziwa kophando lwezonyango kodwa bafuna ukuqinisekiswa ukuba izilwanyana ziphathwa njengabantu kangangoko kunokwenzeka , into yokuba inani lezilwanyana ezisetyenziswayo lelona lincinane nelifuneka ngenene , nokuba izilwanyana zisetyenziswa kuphela xa kuyimfuneko . ”
