Abantu abaninzi abalwela inkululeko yezilwanyana nabeyiseke ngokupheleleyo abahambisani nokusetyenziswa kwezilwanyana ukulungiselela ukutya , izambatho , imidlalo kwanokuba nje zibe zizilwanyana ezingamaqabane .
