Imibuzo Ekufuneka Iphendulwe
NGAXA lithile ebomini bakho , usenokuba wakhe wazibuza oku : ‘ Ukuba uThixo ukho , kutheni evumele ukubandezeleka okungaka ?
Yaye kutheni ekuvumele ixesha elide kangaka , ukutyhubela yonke imbali yabantu ?
Ngaba ukubandezeleka kuya kuze kuphele ? ’
Ngenxa yokungabi nazimpendulo zanelisayo kwimibuzo enjalo , abaninzi bayacaphuka .
Bambi bade bayeke nokukholelwa kuThixo , okanye bambek ’ ityala ngamashwa abo .
Ngokomzekelo , indoda eyasinda Ekubulaweni Kwabantu Ngenkohlakalo , ukubulawa kwezigidi ngamaNazi kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II , yaba buhlungu kangangokuba yathi : “ Ukuba ubunokuyikhotha intliziyo yam , ibiya kukutyhefa . ”
Enye indoda eyabandezeleka ngenxa yentshutshiso yohlanga , eyabangela ukufa kwabahlobo namalungu entsapho kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi I , ibuhlungu yabuza isithi : “ Wayephi uThixo xa sasimfuna ? ”
Ngaloo ndlela , abantu abaninzi badidekile .
Ngokwendlela abazibona ngayo izinto , kubonakala kungangqinelani noThixo wokulunga nothando ukuvumela izinto ezimbi zenzeke kangangexesha elide kangaka .
Okwenziwe Ngabantu
Ngokuqinisekileyo liyinyaniso elokuba abantu baye benza izinto ezimbi kakhulu kwabanye ukutyhubela iinkulungwane ​ —⁠ enyanisweni , kangangamawaka eminyaka .
Ubunzulu nokoyikeka kwako konke oku kungaphaya kokuqonda .
Njengoko kubonakala ngathi impucuko yenza inkqubela , abantu benze izixhobo eziya zisothusa ngakumbi ukwenzela ukutshabalalisa okanye ukwenzakalisa abanye : oombayimbayi , imibhaxa , iinqwelo - moya zokulwa , iitanki , imijukujelwa , iintolo zomlilo , izixhobo ezikhupha imichiza nezenyukliya .
Ngenxa yoko , kule nkulungwane kuphela , iimfazwe zeentlanga ziye zabulala abantu abamalunga nekhulu lezigidi !
Amakhulu ezigidi angakumbi aye enzakala okanye abandezeleka ngezinye iindlela .
Yaye izinto eziye zatshatyalaliswa , ezinjengezindlu nezinye izinto ezixabisekileyo , azinakubalwa .
Cinga ngosizi , intlungu neenyembezi ezingathethekiyo eziye zabangelwa yimfazwe !
Phantse ngalo lonke ixesha ngabantu abamsulwa abaye babandezeleka : amaxhego namaxhegokazi , abantwana , iintsana .
Yaye izihlandlo ezininzi , abaninzi abenze obo bubi abazange baphenduliswe .
Zwenibanzi , ukubandezeleka kuyaqhubeka kude kube ngulo mzuzu .
Suku ngalunye , abantu bayabulawa okanye babe ngamaxhoba olwaphulo - mthetho ngandlel ’ ithile .
Bayenzakala okanye bafe kwiingozi , kuquka ‘ izenzo ezingokwemvelo ’ ezinjengeziphango , izikhukula neenyikima .
Babandezelwa kukungabikho kokusesikweni , ikhethe , ubuhlwempu , indlala , okanye izifo , okanye ngezinye iindlela ezininzi .
Kunokwenzeka njani ukuba uThixo olungileyo abe wadala okuthile ​ —⁠ uluntu ​ —⁠ oluye ngokufuthi , lwabandezeleka kabuhlungu kangaka kangangeenkulungwane ?
Ingxaki Esemzimbeni Womntu
Le ngxaki ibonakaliswa nasemzimbeni womntu .
Izazinzulu nabanye abaye bafunda ngomzimba womntu bayavuma ukuba wenziwe ngokumangalisayo nangokubalaseleyo .
Qwalasela ambalwa nje kumalungu awo amangalisayo : iliso lomntu elingakholelekiyo , ekungekho khamera inokufana nalo ; ingqondo emangalisayo , eyenza neyona khompyutha yenziwe ngobugcisa ikhangeleke ingento ; indlela amalungu omzimba antsonkothileyo asebenzisana ngayo ngaphandle kokulawulwa yimigudu yethu ; ummangaliso wokuzala , ukuvelisa umntwana obukekayo ​ —⁠ ongumfanekiso wabazali bakhe⁠ —⁠ ngeenyanga nje ezilithoba .
Abantu abaninzi bagqiba kwelokuba olu yilo lobugcisa , umzimba womntu , kumele ukuba lwadalwa nguMyili oligcisa ​ —⁠ uMdali , uThixo uSomandla .
Kanti , okulusizi kukuba , kwalo mzimba umangalisayo uyawohloka .
Ekuhambeni kwethuba woyiswa kukugula , ukwaluphala nokufa .
Ekugqibeleni uyavuthuluka ube luthuli .
Olunjani lona usizi !
Xa kanye umntu efanele azuze iingenelo kwiminyaka emininzi yamava aze abe ngolumke ngakumbi , umzimba uyaphelelwa .
Ekupheleni kwawo , onjani ukuba lusizi umahluko , kwimpilo , ukomelelela , nobuhle umzimba owawunokuba nabo ekuqaleni kwawo !
UMdali onothando wayenokukwenzela ntoni okuthile okubalasele njengomzimba womntu , ukuze nje akuyeke kuphele ngokulusizi ngolo hlobo ?
Wayenokuwudalela ntoni umatshini oqala kakuhle ngolo hlobo , unamandla kangako , kodwa uphele ngendlela enjalo ukuba mbi ?
Indlela Abanye Abakucacisa Ngayo
Abanye baye bathi ubungendawo nokubandezeleka zizixhobo zikaThixo zokuphucula ubuntu bethu esebenzisa inkxwaleko .
Umfundisi waseWisile wathi : “ Ukuhlawula kwabalungileyo ngenxa yababi kuyinxalenye yecebo likaThixo losindiso . ”
Wayethetha ukuba ukuze bakhe ubuntu babo baze basindiswe , abantu abalungileyo bamele babandezeleke ngenxa yezenzo zabantu ababi njengenxalenye yecebo likaThixo .
Kodwa ngaba ubawo onothando ongumntu ebenokuzama ukuphucula ubuntu babantwana bakhe ngokuceba ukubavumela ukuba babe ngamaxhoba ezaphuli - mthetho ezineengcwangu ?
Kwakhona , qwalasela ukuba abantu abaselula abaninzi bayafa kwiingozi okanye bayabulawa okanye bayafa emfazweni .
Loo maxhoba aselula akayi kuba nathuba limbi lokuphucula ubuntu bawo kuba aya kuba efile .
Ngoko ingcamango yokuba ukubandezeleka kuvunyelwe ukuze nje kuphuculwe ubuntu ayikho ngqiqweni .
Akukho bawo ungumntu onengqiqo nonothando obeya kufuna ukuba abathandekayo bakhe babandezeleke okanye bahlelwe yintlekele .
Enyanisweni , ubawo obeya kuceba ukuba abathandekayo bakhe babandezeleke ukuze ‘ bakhe ubuntu ’ ebeya kugqalwa engafanelekanga , engalungelelananga nangokwasengqondweni .
Ngoko ngaba kunokutshiwo ngokusengqiqweni ukuba uThixo , uBawo onothando ongoyena uphakamileyo , uMdali onobulumko bonke wendalo iphela , wakulungiselela ngabom ukubandezeleka njengenxalenye ‘ yecebo lakhe losindiso ’ ?
Oko ibiya kuba kukongezelela uphawu lwenkohlakalo engathethekiyo nolothusayo kuye , uphawu sonke esingalwamkeliyo kwanakubantu abaphantsi .
Ukufumana Iimpendulo
Sinokuphethukela phi ukuze sifumane iimpendulo kwimibuzo emayela nokuvumela kukaThixo ukubandezeleka nobungendawo ?
Ekubeni imibuzo ibandakanya uThixo , kusengqiqweni ukubona ukuba yena ngokwakhe uzilungiselele njani na iimpendulo .
Sizifumana njani iimpendulo zakhe ?
Ngokuya kumthombo uThixo athi uwubhalile njengokhokelo loluntu ​ —⁠ iBhayibhile Engcwele , iZibhalo Ezingcwele .
Kungakhathaliseki ukuba ubani ucinga ntoni na ngaloo mthombo , ukufanele ukuhlolisiswa , kuba , njengokuba umpostile uPawulos watshoyo : “ Sonke isibhalo , siphefumlelwe nguThixo nje , sikwancedela . . . ukululeka . ”
Wakwabhala esithi : “ Nathi , ukulamkela ilizwi likaThixo lodaba kuthi , analamkela lililizwi labantu ; nalamkela , njengokuba kunjalo okwenyaniso , lililizwi likaThixo . ”
* ​ —⁠ 1 Tesalonika 2 :⁠ 13 .
Ukufumana iimpendulo kwimibuzo emalunga nokuvunyelwa kokubandezeleka kungaphezulu kunokuba ibe kukuvavanya nje amandla engqondo .
Iimpendulo zibalulekile ukuze sikwazi ukuqonda oko kwenzekayo ngoku ehlabathini , oko kuya kwenzeka kwikamva elingekude nendlela ngamnye wethu achaphazeleka ngayo .
Kokokulungelwa kwethu ukuba sivumele iBhayibhile , eyindlela kaThixo yokunxibelelana nentsapho engabantu , izithethele ngokwayo .
Ngoko , ithini ngendlela okwaqala ngayo ukubandezeleka nesizathu sokuba uThixo ekuvumele ?
Into eya kusinceda ukuba siyiqonde impendulo inento yokwenza nendlela esenziwe ngayo ngokwengqondo nangokweemvakalelo .
IBhayibhile ibonisa ukuba uMdali wafaka olu phawu lubalulekileyo kwindlela esenziwe ngayo njengabantu : umnqweno wenkululeko .
Ngokufutshane makhe siqwalasele eyona nto ibandakanyekileyo kwinkululeko yabantu yokuzikhethela nendlela oku okukuchaphazela ngayo ukuvumela kukaThixo ukubandezeleka .
