Ukusetyenziswa Kakubi Kwenkululeko Yokuzikhethela
Abazali bethu bokuqala basilibala isibakala sokuba babengadalelwanga ukuba baphumelele ngaphandle koThixo nemithetho yakhe .
Bagqiba kwelokuba bazimele geqe kuThixo , becinga ukuba oko kwakuya kubuphucula ubomi babo .
Kodwa oku yayikukusebenzisa kakubi inkululeko yabo .
Baphumela ngaphandle kwemida emiselwe nguThixo yenkululeko yokuzikhethela . ​ —⁠ Genesis , isahluko 3 .
Kutheni uThixo engazange amtshabalalise uAdam noEva aze aqale ekuqaleni ngesinye isibini esingabantu ?
Kungenxa yokuba ulongamo lwakhe lwendalo iphela nendlela yakhe yokulawula zathi zathandatyuzwa .
Ukuba nguThixo kwakhe onguSomandla nokuba nguMdali wazo zonke izidalwa kumnika ilungelo lokuzilawula .
Ekubeni enoBulumko Bonke , ulawulo lwakhe lolona luzilungeleyo zonke izidalwa .
Kodwa ngoku ulawulo lukaThixo lwalucelwe umngeni .
Ngaba abantu babenokulawula bhetele kunokulawulwa nguThixo ?
Ngokuqinisekileyo uMdali wayeyazi impendulo kuloo mbuzo .
Indlela eqinisekileyo abantu ababenokufumanisa ngayo yayikukubavumela ukuba babe nenkululeko engasikelwe mda ababeyinqwenela .
Ngoko ke , esinye isizathu , phakathi kwezinye , sokuba uThixo eye wavumela ubungendawo nokubandezeleka sikukubonisa ngaphandle kwamathandabuzo enoba ulawulo lwabantu ngaphandle kwakhe lunokuphumelela kusini na .
