UAdam noEva bazizisela ukubandezeleka bona nenzala yabo .
‘ Bavuna ababekuhlwayele . ’
‘ Bazonakalisile kuye ​ —⁠ bengenyana [ bakaThixo ] , sisiphako sabo . ’ ​ —⁠ Duteronomi 32 : ​ 5 .
Abazali bethu bokuqala babelunyukisiwe ukuba ukuzimela geqe kulawulo lukaThixo kwakuya kuphumela ekufeni kwabo .
Oko kwangqineka kuyinyaniso .
Ngokushiya uThixo , bashiya umthombo wabo wempilo nobomi .
Baphelelwa ngamandla de ukufa kwabongamela . ​ —⁠ Genesis 3 :⁠ 19 .
Emva koko , uThixo wavumela ixesha elaneleyo lokuba intsapho engabantu ibonakalise ngokupheleleyo enoba nayiphi na inkqubo yobupolitika , yezentlalo , okanye yezoqoqosho abayiyile ngaphandle kolawulo lwakhe yayiya kungqineka isanelisa ngokupheleleyo kusini na .
Ngaba nayiphi na yezi nkqubo yayiya kuzisa ihlabathi elonwabileyo , elinoxolo elingenalo ulwaphulo - mthetho okanye imfazwe ?
Ngaba nayiphi na yayinokuzisa impumelelo engokwezinto eziphathekayo kubo bonke ?
Ngaba nayiphi na yayinokukoyisa ukugula , ukwaluphala nokufa ?
Ulawulo lukaThixo lwalulungiselelwe ukufeza zonke ezo zinto . ​ —⁠ Genesis 1 : ​ 26 -⁠ 31 .
Oko Siye Sakufunda Njengoko Ixesha Lihamba
Kungekudala imbali yayenza yacaca inyaniso ekumaRoma 5 : ​ 12 : “ Ukufa kwabatyhutyha abantu bonke . ”
Le ndinyana icacisa ukuba “ isono sangena ngamntu mnye ehlabathini , kwangena ke ukufa ngaso isono . ”
Xa abazali bethu bokuqala baluvukelayo ulawulo lukaThixo , baba ngabanesiphako , abangafezekanga .
Esi siphako sasikuphela kwento ababenokuyidlulisela kwinzala yabo .
Ngokomphumo , sonke siye sazalwa sinesiphako , sichanabeke ekuguleni nasekufeni .
Kwakhona ukuhamba kwexesha kuye kwatyhila indlela embi kunene abantu abanesono abaye baphathana ngayo .
Kuye kwakho iimfazwe ezingenakubaleka ezihambisa umzimba . Intiyo yobuhlanga neyonqulo , iinkundla zokuncina amakholwa , ulwaphulo - mthetho oloyikekayo lweentlobo ngeentlobo , nezenzo zokuzingca nokubawa .
Ukongezelela , izigidi ezingenakubalwa zabantu ziye zangamaxhoba obuhlwempu nendlala .
Ebudeni bamawaka eminyaka edluleyo , uluntu luye lwazama zonke iindlela ezinokucingwa zoorhulumente .
Kanti , omnye emva komnye baye basilela ukwanelisa iintswelo zabantu .
Kutshanje , oorhulumente bobuKomanisi baye bachaswa kumazwe amaninzi .
Kwiintlanga zolawulo - melo ulwaphulo - mthetho , ubuhlwempu , ukungazinzi kwezoqoqosho , nokonakala kwandile .
Eneneni , zonke iintlobo zoorhulumente babantu ziye zangqineka zisilela .
Ngokubhekele phaya , uThixo uye wavumela abantu ithuba lokuba bafikelele konke abanokukufikelela kwinzululwazi nakwizinto eziphathekayo .
Kodwa ngaba oku kuyinkqubela yokwenene xa utolo nesaphetha ziye zathatyathelwa indawo yimijukujelwa yenyukliya ?
xa abantu benokuya emajukujukwini kodwa bengenakuhlalisana ngoxolo emhlabeni ?
xa izigidi zabantu zisoyika ukuphuma ebusuku ngenxa yolwaphulo - mthetho ?
Okuye kwaboniswa kukuhamba kwexesha kukuba akuseyonto inokwenzeka ngabantu ‘ ukuqinisela ukunyathela kwabo ’ ngokunempumelelo kanye njengokuba kungenakwenzeka ngabo ukuphila ngaphandle kokudla , amanzi nomoya .
Sasenzelwe ukuba sixhomekeke kukhokelo loMenzi wethu kanye njengokuba sasenzelwe ukuba sixhomekeke kukudla , amanzi nomoya . ​ —⁠ Mateyu 4 :⁠ 4 .
Ngokuvumela ubungendawo nokubandezeleka , uThixo uye wayibonisa okokugqibela imiphumo elusizi yokusebenzisa kakubi inkululeko yokuzikhethela .
Esi sisipho esixabisekileyo kangangokuba endaweni yokuba athabathe inkululeko yokuzikhethela ebantwini , uThixo uye wabavumela ukuba babone oko kuthethwa kukuyisebenzisa kakubi .
Mayela nenkululeko yokuzikhethela , impapasho ethi “ Statement of Principles of Conservative Judaism ” ithi : “ Ukuba bekuyinto engenakwenzeka ngabantu ukuba benze ukhetho oluphosakeleyo xa bejamelene nokulungileyo nokubi , ingcamango yokhetho xa iyonke ayinantsingiselo . . . .
Okuninzi kokubandezeleka kwehlabathi kubangelwa ngokungqalileyo kukusebenzisa kwethu kakubi inkululeko yokuzikhethela esiyinikiweyo . ”
Ngokuqinisekileyo , uYeremiya wayechanile xa wathi : “ Akukhona endodeni ehambayo ukuqinisela ukunyathela kwayo . ”
Yaye uSolomon naye wayechanile xa wathi : “ Ngexesha athi umntu agunyazele umntu , kube kubi kuye . ” ​ —⁠ INtshumayeli 8 :⁠ 9 .
Ngendlela esebenzisekayo , oko kubonisa ukungakwazi komntu ukuphelisa ukubandezeleka .
KwanoSolomon , kubo bonke ubulumko , ubutyebi , namandla akhe akazange akwazi ukuyiphelisa inkxwaleko ebangelwa lulawulo lomntu .
Ngoko , uThixo uya kukuphelisa njani ukubandezeleka ?
Ngaba uya kuze ababuyekeze abantu ngokubandezeleka kwabo kwexesha elidlulileyo ?
