Ukwaluphala Nokugula Akusekho : “ Isuka ibe nentlahla inyama yakhe ; ubuyela emihleni yobudodana bakhe . ”
“ Akayi kuthi ummi wakhona , Ndiyafa . ” ​ —⁠ Isaya 33 :⁠ 24 .
Ukufa , Isijwili , Nentlungu Azisekho Ngonaphakade : “ Azisule uThixo zonke iinyembezi emehlweni abo , kungabi sabakho kufa , kungabi sabakho nasijwili , nakukhala , nantlungu ; ngokuba izinto zokuqala zigqithile . ” ​ —⁠ ISityhilelo 21 : ​ 4 .
Bengachatshazelwa Lixesha Elidluleyo
Ihlabathi elitsha elenziwe nguThixo liya kwanelisa kangangokuba ukunandipha ubomi kwabemi bomhlaba akuyi kuphazanyiswa , kwanaziinkumbulo ezingathandekiyo zokubandezeleka kwangaphambili .
Iingcinga ezakhayo nemisebenzi emininzi eya kuba bubomi bemihla ngemihla babantu ngelo xesha litsha ngokuthe ngcembe ziya kuzicima iinkumbulo ezimbi zexesha elidluleyo .
Idinga likaThixo likukuba : “ Angakhunjulwa awokuqala , angenyuki athi qatha entliziyweni . ”

Abantu baya ‘ kugcoba nanini ’ yiloo nto uThixo aya kuyidala emhlabeni wonke .
“ Liphumle , lizolile ihlabathi lonke ; bayagqabhuka bamemelele . ” ​ —⁠ Isaya 65 : ​ 17 , 18 ; 14 :⁠ 7 .
Namhlanje , “ ukulindela okubanjezelweyo kubulala intliziyo , ” njengokuba iBhayibhile isitsho .
Kodwa imeko iya kuguquka kwihlabathi elitsha .
Ngelo xesha ‘ umnqweno ofezekileyo uya kuba ngumthi wobomi . ’
Iintliziyo azisayi kubuye zisindwe kukubandezeleka okanye zizithembiso ezingazalisekanga .
Endaweni yoko , ziya kuzaliswa lulwaneliseko novuyo ngenxa yezinto ezininzi ezimangalisayo uThixo aya kuzilungiselela intsapho yabantu .
Ulawulo Olwahlukileyo
Endaweni yolawulo olunganelisiyo lwabantu oluzimele geqe kuThixo , ihlabathi elitsha liya kuba nolawulo olwahluke ngokupheleleyo .
Igunya loburhulumente liya kuthatyathwa ebantwini .
Abasayi kuze baphinde bavunyelwe bazilawule ngaphandle koThixo .
Isiprofeto seBhayibhile sithi : “ Ngemihla yabo kumkani [ abalawuli abaphetheyo ngoku ] , uThixo wamazulu uya kumisa ubukumkani [ emazulwini ] obungayi konakala naphakade .
Obo bukumkani abuyi kusala nabantu bambi [ ekubeni ulawulo lomntu lungasekho ] ; buya kuzicola buzigqibe zonke ezo zikumkani [ ezikhoyo ngoku ] , bona bume ngonaphakade . ” ​ —⁠ Daniyeli 2 :⁠ 44 .
UYesu wafundisa abalandeli bakhe ukuba bathandazele ulawulo olutsha emhlabeni xa wathi : “ Mabufike ubukumkani bakho .
Makwenziwe ukuthanda kwakho nasemhlabeni , njengokuba kusenziwa emazulwini . ” ​ —⁠ Mateyu 6 :⁠ 10 .
Obo iya kuba buburhulumente obutsha babantu ​ —⁠ ulawulo lukaThixo lwasezulwini ngoBukumkani bakhe obulawulwa nguKristu .
Yaye emhlabeni , abakhonzi bakaThixo abanyanisekileyo abangabantu baya kuyilawula imicimbi ngokolwalathiso lukaThixo .
Umpostile uPetros wathetha ngeli lungiselelo litsha ‘ njengezulu elitsha nomhlaba omtsha esiwulindeleyo ngokwedinga lakhe , apho kumi ubulungisa . ’
Olo lawulo loBukumkani luyimfundiso esisiseko yeBhayibhile .
‘ Indalo Ikhululwe ’
Kwakhona olu lawulo lutsha luya kuwalawula ngokupheleleyo amandla endalo omhlaba .
‘ Izenzo ezingokwemvelo ’ ezinjengeenyikima , iinkanyamba , izikhukula okanye iimbalela azisayi kuphinda zibangele ukuxinezeleka .
UYesu ngokwakhe wabonisa igunya lakhe lokulawula la mandla .
Ngokomzekelo , ngasihlandlo sithile xa umkhombe uYesu nabafundi bakhe ababekuwo wawuza kuphequka ngenxa yesaqhwithi , wawuzolisa umoya nolwandle .
Abafundi ababemangalisiwe bathi : “ Ngumntu mni na lo , lento alulanyelwayo nayimimoya nalulwandle ? ” ​ —⁠ Mateyu 8 : ​ 23 -⁠ 27 .
Ngoko umhlaba , kwakunye nendalo engabantu , uya kufumana inkululeko engenakulinganiswa nanto .
“ Nendalo ngokwayo iya kukhululwa ebukhobokeni bokonakala , isingiswe enkululekweni yozuko lwabantwana bakaThixo .
Kuba siyazi ukuba yonke indalo iyancwina , inenimba kunye , unangoku . ” ​ —⁠ Roma 8 : ​ 21 , 22 .
Ngaba sinokuqiniseka ukuba kungekudala ulawulo lwabantu luya kuphela nokuba urhulumente omtsha kaThixo uya kuthabatha iintambo ekulawuleni yonke imicimbi yomhlaba ?
Ngokuqinisekileyo sinako , kuba uMongami Wendalo Iphela uyasiqinisekisa : “ Icebo lam liya kuma , ndikwenze konke ukuthanda kwam ; . . .
Nditshilo , ewe , ndiya kukufeza ; ndiyilile , ewe , ndiya kukwenza . ” ​ —⁠ Isaya 46 : ​ 10 , 11 .
‘ Ixesha Elimisiweyo ’
Kuya kwenzeka njani oko ?
Kuya kwenzeka nini ?
ILizwi likaThixo lithi : “ Into yonke inexesha elimisiweyo . ”
Oku kuquka ixesha elimisiweyo lokuba uThixo athi ‘ kwanele ! ’
nelokuphelisa ubungendawo nokubandezeleka .
UDaniyeli wabhekisela “ kwixesha elimisiweyo lokuphela . ”
UYesu wakwathetha ‘ ngexesha elimisiweyo . ’ ​ —⁠ Marko 13 : ​ 32 , 33 , NW .
Ewe , uThixo umisele ixesha eliqinisekileyo aya kungenelela ngalo kwimicimbi yabantu aze atshayele ulingelo olubangela usizi lolawulo lwabantu oluzimele geqe kuye .
“ Nolilungisa nongendawo , uThixo uya kulithetha ityala labo ; ngokuba umise ixesha layo yonke imicimbi . ”
Yaye ubungqina bokuzaliseka kweziprofeto zeBhayibhile bubonisa ukuba ixesha uThixo alimisileyo lokuvumela ukubandezeleka sele liza kuphela .
Xa elo xesha liphelile , uya kulutyumza luphele ulawulo lwabantu olunganelisiyo oluye kangangamawaka eminyaka lwezisa ukubandezeleka okukhulu kwintsapho yabantu . ​ —⁠ Mateyu 24 : ​ 3 - 14 ; 2 Timoti 3 : ​ 1 - 5 , 13 ; ISityhilelo 19 : ​ 11 -⁠ 21 .
Xa uThixo ephumeza imigwebo yakhe , phawula oko kuya kwenzeka kwabo bazithobayo kulawulo lwakhe , xa kuthelekiswa nabo bangazithobiyo : “ Kusaya kuba mzuzwana , angabikho ongendawo ; . . . ke bona abalulamileyo baya kulidla ilifa ilizwe , baziyolise ngobuninzi boxolo . ”
“ Ke yona imbewu yongendawo iyanqanyulwa .
Amalungisa aya kulidla ilifa ilizwe , ahlale kulo ngonaphakade . ”
“ Gcina ogqibeleleyo , ukhangele othe tye ; ngokuba izivela - mva zezomntu woxolo .
Ke bona abangendawo batshatyalaliswa kuphele . ” ​ —⁠ INdumiso 37 : ​ 10 , 11 , 28 , 29 , 37 , 38 ; bona kwaneMizekeliso 2 : ​ 21 , 22 ; Mateyu 5 :⁠ 5 .
Kodwa kuthekani ngamawaka ezigidi zabantu abasele befile ?
Ziya kungenelwa njani kwihlabathi elitsha ?
Ngovuko , ukubuyiselwa ebomini kanye apha emhlabeni .
Ziya kubuya emangcwabeni zize zinikwe ithuba lokunandipha ubomi ngonaphakade .
ILizwi likaThixo liyaqinisekisa : “ Kuza kubakho uvuko lwabafileyo , lwamalungisa kwanolwabangemalungisa . ”
Yaye uYesu wakubonisa oku ngokuvusa abantu abafileyo , abanjengoLazaro nonyana womhlolokazi waseNayin . ​ —⁠ Yohane 11 : ​ 38 - 44 ; Luka 7 : ​ 11 -⁠ 16 .
“ Imbuyekezo ”
Hayi indlela ekukhuthaza ngayo ukwazi ukuba injongo kaThixo kukuphelisa ukubandezeleka nokuzisa ihlabathi elitsha lobulungisa !
Cinga ngokuphila izigidi zeminyaka ​ —⁠ enyanisweni , ngonaphakade⁠ — ​ kwimpilo nolonwabo olufezekileyo phakathi kweemeko zeParadisi , apho ubungendawo nokubandezeleka ziya kuba zizinto zexesha elidluleyo ngonaphakade !
Ubungayi kuvuma na ukuba le “ mbuyekezo ” uThixo aya kuyinika uluntu ​ —⁠ kuwo onke amaphakade ​ —⁠ ngokwentelekiso iyigqwesa lee iminyaka engamawaka ambalwa athe ebudeni bayo uThixo wavumela ukubandezeleka ?
Kwakhona ngaba ayiyigqwesi iminyaka engama - 70 okanye engama - 80 yokubandezeleka ​ —⁠ okanye engaphantsi ​ —⁠ esisenokuba siye sayinyamezela njengabantu ngabanye ebudeni bokuphila kwethu ?
Imbono Yexesha elide
Kwimbono yakhe yexesha elide ngezinto , uMdali uyazi ukuba kwakubalulekile ukuzinzisa kuqala imibandela ebalulekileyo engelungelo lakhe lokulawula njengoMongami Wendalo Iphela nokulunga kolawulo lwakhe .
Yaye kwakubalulekile ukuzinzisa umbandela wokusetyenziswa ngokufanelekileyo nangokungafanelekanga kwenkululeko yokhetho .
Kwakukwayimfuneko ukubonisa ukuba indalo yakhe igqibelele ngokuba abantu abazithoba ngokunyaniseka kulawulo lwakhe lobulungisa banokugcina ingqibelelo yabo kuye ngaphantsi kokutshutshiswa nokuvavanywa ngabalawuli behlabathi , umzekelo obalaseleyo woku nguNyana wakhe , uYesu , ngoxa wayesemhlabeni .
Ekubeni ezizinzisile zonke ezi mbambano , uThixo akayi kuvumela ubungendawo nokubandezeleka zibekho kwakhona ukuze ziphazamise uxolo lwendalo iphela .
“ Imbandezelo ayisayi kuphakama izihlandlo ezibini . ” ​ —⁠ Nahum 1 :⁠ 9 .
Ukutyhubela amaphakade ezayo , uThixo unokusebenzisa oko kuye kwenzeka kula mawaka eminyaka adluleyo njengokungathi lityala elivavanywe kwinkundla ephakamileyo .
Okwenzekayo ngaphambi kwalo kunokusetyenziswa nangaliphi na ixesha kwikamva , nakweyiphi na indawo kwindalo iphela , ukuba kunokwenzeka kwakhona kuphakame amathandabuzo mayela nokuba ngumongami kukaThixo okanye ukusetyenziswa ngokufanelekileyo kwenkululeko yokuzikhethela .
Uya Kukhetha Ntoni ?
Namhlanje sijamelene nokhetho .
Inkululeko yethu yokuzikhethela sinokuyisebenzisa ngenye yeendlela ezimbini : Sinokukhetha ukuzityeshela iinjongo zikaThixo , saneliseke lulawulo lwabantu olungafezekanga , size sibe nesabelo kwisiphelo salo , okanye sinokusebenzisa inkululeko yethu yokuzikhethela ukufunda oko zikuko iinjongo zikaThixo noko kufuneka sikwenzile ukuze simkholise njengabameli abazinikeleyo boBukumkani bakhe .
UYesu wathi kuThixo emthandazweni : “ Bubo ke obu ubomi obungunaphakade , ukuba mabakwazi , wena ukuphela koThixo oyinyaniso , naye uYesu Kristu omthumileyo . ”
Ngoko ukuba sifuna ubomi kwihlabathi elitsha , kufuneka senze umgudu wokufunda inyaniso engoThixo , iinjongo zakhe neemfuno zakhe .
Phawula indlela iBhayibhile ekubeka ngayo oku : “ UYehova unani ekubeni ninaye ; ukuba nithe namquqela , nomfumana ; ukuba nithe namshiya , wonishiya nani . ” ​ —⁠ 2 Kronike 15 :⁠ 2 .
Eli hlabathi lidala liphelelwa lixesha ; elitsha lisemnyango : “ Ihlabathi ke liyadlula , nenkanuko yalo ; ke yena owenza ukuthanda kukaThixo uhleli ngonaphakade . ”
Uya kukhetha liphi ​ —⁠ ihlabathi elidala elidlulayo okanye elo litsha lizayo ?
ILizwi likaThixo lithi : “ Ndibeke phambi kwenu ubomi nokufa , intsikelelo nesiqalekiso . Nyula ke ubomi , ukuze uphile , wena nembewu yakho ; ukuba umthande uYehova uThixo wakho , uliphulaphule ilizwi lakhe , unamathele kuye : ngokuba bubomi bakho , nokolulwa kweemini zakho . ” ​ —⁠ Duteronomi 30 : ​ 19 , 20 .
Ngaba kungumnqweno wakho ukunandipha iintsikelelo uThixo azigcinele abo bavisisanisa ukuthanda kwabo nokuthanda kwakhe ?
Abapapashi beli phephancwadi okanye amaNgqina kaYehova naphi na ehlabathini aya kukuvuyela ukukunceda , ngesisa , ukuba ufunde okungakumbi ngoku .
