Ukuvala Umsantsa Phakathi Koogqirha Nabaguli AbangamaNgqina
EHLABATHINI lonke inye kuphela into eyaziwa ngoogqirha ngamaNgqina kaYehova : Awakwamkeli ukutofelwa igazi .
Noko ke , oogqirha abaninzi bazi okuncinane gqitha ngamaNgqina .
Ngoko xa befuna ukutofela igazi kumguli oliNgqina , ukungakwamkeli kwakhe bakujonga njengokungekho ngqiqweni ngokupheleleyo .
Ngenxa yoku , kunokuvuleka umsantsa omkhulu phakathi kogqirha nomguli .
Bebonke bambalwa gqitha oogqirha abaqondayo ukuba amaNgqina kaYehova awachasananga nonyango lwezamayeza nokuba ukuma kwawo kumbandela wegazi akunakuguqulwa yaye kusekelwe ngokunzulu kumthetho ongokweZibhalo .
Kwangaxeshanye , ukuba sengqiqweni koku kuma okungokweZibhalo ngokuqhubekayo kuye kwangqinwa luthotho lwencazelo entsha eye yafunyaniswa ngokwezenzulwazi mayela neengozi zokutofelwa kwegazi elingokwemvelo nokukhuseleka kokusetyenziswa kwezinye izinto endaweni yokutofela igazi .
Kodwa amaNgqina kaYehova anokubenza njani oogqirha bezamayeza bayifumane le nkcazelo ?
IiKomiti Zokunxibelelana Nezibhedlele
Kulo mba , iQumrhu Elilawulayo lamaNgqina kaYehova liye layalela ukuba kusekwe iikomiti zokunxibelelana nezibhedlele kwizixeko ezikhulu nezinamaziko amakhulu ezonyango .
EUnited States , iikomiti ezinokuba likhulu , inye inamalungu amahlanu ngokomlinganiselo , sele zisenza unxibelelwano phakathi kwabo bakwimicimbi yezonyango namaNgqina .
Ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka eli lungiselelo liye ladluliselwa nakwamanye amazwe .
Ukususela ngoFebruwari 19 ukusa kuMatshi 27 , amalungu amathathu eSebe Lenkcazelo Yezibhedlele eBrooklyn aye atyelela iiofisi zamasebe ezisibhozo zamaNgqina kaYehova kummandla wePasifiki .
Injongo yolu tyelelo yayintlu - ntathu : kukuqhuba iinkomfa zokuqeqesha abalungiseleli abangamaNgqina nabanyulwe kusengaphambili kumsebenzi weekomiti zokunxibelelana nezibhedlele , ukuqeqesha abasebenzi bamasebe ukwalathisa kwiSebe Lenkcazelo Yezibhedlele kwisebe ngalinye , nokutyelela izibhedlele noogqirha ukubakhuthaza ukuba baqhubeke baze bakhulise ubuchule babo ekunyangeni amaNgqina kaYehova ngaphandle kokusebenzisa igazi .
Kwaqhutywa iinkomfa ezine ; eyokuqala yayiseSydney kulungiselelwa isebe laseOstreliya nelaseNew Zealand ; kwaqhutywa enye eManila ukwenzela iiPhilippines , iHong Kong neTaiwan ; kwisiXeko sase - Ebina kwaqhutywa eyaseJapan neyaseKorea ; yaye eyokugqibela yaseHawaii yaqhutyelwa eHonolulu .
Kule nkqubo kwakusetyenziswa iimifanekiso yeeslides neyevideo ekuchazeni imisebenzi noko kuqulethwe ligazi noludwe olwandayo lwezinto ezinokusetyenziswa endaweni yegazi elingokwemvelo .
Kwezi ngxubusho kwagutyungelwa iindlela zokunceda amaNgqina kaYehova xa ejamelene neengxaki ezibandakanya igazi .
Kwakule nkomfa kwagxininiswa imbaluleka yokusebenzisana noogqirha nezibhedlele , ngaloo ndlela kusenza kube lula ngabo ukukuhlonela ukuma kwamaNgqina .
Elinye ilungu lale komiti yaseJapan lathi : “ Enyanisweni olu cwangciso lusixhobisele ukuba siwusingathe kakuhle lo msebenzi wokuhlakulela ukuqondana . ”
AmaNgqina angaphezu kwangama - 350 azo zonke iindidi zabantu aqeqeshwa kwezi nkomfa zine .
Ngaphambi kolu tyelelo , iiofisi zamasebe zalungiselela ukubonana noogqirha namalungu aphambili kwizibhedlele ezikhulu ukuze zixubushe ukungalwamkeli kwamaNgqina kaYehova unyango ekusetyenziswa kulo igazi .
Amaqela amathathu kwisebe ngalinye abelwa ukuba enze olu tyelelo , qela ngalinye likhokelwa ngomnye wabameli abathathu abavela eBrooklyn .
Oku akuzange nje kuphela kunikele uqeqesho olukhawulezileyo kwabo babelwe ukuba babe ngamalungu kwezi komiti zezibhedlele kodwa kwabenza baziva bekhululekile xa bethetha noogqirha neengcali zezempilo .
Kwixesha leeveki ezintandathu kwenziwa amatyelelo anjalo angaphezu kwama -⁠ 55 .
Unxibelelwano Olubangela Intsebenziswano
Oku kube nemiphumo emihle gqitha .
EOstreliya elinye iqela elityelelayo lahlangana nesekela lomphathiswa wezempilo welizwe laseNew South Wales .
Laxubusha naye ngokwenziwa kotyando ngaphandle kokusetyenziswa kwegazi kumaziko amaninzi ezempilo , licebisa ukuba elaseOstreliya linokuba liziko lotyando olunjalo lwamaNgqina kaYehova kuMzantsi Pasifiki .
Eli sekela alizange lisibone isizathu sokuba kungenakusekwa amaqela oogqirha okwenza utyando olunjalo .
Kwatyelelwa iindawo ezingama - 22 eOstreliya .
Omnye umalathisi wesinye isibhedlele wathi : “ Ninolwazi olugqithisileyo ngombandela wegazi nowonyango ngaphandle kwalo kunokuba thina sisazi . ”
Intsumpa yequmrhu lezibhedlele ezisixhenxe yaqinisekisa ukuba yayiza kumisela unjingalwazi wotyando ukuba akhe aphande ngelinge lokumisela iqela labatyandi kwesinye sezibhedlele zabo ukuba silungiselele unyango lwamaNgqina kaYehova ekungasetyenziswa gazi kulo .
Kwiziko loqhaqho - fakelo lwentliziyo laseManila ​ —⁠ eligqalwa ngabathile njengelilelona liphambili eMpuma⁠ — ​ umalathisi wezamayeza waxelelwa ukuba amaNgqina kaYehova anokuba likhulu nalindele ukutyandwa iintliziyo ayebekwe ekugqibeleni kuludwe kuba engalamkeli igazi .
Wathi uza kukutshitshisa oku .
Umalathisi wezamayeza kwesona sibhedlele siphucukileyo kwiiPhilippines , iSt .
Luke , waboniswa oko kuthethwa ziincwadi zonyango ngotyando ekungasetyenziswa gazi kulo , yaye wavuma ukuba lolona lukhuselekileyo .
Wavuma esithi : “ Le yeyona nto ifanelekileyo .
Ikuphela kwendlela esinokuphepha ngayo uGawulayo nesifo sesibindi . ”
Wabonisa ukuba ukulungele ukuwavumela amaNgqina ukuba anyangwe ngaphandle kwegazi kwisibhedlele sakhe ; ukwangumongameli weziko lokulondoloza igazi .
Kwinkomfa eyayiseJapan yeentsuku ezintathu , elaseKorea lalikwanabameli , kukho amaNgqina kaYehova angama - 44 , aba -⁠ 5 bawo bengoogqirha .
Kwakukho abalungiseleli abangama - 255 abangamaNgqina abavela eJapan , kuquka oogqirha abangama - 41 , phakathi kwabo kukho noogqirha bokutyanda bezigulo ezinxulumene nentloko nabokuphelisa iintlungu ngexesha lotyando , ndawonye namagqwetha amabini .
Kwasekwa iikomiti ezingamashumi amabini eJapan , nezisixhenxe eKorea .
Emva kwale nkomfa , abahlohli bahamba namalungu asekuhlaleni eekomiti zesibhedlele ukuya kutyelela oogqirha nezibhedlele ezikwimimandla yaseTokyo ukuze kusekwe umoya wentsebenziswano .
Omnye umlungiseleli waseJapan unikela le ngxelo : “ Satyelela isekela likanjingalwazi wezokubelekisa kwisibhedlele saseyunivesithi .
Uye wabelekisa abafazi abalishumi abangamaNgqina kaYehova .
Omnye wabo ngenxa yokopha walahlekelwa ligazi elingangekyubhiki sentimitha ezingama - 2 800 , yaye umlinganiselo wehemoglobin yakhe wehla waba ziidesilitha ezisisi - 3,5 ngegram nganye .
( Umlinganiselo owamkelekileyo kwibhinqa ngalinye ziidesilitha ezili - 14 ngegram . )
Kodwa lo gqirha wakwazi ukumbelekisa ngaphandle kokusebenzisa igazi .
Nangona engumBhuda , inkqubo yakhe yeyokuxabisa inkolelo yabaguli abanyangayo .
Wavuma ukuqhubeka ebamkela abaguli abangamaNgqina kaYehova . ”
Umalathisi wezamayeza waseYokohama wavuma ukuba isibhedlele sakhe sibalelwe kwizibhedlele ezikulungeleyo ukusebenzisana nabaguli abangamaNgqina waza wathi baya kukuvuyela nokwamkela lawo angamkelwanga kwezinye izibhedlele .
Lo gqirha wathi : “ Ukunyanga amaNgqina kaYehova ngaphandle kokusebenzisa igazi enyanisweni kulucelomngeni , kodwa ndiyawaxabisa amaNgqina kuba andivulele ithuba lokuphucula ubuchule bam njengogqirha . ”
Kwakhona omnye ugqirha ongumbelekisi eYokohama wathi : “ Ndiya kuwalwela amalungelo omguli nasenkundleni ukuba bendiya kumangalelwa ngokungatofeli igazi ngenxa yokuthobela oko kukukuthanda komguli . ”
Iikomiti ezasekwa eKorea zinikela ingxelo yempumelelo entle .
NgoMeyi 26 kwatyelelwa iSibhedlele seYunivesithi iYonsei .
Saziwa ngokubanzi kwelaseKorea yaye sinamasebe amathathu .
Amalungu awo onke la masebe ayekho , abantu abangama - 62 bebonke .
Unjingalwazi wokuphelisa iintlungu ebudeni botyando wathetha phantsi komxholo othi “ Ukusetyenziswa Kwamayeza Okuphelisa Iintlungu Kubaguli AbangamaNgqina KaYehova . ”
Inkcazelo awayinikelayo iza kubhalwa kulindixesha waseKorea wezamayeza okuphelisa iintlungu .
Ekubeni sisesinye sezibhedlele eziphambili eKorea , oku kufanele kube nempembelelo entle nakwezinye izibhedlele nakwabanye oogqirha .
