Kusenokufuneka lufunde indlela yokusebenza phantsi komphathi ‘ ekunzima ukumkholisa ’ okanye ocaphuka msinya , okanye indlela yokuqhubana ngobubele nabathengi abanolunya ​ —⁠ nabo basebenza nalo .
