Noko ke , namhlanje ulutsha oluninzi ( ingakumbi eUnited States ) lusebenza kwizindlu zokutyela ukutya okwenziwa ngokukhawuleza okanye kumashishini asebenza ngokutya apho umsebenzi uquka imisetyenzana enjengokufaka iihamburgers ezibhokisini okanye ukusebenza ngoomatshini ekuhlawulwa kubo .
