Kunokukhulisa umnqweno ongalunganga wezinto eziphathekayo .
( Thelekisa eyoku -⁠ 1 kuTimoti 6 : ​ 8 , 9 . )
Kunokukhulisa umoya wokuzingca , wokuba ndim kuqala ochaseneyo nomoya wobuKristu wokupha .
Ngoko ngaphambi kokufumana umsebenzi , bekungayi kuba kokona kulunge kakhulu ukuqinisekisa enoba kuyimfuneko ngokwenene ?
Isikolo Nomsebenzi
Enye into yokuqwalaselwa ngumphumo ukusebenza okunokuba nawo kwimfundo yakho .
UYesu wathi : “ Akukho umntu unako ukukhonza nkosi mbini . ”
Lo mgaqo uyasebenza kubafundi abaninzi ekufuneka bejamelene nengxaki yokufunda usebenza .
Ufundisiso lubonisa ukuba abaselula abasebenzayo kusenokwenzeka ngakumbi ukuba bangabikho esikolweni kunabangasebenziyo .
Yaye xa bekhona , badla ngokunganikel ’ ingqalelo .
UOlga oselula ucacisa athi : “ Ndandiphuma esikolweni emini emaqanda ndize ndenze umsebenzi wokuba ngunobhala ukususela ngentsimbi yokuqala kuse kweyesihlanu . ”
Waba yintoni umphumo ?
“ Ndandidinwa .
Ukufunda nokusebenza kuyadinisa . ”
Ngoko , akumangalisi ukuba amanqaku afunyanwa ngabafundi abaninzi esihla emva kokuqalisa ukusebenza .
Abanye bade bangaphumeleli .
“ Kwafuneka ndiye kwizifundo ezibakho ngexesha lasehlotyeni , ” ukhumbula oko uAnthony , owatshonayo ngoxa wayesebenza kumzi - mveliso ukuphuma kwesikolo .
Noko ke , uAnthony waqhubeka esebenza ukutyhubela ihlobo .
Waba yintoni umphumo ?
“ Ndatshona kwakhona kwisikolo sasehlotyeni yaye kwafuneka ndiliphinde elo banga . ”
Enyanisweni , abanye abafundi abakrelekrele baba nako ukufumana amanqaku amahle .
UMichelé ukhumbula oku : “ Bendiye ndiphulaphule nje kumfundisi - ntsapho , ndinqakule oko akuthethayo , ndize ndiphumelele .
Akuzange kufuneke ndifundisise . ”
Noko ke , kukho umahluko omkhulu phakathi kokuphumelela nje esikolweni nokumilisela ingqalelo ekufundeni kokwenene . ​ —⁠ Thelekisa eyoku -⁠ 1 kuTimoti 4 :⁠ 15 .
Ngoko ukuba ucinga ngokuqeshwa , zibuze oku : ‘ Ngaba ndiya kukwazi ukunikela ingqalelo efanelekileyo emsebenzini wesikolo owenzelwa ekhaya ?
Ngaba ndiya kukwazi ukuphumla nokulala ngokwaneleyo ? ’
Okuninzi kuya kuxhomekeka kuhlobo lomsebenzi nakucwangciso lwakho .
Kodwa ukuba umsebenzi uphazamisa imfundo yakho , ngaba ngokwenene uxabisekile ?
Umsebenzi Nentsapho Yakowenu
Okunye emakuxhalatyelwe ngumphumo ukusebenza okusenokuba nawo kulwalamano lwakho namalungu entsapho .
Abaphandi uLaurence Steinberg noEllen Greenberger bathi : “ Uhlolisiso lwethu lubonisa . . . ukuba abafikisa ebuntwini abasebenzayo bachitha ixesha elincinane kwizinto zentsapho kunoontanga babo abangasebenziyo . ”
Ngokomzekelo , “ abaselula abaninzi abasebenzayo bathi batya isidlo sangokuhlwa nentsapho yabo manqaphanqapha ( ngaloo ndlela bephulukana nelinye lamaxesha ambalwa emini ekuthi ebudeni bawo abazali nabantwana babe nokufumanisa okwenzekileyo kwizinto ebebezenza abanye ) . ”
Amaxesha okutya ayeyinxalenye ebalulekileyo yobomi bentsapho kumaxesha okubhalwa kweBhayibhile yaye asaqhubeka enganjalo phakathi kwabantu bakaThixo namhlanje .
( Thelekisa IMizekeliso 15 : ​ 17 . )
Phakathi kwamaNgqina kaYehova , iintsapho ezininzi zisebenzisa isidlo sakusasa okanye sangokuhlwa njengethuba lokuxubusha ngemibandela engokomoya .
Ngaba umsebenzi wempangelo wasemva kwesikolo uya kukuthintela ekuthabatheni inxaxheba ?
Abaselula abasebenzayo basekwanokuqalisa ukuvakalelwa kukuba abasaxhomekekanga nje kwaphela kubazali babo .
Abanye bade baqiqe ngelithi ekubeni benemali eyeyabo , abakho phantsi kwegunya elipheleleyo labazali babo .
Noko ke , itsheki yomvuzo ayikukhululi kwimfanelo yakho engokweZibhalo ‘ yokuva uqeqesho lukayihlo ’ okanye yokuthobela ‘ umyalelo kanyoko . ’
Ngokomzekelo , abazali bakho banelungelo lokugqiba ngobungakanani bemali oyibileleyo efanele iye kwiinkcitho zentsapho .
Ngapha koko , phantse yonke imali yabo yenza njalo .
Ukuba ugqiba kwelokuba usebenze , kutheni ungabonakalisi ukukhula kwakho nomdla wakho kwimpilo - ntle yentsapho ngokubuza abazali bakho ngemali onokuyinikela kwimali yentsapho ?
Umsebenzi Wakho Nobumoya Bakho
Eyona nto ibalulekileyo omele uyiqwalasele kunazo zonke ngumphumo ukusebenza okusenokuba nawo kubumoya bakho .
USteinberg noGreenberger bathi ukuchanabeka kwindawo yomsebenzi kudla ngokuphumela kwiindlela ezithile ‘ zesimilo esinxaxhileyo ’ solutsha , njengokuba emsebenzini okanye ukuqhatha esikolweni .
Olunye ulutsha lude lunikezele kwingcinezelo yoontanga luze lunike abahlobo izaphulelo ezingavunyelwanga ​ —⁠ okanye lude lubabele izinto .
Iingcinezelo zomsebenzi ( nokusoloko unemali ekufutshane ) ziye zakhokelela ulutsha oluninzi ekusebenziseni iziselo ezinxilisayo nasekusebenziseni kakubi iziyobisi .
Enyanisweni , ekubeni unemigaqo yobuKristu , ubungayi kuze ucinge nokucinga ngokwenza izinto ezinjalo .
Noko ke , ukusebenza kunokumchanaba oselula “ kunxulumano olubi ” ukusa kwinqanaba elikhulu .
Ngaba ukulungele ukusingatha ingcinezelo enjalo ?
Ngoxa usesikolweni , ngaba uye ‘ wahamba ngobulumko ngakwabo bangaphandle ’ ngokuphepha unxulumano olonakalisayo ?
Ukuba uye wabonakalisa ubuthathaka obuthile kule nkalo , ngaba ukulungele ngokwenene ukujamelana neengcinezelo ezinkulu ngakumbi zendawo yempangelo ?
Ucwangciso lomsebenzi oludinisayo lusekwanokwenza kube nzima ngawe ukulandela inkqubo emiselweyo yobuKristu yeentlanganiso , isifundo seBhayibhile sobuqu , nokuba nenxaxheba kubulungiseleli bamaKristu .
UMichelé uthi : “ Ndiye ndaphoswa ziintlanganiso ngenxa yokuba ndandidinwa emva kosuku lwesikolo nomsebenzi . ”
Ngaloo ndlela isigqibo sokufumana umsetyenzana wempangelo emva kwesikolo sesibalulekileyo .
Bonke oothunywashe ababandakanyekileyo bamele baqwalaselwe ngenyameko .
Thetha ngemibandela nabazali bakho okanye nomKristu okhulileyo .
Ukuba umsebenzi ugqalwa uyimfuneko , zama ngamandla ukugcina ulungelelwano lwakho .
Yenza ucwangciso olukuvumelayo ukuba unikele ingqalelo eyaneleyo kwimfundo yakho nakwinkqubela yakho engokomoya .
Ukuba oko akunakwenzeka , cinga ngezinye iindlela zokwamkela imali .
Mhlawumbi kukho imisebenzi emikhulu yasendlwini abazali bakho abaya kukulungela ukukuhlawula ngokuyenza .
Olunye ulutsha luqalisa amashishini amancinane , anjengokucheba ingca okanye ukugcina abantwana , aluvumelayo ukuba lwamkele imali ngethuba lalo .
Kodwa kuthekani ngolutsha olukumazwe ahlwempuzeke ngakumbi olungenakwenza ngakumbi kodwa olumele lusebenze ?
Inqaku elizayo liza kuxubusha ngemeko yalo .
