Ukungakholelwa kubukho bukaThixo kwakuyinto eyayishunyayelwa ngokukhutheleyo , yaye izindlu ezithile zabefundisi nezecawa zaguqulelwa ekubeni ziimyuziyam zabo bangakholelwayo kubukho bukaThixo , njengaleyo ityelelwe gqitha ngabakhenkethi eLeningrad .
Nabaphi na abefundisi ababeqhubeka besebenza babesiba zizicaka zikarhulumente walapho .
Ekubeni zonke iindawo zonqulo , njengezindlu zoonongendi , izindlu zeecawa nezindlu zecawa zamaSilamsi , zavalwa ngokusemthethweni ngowe - 1967 , iAlbania yade yabizwa liZiko Likanomathotholo iTirana ‘ njengelizwana lokuqala ehlabathini labantu abangakholelwayo kubukho bukaThixo . ’
Ngoku , ekubeni kuye kwakho inkululeko kulo lonke elaseMpuma Yurophu ngokungathi kukudubula kweentyatyambo entwasahlobo , yintoni eyenzekayo elunqulweni ?
Kunjengokuba umbhali waseFransi uJean - François Kahn wabhala esithi : “ Unqulo obeluthintelwe ziingcinezelo ngoku lunokubambisana nesizwe ebesicinezelekile .
Oku kusandul ’ ukwenzeka eIran .
Kuyenzeka khona ngoku eAzerbaijan yaseRashiya .
Kwixesha elizayo isenokunwenwela kulo lonke elaseRashiya njengomlilo wedobo . ”
Kwanangoku ezinye iicawa zizimanyanisa neengcamango nezilangazelelo zobuhlanga yaye ziphambili kwiimvukelo zezobupolitika , zizingcwalisa ngokubakho kwabefundisi bazo bamaKatolika nabobuOthodoki nabamaLuthere .
Ngoko ke unqulo luqhuba njani kule mekobume intsha yolawulo - melo ?
