Ingxelo engeCawa yobuOthodoki yaseRomania ithi : “ UBhishophu Omkhulu kunye neqela loobhishophu abaye basebenzisana nomkhosi [ kaCeauşescu ] baye banyanzelwa ukuba barhoxe .
