Iinguqulelo EAlbania
Ngokutsho kweengxelo zamaphephandaba , ngokuthe ngcembe kwenzeka iinguqulelo ezothusayo eAlbania , ilizwana elineentaba nelinabemi abazizigidi ezithathu ezinesiqingatha , abahlala kwindawo efihlakeleyo kuNxweme lweAdriatic phakathi kweYugoslavia neGrisi .
Iphephandaba laseJamani iDie Welt lanikela ingxelo ethi : “ EAlbania , intsika yokugqibela yohlobo oludala lobukomanisi eYurophu , abantu baqalise ukuvota ngeenyawo zabo ” ngokubalekela kubameli bamazwe aseNtshona , apho bathi bavunyelwe ukuba bafudukele eItali , eJamani nakwamanye amazwe .
Le ngxelo ihlabela mgama ize ithi : “ NgoMeyi 1990 abemi baseAlbania bathenjiswa ngokunikwa iincwadi zokundwendwela nokupheliswa kwemithetho ethintela imibandela yonqulo . ”
( Oku kucatshulwe kwiThe German Tribune , kaJulayi 15 , 1990 ) Unjingalwazi kwizifundo zembali uDenis R .
Janz wabhala esithi : “ Umzamo othabathe ixesha elide nonzima wokuphelisa lonke unqulo uye wabekelwa ecaleni . ”
