AmaNgqina KaYehova EMpuma Yurophu
NGONOVEMBA 1989 , xa uDonga lwaseBerlin lwadilikayo , iAsiaweek yathi “ malunga nezigidi ezibini zabemi baseMpuma Jamani bathontelana ukungena kwicala elingasentshona lelizwe labo elahlulahluliweyo kwiintsuku ezimbini emva kokuvulwa kwemida yaseMpuma Berlin . ”
Babeyokwenza ntoni ?
Eyona nto yayingamandla , babeye kuthenga .
Abanye babeye kubuka nje yaye bevuyela ukungcamla le nkululeko intsha bayifumeneyo .
Abaninzi bafumana amaNgqina kaYehova ezitratweni zaseBerlin nakwezinye izixeko baza bamkela uncwadi kuwo .
Ukususela ngoko , bambi baye babhalela kwiofisi yesebe yeWatch Tower Society eseSelters , kufuphi naseFrankfurt am Main , bebonakalisa intsabelo emangalisayo .
Enye ileta yavakalisa oku : “ Xa ndandityelele eNtshona Berlin okokuqala ebomini bam , ndafumana inkupho yeMboniselo njengesipho esivela kumaNgqina kaYehova endadibana nawo esitratweni .
Ukususela ngoko , ndiye ndaqalisa ukuyijonga iBhayibhile kwakhona , yaye nakubeni ndineengxaki ezininzi gqitha , kwakhona kukho umntu ondinik ’ ithemba novuyo ebomini .
Ndingakuvuyela gqitha ukuba ndinokufunda incwadi ethi Ubutsha Bakho ​ —⁠ Ukufumana Okona Kulungileyo Kubo .
Bendingakuvuyela nokuqhagamshelana namaNgqina kaYehova . ”
Olunye undwendwe lwabhala lusithi : “ Xa ndandiphuma kwitonela eliya kwisikhululo esikhulu saseNuremberg , inenekazi elithile landinika umbhalo kaVukani !
noweMboniselo .
Ndandichwayite gqitha ngoxa ndandizifunda .
Kangangeentsuku ezithile ndiye ndayisebenzisa iBhayibhile kwakhona . ”
Kwaqhutywa iindibano zamaNgqina kaYehova kwizixeko ezikhulu kulo lonke elaseMpuma Yurophu ebudeni bexesha lehlobo ngowe - 1990 .
IBala lemidlalo iOlympia elaliseNtshona Berlin ngaphambili laba yindawo eyaqhutyelwa kuyo enye indibano awayeye kuyo amaNgqina avela kumazwe ngamazwe , kuquka nawasempuma Jamani .
Kuqikelelwa ukuba kwangama - 44 532 awayekho , anokuba ngama - 30 000 ayevela empuma Jamani .
Iphephandaba iBerliner Morgenpost lanikela ingxelo yokuba amaNgqina amatsha ali - 1 017 abhaptizwa kumadama okuqubha aseOlympia , entywiliselwa ngokupheleleyo emanzini , inkqubo “ ababambelela kuyo abo bantywiliselwayo njengaleyo yamaKristu amandulo . ”
Izinto ziguquke njani empuma Jamani ?
NgoMatshi 1990 amaphephandaba aseMpuma Jamani avakalisa ukuba amaNgqina kaYehova aye amkelwa ngokusemthethweni .
Phantsi komxholo othi : “ Amkelekile Ngokwasemthethweni Kwakhona AmaNgqina KaYehova , ” iphephandaba laseMpuma Jamani iMitteldeutsche Zeitung lathi : “ NgoMatshi 14 saphela isibhengezo sokuvalwa umlomo kwawo esithabathe iminyaka engamashumi amane sikho .
Ngolu suku abameli abangamaNgqina kaYehova aseJamani bakwazi ukuphuma kwisakhiwo esineZiko likaSosiba kaRhulumente kwiMicimbi Engonqulo weR [ iphabliki ] Y [ olawulo - melo ] yaseJ [ amani ] ( eMpuma Jamani ) bephethe uxwebhu olungokwasemthethweni oluwavumelayo kwakhona ukuba angaphinda aluqhelisele ngokukhululekileyo unqulo lwawo eMpuma Jamani . ”
Ileta eyafunyanwa kwintwasahlobo ephelileyo ivela kwiNgqina elithile laseLeipzig ithi : “ Kwiveki enye edluleyo besisaodola ngokufihlakeleyo ukudla kokomoya ngezixa ezincinane .
Ngoku [ ngoMatshi 14 , 1990 ] siye samkelwa ngokusemthethweni !
Kungekudala siza kube sisothula ilori enkulu eneetoni ezine zoncwadi ! ”
Enyanisweni , ilori yokuqala eyathulwa eMpuma Jamani yayinoncwadi lweBhayibhile oluziitoni ezingama - 25 , yaye kwiinyanga ezimbini , kwathunyelwa ezinye iitoni ezingama - 250 .
Kwakunjalo ke ukulamba okungokomoya kwaloo maNgqina awayehluthwe inkululeko kangangeminyaka engama - 40 !
Xa sikhumbula ukuba ubuNazi ( 1933 - 45 ) nobuKomanisi bazama ukuwubhangisa umsebenzi wamaNgqina eJamani , imisebenzi yawo yenkalipho yethuba elidluleyo neyangoku ibubungqina obucacileyo bengqibelelo yawo nentsikelelo aye wawathululela yona uThixo .
AmaNgqina KaYehova ERashiya
NgoDisemba 1989 , uMikhail Gorbachev waba nentlanganiso noPopu John Paul II eVatican .
Iphephandaba laseRashiya iPravda lanikela ingxelo yokuba uGorbachev wathi ngale ncoko yabo : “ Saba nengxubusho enzulu nenentsingiselo . . . .
Sathetha ngonqulo neenkqubo eziphathelele nalo eYurophu , ehlabathini , naseRashiya . ”
IL’Osservatore Romano , iphephandaba elisemthethweni laseVatican , lanikela ingxelo yokuba uMnu . Gorbachev xa wayethetha nopopu wathi : “ Abantu beenkonzo ezininzi , kuquka amaKristu , amaSilamsi , amaYuda , amaBhuda nabezinye iinkonzo , bakho eRashiya .
Bonke banelungelo lokwanelisa iintswelo zabo zokomoya .
Kungekudala , kwilizwe lethu kuza kumiselwa uMthetho weNkululeko Engokonqulo . ”
Ngokuvumelana nelo lizwi , ngoSeptemba 1990 iqumrhu lowiso - mthetho laseRashiya lamisela umthetho ovumela inkululeko yesazela .
KwiGatya 3 lalo mthetho kwathiwa : “ Ngokuvisisana nelungelo lenkululeko engokonqulo , wonke ummi uzigqibela ngokwakhe imibandela engokonqulo , unelungelo lokuqhelisela naluphi na unqulo njengomntu ngamnye okanye njengeqela okanye ukungaqheliseli naluphi na , ukuvakalisa nokusasaza iinkolelo zakhe ngokuphathelele unqulo . ”
Kukho amawaka amaNgqina kaYehova eRashiya akhangele phambili ekuqheliseleni unqulo ngokukhululekileyo .
( Bona iphepha 30 . ) KwiiNdibano “ Zentetho Enyulu ” zowe - 1990 , kwakukho iindwendwe ezingaphezu kwezili - 17 000 ezivela eRashiya ezazikucwangciso lwesiRashiya eWarsaw ezazimele onke amaNgqina asasazeke kulo lonke elaseRashiya .
Akhangele phambili kumhla ekuya kuba nokwenzeka ukuba abe neendibano eRashiya .
Inkqubela EPoland
AmaNgqina kaYehova amkelwa ngokusemthethweni ePoland ngoMeyi 1989 .
Ukususela ngoko kuye kwasekwa iofisi yesebe , yaye kwakhiwa izakhiwo ezikhulu kufuphi naseWarsaw .
Ngaphambili , amakhulu amaNgqina aselula ebevalelwa entolongweni ngenxa yembambano yobundilele bobuKristu .
Ngoku akhululekile kwinkonzo yezomkhosi nakwisohlwayo ukuba nje avelisa isiqinisekiso esifanelekileyo .
Iindibano ezaqhutyelwa ePoland ngowe - 1989 nangowe - 1990 zibe lolunye ukhuthazo kumaNgqina alapho .
Ingxelo ithi inani lamaNgqina akhutheleyo ePoland liye landa nyanga zonke ebudeni bonyaka ophelileyo , lafikelela kwincopho engaphezu kwama - 97 000 .
Alithandabuzeki elokuba kungekudala iPoland iza kuba lilizwe le - 12 elinamaNgqina angaphezu kwe - 100 000 .
