Inkululeko Engokonqulo ERomania
Avuyiswa gqitha amaNgqina aseRomania kukuva ukuba intlangano yawo iye yamkelwa ngokusemthethweni ngoAprili 1990 . ( Bona ibhokisi , kwiphepha 13 . )
Kungekudala kwalungiselelwa iindibano zesiphaluka kulo lonke elo lizwe , yaye kolunye ungcelele kweza abantu abangaphezu kwama - 44 000 , kanti kwakukho kuphela amaNgqina amalunga ne - 19 000 ngelo xesha .
Ngokuqinisekileyo abantu abaninzi baseRomania bayasabela kwisigidimi soBukumkani .
Iindibano zesithili zowe - 1990 zehlabathi lonke ezinomxholo othi “ Intetho Enyulu ” zaqhutywa kwisixeko saseBrasov nesaseCluj - Napoca .
Ucwangciso lwaqhutywa ngesiRomania nangesiHungary .
Kwakuze abantu abangaphezu kwama - 36 000 , yaye kwabhaptizwa abali - 1 445 .
Ukususela kwinkupho yeMboniselo kaJanuwari 1 , 1991 , isiRomania siza kuqaliswa ukupapashwa ngaxeshanye nesiNgesi yaye ngombala opheleleyo .
KwiBulgaria engekude , apho lugquba khona unqulo lobuOthodoki baseMpuma , amaNgqina awakamkelwa ngokwasemthethweni kodwa aqesha amagumbi athile ukuze aqhubele kuwo iintlanganiso zawo zebandla .
Angaphezu kwamakhulu amabini athi aya eSalonika , eGrisi , kwiNdibano “ Yentetho Enyulu ” ebiqhutywa ngolwimi lwaseBulgaria nangesiGrike .
Iindaba Ezimnandi Ezivela EHungary
UJuni 27 , 1989 , yayilusuku olubalulekileyo kwimbali yamaNgqina aseHungary .
Iphephandaba iMagyar Nemzet lavakalisa oku : “ IOfisi kaRhulumente Engemicimbi yeCawa iye yavakalisa ukuba intlangano yonqulo yamaNgqina kaYehova eHungary , ngokuvumelana nomthetho wenkululeko engokonqulo , igqalwa njengonqulo olwamkelekileyo ngokwasemthethweni . ”
Ezi ndaba zabhengezwa kunomathotholo , nakumabonwakude .
Abemi baseHungary baye beva ukuba ekugqibeleni uye wamkelwa ngokusemthethweni umsebenzi wamaJehova Tanúi ( amaNgqina kaYehova ) .
Ukuze kugutyungelwe imimandla emikhulu yeli lizwe , kuye kwaqhutywa iiNdibano “ Zentetho Enyulu ” ePecs , eMiskolc , eDebrecen naseBudapest .
Abantu abanokuba nama - 2 000 abathetha isiHungary beza besuka eCzechoslovakia naseRashiya .
Ukubethelela ukumanyana kwamaNgqina kaYehova ezizwe ngezizwe , kwakukho iqela leendwendwe ezingama - 700 ezazisuka eFinland .
Lilonke inani labo babekho eHungary lalingama - 21 568 , kuquka neendwendwe ezingaphezu kwezingama - 2 000 ezazisuka eRomania .
Ukususela ngoJanuwari 1990 , amaNgqina aseHungary ebefumana amaphephancwadi awo ngombala opheleleyo ngokuthe rhoqo , eguqulelwe ngaxeshanye nawolwimi lwesiNgesi .
Ayaqhubeka ECzechoslovakia
Kweli lizwe lihle elineentaba namathafa achumayo , amaNgqina kaYehova axakekile enceda abamelwane bawo ukuba bafunde okungakumbi ngeBhayibhile .
Enye ingxelo engomsebenzi wawo ithi : “ Umsebenzi wenziwa ngokuphandle , yaye kuqhutywa iintlanganiso ezinkulu . ”
Emva kweenguqulelo eziphawulekayo ezenzeke eMpuma Yurophu ngasekupheleni kowe - 1989 , amaNgqina aseCzechoslovakia athabatha amanyathelo ngokukhawuleza aza alungiselela ungcelele lweendibano zesiphaluka ebudeni benyanga ka - Aprili ukusa kwekaJuni 1990 .
Ngenxa yoku , okwesihlandlo sokuqala , kwabakho ingxelo entle engamaNgqina kumaphephandaba .
Sithetha nje , kukho amaNgqina angaphezu kwama - 21 000 eCzechoslovakia , yaye ngowe - 1990 abantu ababezile kwiSikhumbuzo sokufa kukaKristu babengama - 40 295 .
Ngaphezu kwesiqingatha samabandla sesineendawo ezithile eziqeshwayo apho anokuqhubela khona iintlanganiso zawo , yaye amabandla ali - 12 ade aneeHolo zawo zoBukumkani .
NgoAgasti 1990 kwaqhutywa indibano ePrague , bebonke abantu ababekho babengama - 23 876 , yaye kwabhaptizwa abali - 1 824 .
Ukuwenza amabala emidlalo afanelekele iindibano , amaNgqina angaphezu kwangama - 9 500 ngokuzithandela achitha iiyure ezingaphezu kwezingama - 58 000 ekucoceni nasekupeyinteni .
Ummeli weziko likamabonwakude eCzechoslovakia wathi : “ Siye satyelela iimbutho ezininzi , kodwa siyayincoma indlela enilungelelaniswe ngayo kweli bala lemidlalo .
Kunzima ukuba sikholelwe kwelokuba niyaqala ukulungiselela indibano elolu hlobo . ”
Olunye undwendwe lwathi : “ Ndiyayithanda imekobume engokomoya , imvisiswano nothando oluphakathi kwenu bazalwana .
Bendize njengomhlobo ; ndihamba ndingongakumbi . ”
Amaphephancwadi IMboniselo noVukani !
apapashwa ngombala opheleleyo ngolwimi lwesiCzech nolwesiSlovak , yaye IMboniselo ifumaneka ngaxeshanye nesiNgesi kwezi lwimi zombini .
Xa sicinga ngeemeko ebezicinezela kunyaka nje omnye odluleyo , ezi ziinguqulelo ezimangalisayo .
Amathemba Ekamva
Ngawaphi amathemba akhoyo kumaNgqina angokushumayela kumazwe apho esi sizukulwana sangoku siye sakhula singakholelwa kubukho bukaThixo ?
Ingxelo ichaza oku : “ Kukho ubumnyama obugqithiseleyo ngokuphathelele iBhayibhile noThixo .
Noko ke , eyona nto inik ’ ithemba yeyokuba abantu abadidekanga ziimfundiso zobuxoki ezimele zingamkelwa .
Kuyabonakala ukuba ukuvuna kona kuninzi . ”
Ngoko , sisiphi isigidimi esivela eBhayibhileni amaNgqina kaYehova asidlulisela kubantu baseMpuma Yurophu ?
