Inkoliso yabantu , kungakhathaliseki ukuba banayiphi na imvelaphi yonqulo okanye yobupolitika , bebeya kufuna ukuphila kwihlabathi eliseluxolweni nelinendyebo .
Bebeya kulivuyela ihlabathi elinobulungisa obugqibeleleyo nemvisiswano , apho kungekho konakala ; apho kungasayi kubakho omnye umthetho wabo bemi kakuhle kuze kubekho omnye wabangamahlwempu .
Yaye ngokungathandabuzekiyo , ubuya kuthanda ukuba abantwana bakho babe nentabalala yokutya , ikhaya elihle nemfundo esemgangathweni .
Ngamanye amazwi , ubuya kufuna ukuqinisekisa ukuba wena nenzala yakho ninekamva elizinzileyo .
Yaye ukuba ubunikwe ithuba , ubuya kukhetha impilo efezekileyo nokuphila ixesha elaneleyo ukuze uzalisekise iminqweno namabhongo akho afanelekileyo , kwanokunandipha ubomi obungunaphakade kumhlaba oseluxolweni noyiparadisi .
Kukonke oku akulophupha nje elingenakuzalisekiswa .
Kusisigidimi seBhayibhile amaNgqina kaYehova asishumayela kumhlaba wonke , kuquka nakumazwe aseMpuma Yurophu .
Ithemba LeBhayibhile Eliqinisekileyo Ngekamva
Iziprofeto zeBhayibhile ezinokuthenjwa nezabhalwa kwiinkulungwane ezininzi ezadlulayo zaxela kusengaphambili iziganeko ezaziya kwenzeka kule nkulungwane yethu yama - 20 , ‘ iimfazwe zethu namarhe eemfazwe ’ ; ‘ iinyikima zethu zomhlaba nokunqongophala kokutya kwiindawo ngeendawo ’ ; ‘ ukuxinezeleka kweentlanga zethu , zithingaza , ngoxa abantu baya kube besifa kukoyika izinto ezilizelayo elimiweyo ’ ; ‘ ukuwonakalisa nokuwungcolisa kwethu umhlaba . ’ ​ —⁠ Luka 21 : ​ 10 - 33 ; ISityhilelo 11 :⁠ 18 .
Kanti , zonke ezi ziganeko nezinye ezingakumbi zingumqondiso oqinisekileyo wokuba ihlabathi elitsha elithenjiswe nguThixo likufuphi .
Oku kuquka “ elitsha izulu , nomtsha umhlaba , ” okuthetha ukuthi , ulawulo olutsha lomhlaba , urhulumente wasezulwini , nebutho lomhlaba elihlaziyiweyo ‘ apho kumi ubulungisa . ’
Oku kuthetha ihlabathi elitsha ‘ ekungasayi kubakho ziintlungu , kufa nasijwili kulo . ’ ​ —⁠ Isaya 65 : ​ 17 - 25 ; 2 Petros 3 : 13 ; ISityhilelo 21 : ​ 1 -⁠ 4 .
Ngokucacileyo , akukho nkqubo yabupolitika , kungakhathaliseki ukuba inyaniseke yaye inenyameko kangakanani na , inokuphumeza inkqubo enjalo .
Kuphela yiNkosi enguMongami wendalo iphela , uYehova uThixo , onomdla nonamandla okuphumeza oku .
Ngenxa yoko uNyana wakhe , uKristu Yesu , wafundisa abalandeli bakhe ukuthandaza esithi : “ Bawo wethu osemazulwini , malingcwaliswe igama lakho .
Mabufike ubukumkani bakho .
Makwenziwe ukuthanda kwakho nasemhlabeni , njengokuba kusenziwa emazulwini . ” ​ —⁠ Mateyu 6 : ​ 9 , 10 .
Ukuthanda kukaThixo kukuba umhlaba ube yeyona ndawo intle kwindalo iphela , ekuhleli kuyo intsapho yabantu ethanda uxolo .
Kungekudala uThixo uza kuthabath ’ unyawo lokuzisa oko .
Esi iya kuba sisenzo sokucoca asuse emhlabeni ukungcola nabo bawungcolisayo .
Lonke ungcoliseko lomoya , enoba lolubonakalayo okanye lungokwemilinganiselo yokuziphatha , luya kupheliswa emhlabeni .
Ngoobani abaya kusala ?
UYesu wathi : “ Banoyolo abanobulali ; ngokuba umhlaba baya kuwudla ilifa bona . ” ​ —⁠ Mateyu 5 :⁠ 5 ; ISityhilelo 16 : ​ 14 -⁠ 16 .
Ngaba uyafuna ukuba phakathi kwabo banobulali nabaya kuzuza intsikelelo kaThixo ?
Ngoko qhagamshelana namaNgqina kaYehova asekuhlaleni uze ucele isifundo seBhayibhile sesisa , nto leyo engakubopheleli nganto .
Ziqinisekisele ngokwakho oko ‘ kukuko ukuthanda kukaThixo okulungileyo , okukholekileyo , okuzalisekileyo . ’
Uze emva koko ukwenze . ​ —⁠ Roma 12 :⁠ 2 .
