Kumazwe aseNtshona ulutsha olukwintanga yesikolo lunokusoloko lujonge phambili kwimpela - veki njengexesha lokonwaba nelokuzihlaziya .
Kodwa kwiindawo ezininzi zehlabathi , iimpela - veki asingomathuba okuzihlaziya .
Ngokomzekelo , kwimimandla yasemaphandleni eAfrika , ulutsha ludla ngokuchitha iimpela - veki luncedisa abazali balo emasimini , lubuyisa elinye lexesha elilahleke ebudeni beveki ngenxa yesikolo .
Yaye kumaNgqina kaYehova , ulutsha lunembopheleleko eyongezelelekileyo yokuba nenxaxheba kumsebenzi wokushumayela kwindlu ngendlu nokuya kwiintlanganiso zamaKristu . ​ —⁠ Hebhere 10 : ​ 23 -⁠ 25 .
Ngoko ke , kusenokubonakala kungenakwenzeka ukuba ulutsha lwaseAfrika beluya kufuna ukuthabatha uxanduva olongezelelekileyo lomsebenzi wengqesho .
Kodwa ulutsha oluninzi olunjalo luyasebenza yaye ngeendlela ezahlukeneyo : lulima izitiya zalo luze luthengise imveliso , lwaluke umsingizane luze lwenze iminqwazi , okanye iibhaskithi ukuze luzithengise kwindawo yentengiso .
Sekunjalo olunye luyaloba , luthengise amaphephandaba , luze luvune okanye luthengise iziqhamo .
Noko ke , kutheni olu lutsha lusenza umsebenzi wengqesho ?
Ngaba oku ngokuyimfuneko kuthetha ukuba ufanele wenze okufanayo ?
Isizathu Sokuba Lusebenze
Olunye ulutsha phantse ukuba lunyanzelekile ngokupheleleyo ukuba lusebenze ngenxa yeemeko ezingaphaya kwamandla alo , ezinjengokufa komzali .
( Oku kunokushiya ulutsha lungenabani wokuluxhasa kwimfundo yalo . )
Kwelinye icala , olunye ulutsha luyasebenza ukuze lungaxhomekeki kubazali balo .
Qwalasela uKofi , umfana waseGhana .
Ngoxa wayesesikolweni sobugcisa , wasebenza njengomqeshwa kwifama ethile iiyure ezimbini suku ngalunye emva kokuphuma kwesikolo .
