Ukwavuma ukuba kunemvakalelo yolwaneliseko ukukwazi ukuzithengela izinto .
Ukunceda abazali bakabani ngokwemali xa kukho imfuneko yokwenene kusenokuba yindlela yokunikela imbeko ebafaneleyo .
Noko ke , kwangaxeshanye , akukho nto ngokuyimfuneko ephosakeleyo ekusebenzeni ukuze ubani abe nemali ayichithela kwizinto zakhe .
Ukuba nomsebenzi kusekwanokwenza okuninzi ukufaka engqondweni yolutsha imvakalelo yembopheleleko .
Kunokunceda ulutsha lube nobuchule obunokuthi kamva busetyenziswe ekuxhaseni intsapho .
Ngokomzekelo , uYesu Kristu ngokucacileyo wafunda ukuchwela ngokusebenza noyise owayengumgcini wakhe njengoselula .
Sekunjalo , ‘ ixesha leli hlabathi lifinyele , ’ yaye oselula olumkileyo uyaqinisekisa ukuba ixesha lakhe ulisebenzisa ngokuyingenelo .
Ngoko ngaphambi kokwenza umsebenzi othile , ufanele uzihlolisise zonke iimeko ezibandakanyekileyo ​ —⁠ kuquka iintshukumisa zakho .
Ukubala Iindleko
Eminye imibuzo osenokuyiqwalasela yile : Ngaba abazali bam baluswele ngokwenene okanye bade balufune uncedo lwam olungokwemali ?
Okanye ngaba bakulungele ukwaneliswa kokuncinane ukuze ndikwazi ukwenza umsebenzi wesikolo owenzelwa ekhaya ndize ndikhule ngokomoya ?
Ngaba ndiyiswele ngokwenene imali esecaleni , okanye ngaba ndilandela “ inkanuko yenyama , nenkanuko yamehlo , noqhankqalazo lobu bomi ” ? ​ —⁠ 1 Yohane 2 :⁠ 16 .
Isilumko uSolomon saphawula oku : “ Ndayiqonda ke mna yonke imigudu , nayo yonke impumelelo yomsebenzi , ukuba ingumona wokwanyelana .
Kwanaloo nto ingamampunge , nokusukelana nomoya . . . .
Kulungile ukuzalisa sandla sinye ngokuphumla , kunokuzalisa zozibini izandla ngemigudu nokusukelana nomoya . ” ​ —⁠ INtshumayeli 4 : ​ 4 -⁠ 6 .
Enye imeko emayiqwalaselwe ibiya kuba ngumphumo ukusebenza okusenokuba nawo ekuhambeni kwakho isikolo .
UKofi , obekhankanywe ngaphambili , ukhumbula oku : “ Ngonyaka wam wokuqala kwisikolo sobugcisa xa ndandingenzi msebenzi wengqesho , indlela endandiqhuba ngayo kwizifundo zam yayibalasele .
Kwandula ke kwangunyaka wesibini endaqalisa ngawo umsebenzi wengqesho , yaye amanqaku endandiwafumana aqalisa ukuhla .
Sekunjalo ndakwazi ukuba ngaphezu komlinganiselo wamanqaku amiselweyo , kodwa kwakudinisa kakhulu . ”
Okubangel ’ umdla kukuba , uphengululo olwenziwa eUnited States lwafumanisa ukuba “ ukusebenza kukhokelela ekuhleni komgangatho ubani aqhuba ngawo esikolweni yaye kunciphisa ukubandakanyeka kukabani kwimicimbi yesikolo ngokomntu ofikelela kubuntu obukhulu . ”
Ngaba uyamkhumbula umntakwabo Kofi uMoses , owayenomsebenzi wokufundisa abantwana abangekayi esikolweni ?
Uvuma oku : “ Ngaphandle kokuba ubani ungolumke kakhulu , unokuqalisa ukuthabatha abafundi abaninzi kunabo banokufundiswa ngexesha elilinganiselweyo elifumanekayo . ”
UMawuli , enye indoda yaseAfrika , wasebenza ixesha elincinane njengomlobi .
Uthi : “ Kwakusiba sisilingo kakhulu ukubambisa kakhulu elunxwemeni .
Kwakuqhubela ekubeni ushiye iincwadi uhambe uze uzenzele imali engakumbi .
Amakhwenkwe amaninzi elalini enza oko aza asiyeka isikolo . ”
