Sekunjalo , emva kokuhlolisisa zonke iimeko , wena nabazali bakho nisenokugqiba ekubeni ukusebenza kumsebenzi wohlobo oluthile kuya kuba neengenelo .
Unokulisebenzisa ngokuyingenelo njani eli thuba ?
Ukuziqeqesha kuyimfuneko .
Umpostile uPawulos wathetha ngemigudu yakhe , esithi : “ Ndisuka ndiwuqobe umzimba wam , ndiwuxinzelele phantsi . ”
Kuya kufuna ukuziqeqesha ngawe ukonga ​ —⁠ yaye kungekhona ukuyichitha⁠ — ​ imali oyifumanayo .
Kwakhona kuya kufuna ukuziqeqesha ngawe ukusebenzisa ngokufanelekileyo ixesha lakho eliseleyo .
Kambe ke , ukuzihlaziya nokuphumla okwaneleyo kunendawo yako yaye kunokwandisa umsebenzi onemveliso .
Kodwa lumkela ukuba izinto zokuzonwabisa nokuzihlaziya azithathi xesha lomsebenzi wesikolo owenziwa ekhaya nelezinto zokomoya .
Ngoko ke kuya kufuneka wenze ucwangciso lokwenene lwamathuba okufundisisa ​ —⁠ yaye unamathele kulo .
Ngokomzekelo , kusenokulunga ngakumbi ukuqalisa umsebenzi wakho wesikolo ngokukhawuleza kangangoko kunokwenzeka ekufikeni ekhaya ukuvela emsebenzini , ungalindi de kube semva kwesidlo sangokuhlwa ngexesha osenokuziva usozela .
Abanye banyula ukuya kulala kwangoko baze banyamekele izifundo zabo kuqala ekuseni .
Nokuba iyintoni na imeko , yenza amathuba akho okufundisisa abe nemveliso kangangoko kunokwenzeka .
Kuphephe ukudlala umculo okanye ukuzifica kwezinye izinto eziphazamisayo .
Umsebenzi wakho wesikolo owenzela ekhaya usekwanokuba lula ukuba unikela ingqalelo kwindlela ophulaphula ngayo kwigumbi lokufundela , uthabatha amanqaku eengongoma eziyintloko naweenkcukacha ezixhasayo . ​ —⁠ Thelekisa uLuka 8 :⁠ 18 .
Noko ke , okona kubaluleke kuzo zonke ziintswelo zokomoya .
Ukuze ezi zaneliswe , ukwamele ubekele ecaleni ixesha lesifundo seBhayibhile sobuqu , leentlanganiso zamaKristu nelokuba nesabelo kubulungiseleli basesidlangalaleni .
Kuyinyaniso ukuba , ukusebenza nokufunda kuluxanduva .
Kodwa ukuba umele uzenze zombini , izinto zokomoya mazize kuqala .
Qhubeka uthandaza kuYehova uThixo ukuba akuncede ugcine ulungelelwano lobumoya bakho .
Ukuba kwenziwe isigqibo sokuba kusetyenzwe , ukongezelela ekufundeni , yena unokukomeleza ukuba umelane neengcinezelo zemeko . ​ —⁠ Isaya 40 : ​ 29 -⁠ 31 .
