Umntu Ungumqobo
Umqobo omkhulu othintela ukubakho koxolo olunjalo ngumntu ngokwakhe .
Umzekeliso wamandulo uthi : ‘ Umntu uye wagunyazela umntu kwaba kubi kuye . ’
Yaye imbali yomntu yokwenzakalisa abanye abantu ibonakala kwimpatho aphatha ngayo izilwanyana .
Ngokomzekelo , amarhamncwa asendle aliqela ayebanjwa aze alwiswe kumabala emidlalo kwiRoma yamandulo .
Ngowe - 106 C.E . , umlawuli waseRoma uTrajan kuthiwa wenza imidlalo ekwathi kuyo kwabulawa amadoda awayesilwa angama - 10 000 namarhamncwa angama - 11 000 ukuze kwaneliswe ukunxanelwa igazi kwababukeli abanogonyamelo .
Liyinyaniso elokuba , uhlobo olunjalo lokuzonwabisa aluyonto ixhaphakileyo namhlanje .
Kodwa ukwanda kwenani leendidi zezilwanyana eziphelileyo emhlabeni nezisengozini yokuphela kunikela ubungqina bokuba kukho okuthile okuphosakeleyo kwindlela umntu aziphatha ngayo izidalwa zasendle .
Njengoko amanani abantu esanda , iindawo zokuhlala izilwanyana ziyancipha .
Yaye ngenxa yokubawa kwabantu , iimfele , iimpondo , namabamba ezilwanyana ezinqabileyo afunwa ngokubanzi .
Zimbi iingcali zoyikela ukuba ekugqibeleni ekuphela kwezilwanyana ezininzi eziya kufumaneka iya kuba zezo zikwiindawo zokugcinwa kwezilwanyana .
Izilwanyana Ezidla Abantu
Kusenokubonakala ngathi omnye umqobo othintela ukubakho koxolo ngamarhamncwa athile asendle .
EAfrika naseAsiya , akunto ingaqhelekanga ukufunda iingxelo zokuba amarhamncwa asendle aye ahlasela aza abulala abantu .
IThe Guinness Book of Animal Facts and Feats ithi amarhamncwa akuhlobo lweekati “ kusenokwenzeka ukuba abangela ukufa kwabantu abamalunga ne - 1000 nyaka ngamnye . ”
EIndiya kuphela , izingwe zibulala abantu abangaphezu kwama - 50 nyaka ngamnye .
Wambi amahlosi kwelo lizwe aye azizidla - bantu .
Kwincwadi yakhe ethi Dangerous to Man , uRoger Caras ucacisa ukuba maxa wambi amahlosi aba zizidla - bantu emva kokudla inyama ebolileyo yezidumbu zabantu xa bekukho ubhubhani wesifo .
Ucacisa athi , ngokufuthi oobhubhani abanjalo baye “ balandelwa ziinyanga zoloyiko njengoko amahlosi esanelisa uthando lwawo ngencasa asandul ’ ukuyiva yenyama yomntu aze aqalise ukubulala . ”
Kodwa lo kaCaras uphawula ukuba oobhubhani bezifo ababangeli zonke iintlaselo zamahlosi .
Omnye unobangela woku kukuvuseleleka kwesilwanyana , ingakumbi xa sikufutshane nabantwana .
Ebudeni beminyaka yee - 1918 - 26 , ihlosi elinye eIndiya labulala abantu abali - 125 , ngokutsho kwengxelo kaColonel J .
Corbett kwincwadi yakhe ethi The Man - Eating Leopard of Rudraprayag .
Kumashumi eminyaka kamva , amahlosi azizidla - bantu abulala ubuncinane abantu abangama - 82 kwisithili saseBhagalpur .
Umgcini - zilwanyana eTanganyika ( ngoku eyinxalenye yeTanzania ) wabalisa indlela awachitha ngayo iinyanga ezintlanu ngowe - 1950 ezama ngokungenampumelelo ukudubula ihlosi elisisidla - bantu elalinxunguphalise abantu kummandla ongqonge ilali yaseRuponda .
Ekugqibeleni , emva kokubulala abantwana abali - 18 , labanjiswa ngummi waloo dolophana yaseAfrika .
Elinye ihlosi labulala abafazi nabantwana abangama - 26 kwidolophana yaseMasaguru .
Kukwakho ke nengonyama yaseAfrika .
Xa ithe yaqalisa ukudla abantu , ngokufuthi amaxhoba iba ngamadoda akhulileyo .
UC .
Ionides kwincwadi yakhe ethi Mambas and Man - Eaters , ubhala athi , “ Kwiminyaka engamashumi amabini anesithathu endayichithela kwiSebe Logcino - Zilwanyana , ndadubula iingonyama ezingaphezu kwamashumi amane , inkoliso yazo eyayizizidla - bantu , ngoxa intsalela yayisele iza kuba zizidla - bantu okanye yayigqugqisa imihlambi . ”
Ngokutsho kukaIonides , iingonyama ziba sisisongelo kubantu xa umntu enciphisa ngokungathethekiyo amaxhoba azo .
Uxolo Lomhlaba Wonke Lwaxelwa Kusengaphambili
Phezu kwayo nje le miqobo ethintela ukubakho koxolo phakathi kwabantu namarhamncwa , iBhayibhile ithi : “ Zonke iimvelo zezinto ezizitho zine . . . ziyadanjiswa , kanjalo sezikhe zadanjiswa yimvelo eyiyeyabantu . ” ​ —⁠ Yakobi 3 :⁠ 7 .
IBhayibhile ixela kusengaphambili kuHezekile 34 : ​ 25 isithi : “ [ Mna Thixo ] ndiya kuwenzela umnqophiso woxolo , ndiwaphelise amarhamncwa amabi elizweni , uhlale entlango ukholosile , ulale emahlathini . ”
Ngaba iziprofeto zeBhayibhile ezinjalo ziliphupha nje elingekho gqiqweni ?
Ngaphambi kokuligatya ithemba loxolo lomhlaba wonke phakathi kwabantu namarhamncwa , qwalasela ezinye izinto ezalatha kubunyaniso boko iBhayibhile ikutshoyo .
Kuye kwabhalwa ngeminye imizekelo emangalisayo yemvisiswano phakathi kwabantu abanenkathalo namarhamncwa asenokuba yingozi .
Ngaba Abantu Banokuhlalisana Ngoxolo Namarhamncwa ?
“ Ndavakalelwa ngokungathi ndandisele ndifikile eparadisi ; abantu namarhamncwa bekwimvisiswano yokuthembana . ”
UJoy Adamson wakuchaza ngaloo ndlela oko kwakusenzeka ecaleni koMlambo iUra waseKenya njengoko wayebukele iintlobo ngeentlobo zeentaka nezilwanyana zisiza kusela .
Eyona nto yayinomtsalane koko kwakusenzeka yayisisilwanyana esasibuthume ngokuzolileyo ecaleni kwakhe ​ —⁠ imazi yengonyama ekhulileyo !
Ngaba kwakukho nto ithile ekhethekileyo ngale mazi yengonyama , uElsa , ezithe izigidi zamazi ngokufunda ngaye kwincwadi ethi Born Free , ebhalwe nguJoy Adamson ?
Hayi , wayeyimazi yengonyama eqhelekileyo .
Umahluko yayikukuba wayefunde ukuhlalisana ngoxolo nabantu .
Kamva , xa kwenziwa umfanekiso - bhanyabhanya othi Born Free , iqela leemazi zeengonyama ezenziwe mbuna zasetyenziswa ukuze zidlale indima kaElsa .
Enye yayibizwa ngokuba nguMara .
Wayengathembi kwaphela ekuqaleni , waza wandula wangobanga kakhulu , engabavumeli abahlobo bakhe asandul ’ ukubafumana abangabantu ukuba bamshiye .
Ukuze amthomalalise , umyeni kaJoy , uGeorge Adamson , wagxumeka intente yakhe ecaleni kwendawo awayevalelwa kuyo uMara .
Ekugqibeleni , wayigxumeka intente yakhe ngaphakathi kuloo ndawo wayevalelwa kuyo !
Kwincwadi yakhe ethi Bwana Game , wabhala oku , “ Kangangeenyanga ezintathu ezilandelayo , wayelala ngokuthe rhoqo ngaphakathi [ kwintente yam ] , ngokuqhelekileyo elala phantsi emgangathweni ecaleni kwebhedi yam yaye maxa wambi ebhedini yam . . . .
Akazange andenze ndizive ndingakhuselekanga . ” UMnu .
Adamson wabhala wathi : “ Omnye wemidlalwana yethu esasiyithanda wawukukuba ndilale phantsi emva kwesicithi sengca .
UMara wayeya kwandula achwechwe ngobunono obukhulu , isisu siphantsi emhlabeni kanye njengokuba iingonyama zisenza aze ke enze umtsi okhawuleza ngokombane aze kuwa phezu kwam .
Ngalo lonke ixesha wayezilawula iinzipho zakhe ezoyikekayo yaye akazange andenzakalise . ”
Enye imazi yengonyama eyayidlala indawo kaElsa yayibizwa ngokuba nguGirl .
Xa lo mfanekiso - bhanyabhaya wagqitywayo , uGirl wabuyiselwa endle , apho wathi wadibana nenkunzi waza wazala amathole amabini .
Abahlobo baka - Adamson ababini basifumana isikhundla sakhe .
Lo ka - Adamson ubhala athi : “ Ngeyona ntembelo imangalisayo uGirl wawavumela la madoda mabini , awayezibeke esichengeni esingathethekiyo , ukuba asondele de abe malunga nemitha ukusuka kwindawo awayezalele kuyo . . . isimo sikaGirl sasimangalisa ngokwenene ekubeni [ enye yala madoda ] yayingumntu angamaziyo ngokwentelekiso . ”
UGirl wada wamvumela lo ka - Adamson ukuba awachukumise loo mathole , nangona ezinye iingonyama zagxothwayo .
Ukwenza Mbuna Ingonyama Enoburhalarhume
Iimpawu zeengonyama ziyahlukahlukana .
Ngoxa uJoy Adamson wayekhulisa uElsa , ngezantsi kuMntla Rhodesia ( ngoku oyiZambia ) , umgcini wezilwanyana , uNorman Carr , wayekhulisa amathole amabini aziinkunzi .
Elinye lala mathole , uBig Boy , lalinobuhlobo kakhulu .
Elinye , uLittle Boy , lalibonakala linolunya .
Ethetha ngoLittle Boy , lo kaCarr kwincwadi yakhe ethi Return to the Wild wabhala okulandelayo :
“ Xa uLittle Boy ekule meko , ndichopha ecaleni kwakhe njengoko endigragramela , ndiqiniseke nje ukuba ndikude namathupha akhe atyekele ekuwasebenziseni xa ngoburhalarhume ekukrwempa ngeenzipho ezibukhali ngokweencakuba eziziisentimitha ezintlanu .
Ngomonde ndizama ukumthomalalisa ngokuthetha naye ngelizwi eliphantsi njengoko ndisiya ndisondela ngokusondela ; yaye ekugqibeleni xa ndifikile kuye uyagragrama kodwa ngendlela engenalunya kangako .
Njengoko ndibeka ingalo yam emagxeni akhe avukuvuku ndize ndimphulule esifubeni , uthi abonakale ethomalala ngokungathi izihlunu zakhe ezingwanyalala zithambile . . . .
Ubeka intloko yakhe ethangeni lam , endikhuthaza ukuba ndimphulule . ”
Kwintshayelelo yencwadi kaCarr , iSidwangube saseDalhousie , esasingumlawuli omkhulu welo lizwe , sibalisa ngento esayibonayo xa ezi ngonyama zazingaphezu kweminyaka emibini ubudala yaye zijikeleza nje kungekho mntu uzijongileyo kwithafa elikufutshane nenkampu kaCarr .
UCarr wahlab ’ ikhwelo , yaye nantsi indlela esi Sidwangube esiyichaza ngayo indlela ezasabela ngayo : “ Zeza zixhumaxhuma zakuva umlozi wenkosi yazo zaza zaziphulula iintloko zazo ezoyikekayo kuye , kwangaxeshanye ngomgqumo zivakalisa umbuliso wazo owoyikekayo kodwa wovuyo .
Uthando lwazo ngaye ngokuqinisekileyo lwalunganciphanga . ”
Ngokwemvelo iingonyama ziyamoyika umntu yaye ngokuqhelekileyo zifuna ukumphepha .
Le ntsabelo engokwethuku ekhoyo kwiingonyama namanye amarhamncwa ichazwa ngokuchanileyo eBhayibhileni .
Ngaphandle kwayo umntu ebeya kuba lelona xhoba lichanabeke engozini .
Sekunjalo , amanye amarhamncwa aba zizizidla - bantu .
“ Amarhamncwa Angumahluko ”
Ingcali ngalo mbandela , uRoger Caras , ucacisa athi : “ Phantse phakathi kwazo zonke iindidi zamarhamncwa akuhlobo lweekati ezinkulu kubonakala ngathi kukho iqela elizingela abantu njengokudla .
La ngamarhamncwa angumahluko . . .
Ngokuqhelekileyo umntu unokuhlala ngoxolo [ namarhamncwa akuhlobo lweekati ezinkulu ] . ”
Izilwanyana ezininzi kubonakala ngathi azimqondi umntu xa ehleli efihlakele kwinqwelo - mafutha .
Ngale ndlela abantu bayakwazi ukuthabatha imifanekiso yeengonyama bekufutshane .
Incwadi ethi Maberly’s Mammals of Southern Africa , ilumkisa ithi , “ Kodwa , uzibizela ingozi enkulu ukuba uvula ucango lwakho , okanye uzama ukuphuma ukufutshane neengonyama , kuba ziyabuqonda ubukho bomntu , yaye ukuvela ngequbuliso kubangela umothuko ongakumbi woloyiko osenokuthi ngokulula ubangele ukuba zikuhlasele ngelithi zona ziyazikhusela . . . .
Enyanisweni ukuqubisana ubuso ngobuso nengonyama etyholweni akunabungozi kangako kunaxa uvele nje uthi gqi phambi kwayo uphuma kwinqweno - mafutha ! ”
Kuthekani Ngamahlosi ?
Namahlosi athi abe zizidla - bantu ngangumahluko .
UJonathan Scott kwincwadi yakhe ethi The Leopard’s Tale ucacisa athi : “ Xa lingaphathwanga kakubi yaye lisempilweni entle , ihlosi sisidalwa esineentloni nesiliyebeyebe esinokumoyika umntu .
Xa ligagana naye ngokuqhelekileyo liya kubalekela kwindawo yokuzimela ekufutshane . ”
Lo kaScott wachitha iinyanga kwiNdawo Yogcino - Zilwanyana iMasai Mara yaseKenya efundisisa iintshukumo zemazi yehlosi awayithiya igama lokuba nguChui .
Ngokuthe ngcembe uChui wabuqhela ubukho benqwelo - mafutha kaScott , yaye ngesinye isihlandlo amathole akhe , agama linguDark noLight , eza kuyihlolisisa .
UScott ukholelwa kwelokuba nangona ihlosi ngaphandle libonakala lingenabuhlobo ngokwemvelo lisenokuba linabo .
Abanye baye banamava obuhlobo nehlosi .
Ngokomzekelo , uJoy Adamson wakhulisa ithole lehlosi elingenabazali awalibiza ngokuba nguPenny .
Emva kokuba ekhululwe wabuyela endle , uPenny wadibana nenkunzi waza wazala amathole .
Xa abahlobo bakhe abangabantu bafikayo kuloo mmandla , uPenny wazivelisa waza wababongoza ukuba baze kubona amathole akhe asandul ’ ukuzalwa .
Kwisikhundla sakhe , ehleli ecaleni kwaloo mama unelunda , lo ka - Adamson uchaza okwenzekayo : “ Wakhotha izandla zethu ngoxa amathole ayedlala phakathi kwemikhono yakhe , bonke bonwabile .
Inkolelo eqhelekileyo ikukuba amahlosi azezona zilwanyana zaseAfrika zinobungozi , yaye iimazi ezinamathole zinoburhalarhume ngokukodwa . ”
Kodwa lo ka - ​ Adamson uthi amava akhe ngoPenny asenokungqina ukuba “ inkoliso yeenkolelo ezamkelekileyo zingamampunge . ”
Enye imazi yehlosi “ enesimo esihle , ” egama linguHarriet , yenza uArjan Singh wasemntla Indiya wanamava amangalisa ngakumbi .
USingh wakhulisa uHarriet ukususela eselithole waza wamqeqesha ukuze akwazi ukuzifunela ukutya ehlathini elikufutshane nefama yakhe .
Njengenxalenye yolo qeqesho , uSingh maxa wambi wayeye akhuthaze eli hlosi ukuba lihlasele .
“ Xa ndandikhasa ndize ndimshukumisele ukuba ahlasele , ” ucacisa atsho kwincwadi yakhe ethi Prince of Cats , “ wayesiza kum ebaleka . . . , kodwa xa wayendixhumela wayeqinisekisa ukuba wayetsiba , exhathisa ngentloko yam aze atyibilike kumqolo wam , engashiyi nomkrwelo kumagxa am aze . ”
Indlela eli hlosi elalidlala ngayo nenja kaSingh uEelie yayikwabalasele .
USingh uthi “ umfanekiso oshukumayo ubonisa [ eli hlosi ] lihleli ngemilenze yaye liphos ’ inqindi njengoko le nja ilihlasela ​ —⁠ kodwa alenzi zinzame zakumbetha awe umhlaseli lowo .
Amathupha alo aphuma ngapha nangapha ecaleni kwentamo kaEelie , ngaphezu kwentloko yakhe nangaphantsi engenabungozi . ”
Olu lwalamano lobuhlobo phakathi komntu , inja nehlosi lwaqhubeka nasemva kokuba uHarriet elishiyile ikhaya ukuze aziphilele kwihlathi elikufutshane .
Lo kaSingh uqukumbela ngokuthi , “ Ukuba ubani uthi amahlosi awanakuthenjwa , ndisuka ndicinge ngezihlandlo ezininzi uHarriet awayesiza ngazo [ kwifama yam ] ezinzulwini zobusuku aze andivuse nje ngenjongo yokubulisa njengoko ndandilele phandle . ”
Ekugqibeleni , uHarriet wadibana nenkunzi waza wazala amathole amabini .
Xa isikhundla sakhe sasisongelwa ngumkhukula , eli hlosi lathabatha amathole alo amabini ngomlomo laza liphatha libe linye ngexesha lawazisa kwindawo ekhuselekileyo kwikhaya lakwaSingh .
Xa umkhukula waphelayo , uHarriet wakhwela kwiphenyane likaSingh , waza wakhuthaza ukuba abhexe iphenyane awele umlambo njengoko wayethabathela amathole akhe elinye ngexesha kwisikhundla esitsha ehlathini .
Indlovu YaseAfrika
Kuye kwathiwa indlovu yaseAfrika idlongodlongo kakhulu ukuba ingenziwa isilwanyana sasekhaya .
Noko ke , abantu abaninzi baye bangqina ukuba izibakala zibonisa okuchasene noko .
Omnye umzekelo lulwalamano oluchukumisayo phakathi kweendlovu ezintathu zaseAfrika nomMerika ogama linguRandall Moore .
Ezi ndlovu zaziyinxalenye yamathole awabanjwa kwiKruger National Park yaseMzantsi Afrika aza asiwa eUnited States .
Ekuhambeni kwexesha zaqeqeshelwa umdlalo wecircus zaza zadlala kakuhle .
Xa umninizo wafayo , lo kaMoore wanikwa ezo zintathu waza wazibuyisela eAfrika .
Iimazi ezimbini , ezibizwa ngokuba nguOwalla noDurga , zasiwa kwiNdawo Yokugcina Izilwanyana esePilanesberg eBophuthatswana ngowe - 1982 .
Ngelo xesha loo ndawo yokugcina izilwanyana yayineqela lamathole eendlovu angenabazali awayekwimeko engentle nawayefuna ukunyanyekelwa ziimazi esezikhulile .
Ngaba uOwalla noDurga abaqeqeshelwe umdlalo wecircus babenokuyiphumeza le ndima ?
Emva konyaka , uMoore wafumana iingxelo zokuba iindlovu zakhe zazizithabathele kuzo zonke ezo nkedama zili - 14 yaye kwakuza kuziswa iinkedama ezingakumbi kuloo myezo .
Emva kokungabikho iminyaka emine , lo kaMoore wabuya ukuze azibonele ngokwakhe .
Ecinga ukuba kwakuza kumthabatha ithuba elide ekhangela kwiiNtaba zasePilanesberg , wamangaliswa , kungekudala emva kokufika kwakhe , kukubona uOwalla noDurga phakathi komhlambi omkhulu .
Kwincwadi ethi Back to Africa ubhala athi , “ Imvakalelo yam yokuqala neyobuyatha yayikukubaleka ndiye kuzo , ndizigone ndize ndizizukise .
Loo mnqweno ndawushenxisa ngokwenza into esengqiqweni ngakumbi . ”
Ekuqaleni , uOwalla noDurga kwakufuneka baqiniseke ngobukho bomhlobo wabo wakudala .
Basihlolisisa isandla esasoluliwe ngemiboko yabo .
UMoore ubhala athi , “ UOwalla , wema nkqo phambi kwam ngokungathi wayelindele umyalelo olandelayo .
Zonke ezinye ezi zomhlambi zema zingashukumi zisingqongile . Ndawunikela umyalelo .
Ndathi ‘ Owalla . . .
Trunk UP and FOOT ! ’
( ‘ Owalla . . .
NYUSA umboko NONYAWO ! ’ )
Ngoko nangoko uOwalla wawuphakamisela phezulu emoyeni umkhono wakhe waza wanyusa umboko wakhe phezulu esibhakabhakeni ngendlela awayedla ngokwenza ngayo kudala xa sasikumdlalo wecircus .
Ngubani owathi indlovu ayilibali ? ”
Kwiminyaka emithathu kamva , ngo - Oktobha 1989 , inkumbulo kaOwalla yavavanywa kwakhona .
Ngesi sihlando lo kaMoore wagqiba kwelokuba azame ukwenza into awayengazange ayenze ukususela oko wezisa ezi ndlovu emyezweni kwiminyaka esixhenxe edluleyo .
UOwalla wawuthobela umyalelo wakhe othi makalale phantsi waza wamvumela lo kaMoore ukuba akhwele kuye emqolo .
Ababukeli bakamabonwakude eMzantsi Afrika babechukumisekile kukumbona ekhwele kuye ehamba phakathi kweendlovu zasendle ezingama - 30 .
Kudliwano - ndlebe noVukani ! lo kaMoore wacacisa wathi , “ Oku andikwenzanga kuba bendifuna udumo kodwa ndikwenze ngenxa yokuba bendinomdla wokwazi umlinganiselo wobuhlobo nengqiqo enayo indlovu . ”
Iinkedama zasePilanesberg zanda ngaphantsi kwenyameko enobulumko kaOwalla noDurga .
Kuyinyaniso ukuba , ubuhlobo phakathi kwabantu namarhamncwa asendle namhlanje abuyonto izenzekelayo ; bufuna ukuhlakulelwa ngenyameko .
Bekuya kuba bubuyatha ngokwenene ngomntu oqhelekileyo ukuya endle aze azame ukusondela kwiingonyama , kumahlosi nakwiindlovu .
Kodwa ngoxa ubuhlobo obunjalo phakathi kwamarhamncwa asendle nabantu buyinto enqabileyo namhlanje , kuthekani ngekamva ?
Ngaba buya kuba yinto ezenzekelayo ?
