Iingonyama Zinokuba Mbuna !
“ YIZA uze kuthabatha imifanekiso yam ndikunye neengonyama zam , ” watsho uJack Seale , umalathisi woMyezo Weenyoka Nezilwanyana iHartebeespoortdam eMzantsi Afrika .
Ndiphakuzela , ndamlandela ukuya kwindawo ekuvalelwe kuyo iingonyama , ndithemba ukuba uya kundivumela ndithabathe imifanekiso ndingaphandle kocingo olubiyeleyo .
Indawo ezazivalelwe kuyo yayicocekile , inomthunzi owaneleyo wemithi ejikeleze lo mmandla .
Iingonyama ezisithoba ezisempilweni ngokukhawuleza zamqonda umqeqeshi wazo njengokuba engena kwindawo ezivalelwe kuyo enomncedisi .
Iingonyama zavakalisa imigqumo yobuhlobo kwaye zisehla zinyuka zichulumancile .
UJack wathi , “ Ngena ngaphakathi , ” Ndazenza ongevayo .
“ Ngena ngaphakathi , ” waphinda ekhwaza .
Ukuze bazikhusele kwiingonyama , ekuphela kwezinto ababeziphethe yayizizinti !
Uvalo lwalungongoza ngamandla njengoko ndandizama ukuziqinisa , ekugqibeleni ndaqabela ndangena ngaphakathi .
Ngokukhawuleza ndaqalisa ukuqhakraza ikhamera yam njengoko uJack wayephulula ezinye zezilo zakhe azithandayo .
Hayi indlela endakhululeka ngayo xa sonke sasisele siphumile sikhuselekile !
Kodwa kwakungeyomfuneko ukuba ndoyike .
Kamva uJack wandicacisela esithi , “ Isizathu sokuba singene siphethe izinti sikukuba iingonyama zinothando yaye ziyaluma ukubonisa uthando .
Sizinika izinti ukuze zintlantlathe zona kunokuba zintlantlathe iingalo zethu . ”
UJack neqela lakhe babesandul ’ ukubuya bevela e - Etosha National Park eNamibia .
Kwakutheni ukuze aye nazo kude kangako ehlathini ?
Wandicacisela :
“ Zazisetyenziselwa ukuthabatha imifanekiso engoko kwenziwa zizazinzulu ezenza uphando ukuze zilawule ukwanda kwamanani eengonyama kumahlathi aseNamibia .
Kodwa iingonyama zam zikhetha ubomi ezibuqhelileyo apha .
ENamibia , zathi nje ukuba ziyibone ilori yam , zeza kuyo .
Andizange ndibe nangxaki yokubuya nazo . ” ​ —⁠ Linikelwe .
