Kuthekani Ngekamva ?
Kutheni uxolo phakathi kwabantu namarhamncwa lunqweneleka kangaka ?
Kungenxa yokuba abantu ekuqaleni babedalelwe ukuba bahlalisane ngoxolo nezilwanyana , kwanezo zigqalwa njengezidlongodlongo .
Xa uThixo wenza indoda nomfazi bokuqala , wababeka kummandla womhlaba oyiparadisi ukuze banandiphe ubomi .
Kwakuyinjongo yakhe ngabo ukuba babe nabantwana baze bandise imida yaloo Paradisi yantlandlolo de igubungele umhlaba uphela .
Kuloo mmandla uphela , uluntu lwaluza kuhlala nezilwanyana ziluthobela ngoxolo .
Ingxelo yeGenesis ithi : “ Mababe nobukhosi ezintlanzini zolwandle , nasezintakeni zezulu , nasezintweni ezizitho zine , nasemhlabeni wonke , nasezinambuzaneni zonke ezinambuzela emhlabeni . . . .
Wakubona uThixo konke akwenzileyo , nanko , kulungile kunene . ” ​ —⁠ Genesis 1 : ​ 26 - 31 ; 2 :⁠ 9 .
Oku kuthobela kwezilwanyana kwakungazukuba nogonyamelo .
Kwakucetywe ukuba abantu nezilwanyana bahlalisane ngoxolo .
Oku kunokubonwa kwisibakala sokuba xa izilwanyana zeziswa phambi komntu ukuba azithiye , wayengaxhobanga .
Yaye akuzange kukhankanywe uloyiko olwalubonakaliswa ngumntu okanye lirhamncwa . ​ —⁠ Genesis 2 : ​ 19 , 20 .
Injongo Yantlandlolo Iza Kuzalisekiswa
Okuvuyisayo kukuba , loo njongo kaThixo yantlandlolo kungekudala iza kufezwa , xa bonke oorhulumente babantu beye bathatyathelwa indawo buBukumkani bukaThixo , obulawula ngokusuka ezulwini .
Xa ulawulo lukaThixo lumiselwe kwakhona ngokupheleleyo phezu komhlaba wonke , injongo kaThixo yantlandlolo ngomhlaba nabantu nezilwanyana ezihlala kuwo iya kuqalisa ukuzaliseka .
Imiphumo yolawulo lukaThixo lobulungisa ebangela iinguqulelo ichazwa kakuhle kwiziprofeto ezininzi zeBhayibhile .
Ngokomzekelo , phawula oko uIsaya wakubhalayo ephantsi kwempefumlelo : “ Ingcuka iya kuhlala nemvana , ingwe ibuthe netakane lebhokhwe ; kubuthe ndawonye ithole lenkomo , nengonyama entsha , nenkomo etyetyisiweyo ; nomntwana aziqhube ezo zinto .
Ithokazi lenkomo nemazi yebhere ziya kudla utyani ndawonye , amankonyana azo abuthe ndaweni - nye ; ingonyama idle umququ njengenkomo ; ezo zinto aziyi kwenza bubi , aziyi konakalisa ezintabeni zam zonke ezingcwele ; ngokuba ilizwe liya kuzala kukwazi uYehova , njengamanzi egubungele ulwandle . ” ​ —⁠ Isaya 11 : ​ 6 , 7 , 9 .
Nezinye iziprofeto zibonisa imiphumo emihle yoxolo eya kubakho kwihlabathi elitsha likaThixo .
Kule nkalo uMika waxela kusengaphambili wathi : “ Ziwakhande , amakrele azo abe ngamakhuba , nezikhali zazo zibe zizitshetshe zokuthena imidiliya .
Uhlanga aluyi kuphakamisela kuhlanga ikrele lalo , bangabi safunda ukulwa .
Baya kuhlala elowo phantsi komdiliya wakhe , naphantsi komkhiwane wakhe , kungabikho uboyikisayo . ” ​ —⁠ Mika 4 : ​ 3 , 4 .
