Ngokuphawulekayo , ngasekupheleni kowe - 1990 , amaZiko kaRhulumente Okuthintela Izifo athi kwiingxelo ezifunyenweyo ezili - 153 000 ezingoGawulayo , abaqukiweyo abangama - 637 yayingoogqirha , abangama - 42 yayingoogqirha botyando , abali - 156 yayingoogqirha bamazinyo nezazi ngezococeko , yaye abali - 1 199 yayingabongikazi .
UGawulayo waziwa okokuqala ngowe - 1981 .
Kangangethuba elithile wayefumaneka ngokukodwa kumafanasini angamadoda namakhoboka eziyobisi athi asulelwe ngeenaliti ezingcolileyo .
Kodwa ukusasazeka kwawo phakathi kwamabhinqa kuye kwakhawuleza .
IWorld Health , iphephancwadi leWHO ( [ World Health Organization ] Intlangano Yehlabathi Yezempilo ) , lanikela le ngxelo kwinkupho yalo kaNovemba noDisemba 1990 : “ Inani lamabhinqa [ ehlabathini jikelele ] alindeleke ukuguliswa nguGawulayo kwiminyaka emibini elandelayo liya kuba ngaphaya kwesimbuku esandayo sazo zonke iingxelo zikaGawulayo ezixelwe kwiWHO ebudeni beminyaka yokuqala elishumi yalo bhubhani . ”
EUnited States , Amaziko kaRhulumente Okuthintela Izifo anikela ingxelo yokuba ngasekupheleni kowe - 1990 , kwakukho abantu abali - 15 696 abaneminyaka engaphezu kwama - 50 ubudala abaye baqalisa ukuvelisa iimpawu zikaGawulayo .
Elo linani eliphakamileyo xa lithelekiswa neengxelo ezingama - 2 686 zikaGawulayo kubantwana abaneminyaka engaphantsi kweminyaka eli - 13 ubudala , kuye kwanikelwa ingqalelo engakumbi kwiqela lamaxhoba kaGawulayo .
