Noko ke , kukho ezinye iinkalo zalo mbandela ezibonakala zisengqiqweni .
Ngokomzekelo , uninzi lweempawu zemfuza eziphawulekayo zinempembelelo kwiimpawu zakho zobuntu .
Ngaloo ndlela , bambi abantu bazalwa beyiminyewu , ngoxa abanye bendwebile ngokwemvelo .
Umfazi okhulelweyo unokumnceda okanye amonakalise umntwana wakhe ongekazalwa ngezenzo , ngeengcinga nangeemvakalelo zakhe .
Kanye kanye ungakanani umlinganiselo woxolo okanye wokucaphuka owawuchanabeke kuwo ngoxa wawusesibelekweni sikanyoko ?
Kungakanani owakufundayo kwimvakalo - zwi yabazali bakho , kumculo ababewuphulaphula ?
Wachatshazelwa kangakanani kukutya unyoko awayekutya ?
Ukuba wayesebenzisa iziselo ezinxilisayo okanye iziyobisi , wayechatshazelwa kangakanani zizo ?
Ngexesha lokuzalwa kwakho , izinto ezininzi otyekele kuzo zaqalisa ukuzinza yaye mhlawumbi kunzima ukuziguqula .
Kuthekani Ngokutya Owawukutya , Izinto Ezingamkelwayo Ngumzimba Wakho , Imeko - bume
Njengokuba wawukhulela ebuntwaneni , izinto ezithile ekutyeni kwakho zisenokuba zaba nempembelelo kwiimpawu zakho zobuntu .
Izinto zokuvakalisa incasa , izijiki - mbala ezenziweyo nezinto zokugcina ukutya okunkonkxiweyo kungonakali ​ —⁠ zonke zinokuziphembelela ngeendlela ongaziqondiyo iimpawu zakho zobuntu .
Ukuphakuzela , uxinezeleko olongezelelekileyo , ubucaphucaphu , ukuqaqanjelwa yimithambo - luvo nezenzo ezingalungelelananga nezingalawulekiyo yeminye nje yemiphumo yoku .
Ungcoliso olubangelwa ngumsi ophuma kwizithuthi , olukhutshwa yimizi - mveliso nezinye iityhefu ezikummandla okungqongileyo zikwanegalelo ekubumbeni iimpawu zobuntu bukabani .
Okanye wena ngokobuqu , usenokuba nento engamkelwayo ngumzimba wakho nekuchaphazela ngokunzulu kodwa engabachaphazeliyo abo bakungqongileyo .
Ukongezelela kwezi mpembelelo , iimpawu zobuntu zabazali bakho , izinto abazithandayo nabangazithandiyo ndawonye nekhethe oye wakhula benalo ukususela ebusaneni , ziye zakuchaphazela yaye ziye zabumba ubuntu bakho ukusa kumkhamo othile .
Umphumo uba kukuba iindlela zakho ezininzi nendlela ozibona ngayo izinto ebomini iyimbonakaliso yeyabo ngokupheleleyo .
Uyacatshukiswa zizinto ezibacaphukisayo .
Utyekela ekuzinyamezeleni izinto abazinyamezelayo .
Ibe akufane uziphawule ukuba uxelisa iimpawu zabo zobuntu de umntu othile akuxelele ukuba ufuze uyihlo okanye unyoko .
Umgangatho abakuwo ngokwemali nongokwentlalo nako kuye kwakuchaphazela , njengokuba indawo ohlala kuyo nemeko yasesikolweni yayinjalo .
Kwanabahlobo nezinxulumani zakho zibe nempembelelo enkulu kuwe .
Mhlawumbi ingozi embi ( eyakwehlelayo okanye eyehlela umhlobo osenyongweni ) , intlekele ethile yasekuhlaleni , okanye kwaneziganeko zehlabathi ezikhathazayo ziye zakuchaphazela .
Okanye kusenokuba intlekele ethile , enjengoqhawulo - mtshato okanye ukugula okungamandla , kuye kwashiya isiva esithile , kubuntu bakho .
Ngaba wena , ngokobuqu , unako ukuyiphawula nayiphi na impembelelo enjalo ?
Unqulo Lunayiphi Indima ?
Kucingelwa ukuba , unqulo lufanele lukuncede ekuphuculeni ubuntu bakho , imilinganiselo yakho yokuziphatha , imigaqo ekulawulayo nendlela yamihla le yokuphila kwakho .
Kanye kanye imilinganiselo yokuziphatha nezenzo zakho ziye zachatshazelwa kangakanani lunqulo ?
Ngoxa unqulo lufanele lusebenze njengoluphelisa ukungakhathali , ulwaphulo - mthetho , abantu abaninzi bachatshazelwa ngendlela eyahlukileyo ngokunxulumana kwabo nonqulo .
Babona ukuhanahanisa okuninzi nokubalaseliswa kwezinto eziphathekayo kunakwimilinganiselo yokomoya ezicaweni baze ngenxa yoko babe buhlungu .
Basenokude bangabi namdla kwaphela kunqulo benganikeli ngqalelo kwaphela kwizinto zokomoya , yaye bengenathemba .
Usenokucinga ngezinye iimpembelelo zangaphandle ezibumba iimpawu zobuntu .
Khawunqumame umzuzwana uze ucinge ngazo naziphi na izinto ezisenokuba zakuchaphazela ukuza kuthi ga ngoku .
Ngaba unokuzidwelisa ezinye zazo ?
Akulula ukuphenjelelwa zizibakala , kungekhona iimvakalelo zobuqu okanye umkhethe uze ucinge ngolu hlobo , kodwa kuwufanele umgudu yaye kunokuba luncedo kuwe .
Njani ?
Kaloku , ukuba uyakwazi ukufumanisa impembelelo ethile okanye unobangela wotyekelo oluthile olubi kwiimpawu zakho zobuntu , ukuba ngokukhethekileyo uyakwazi ukulwahlula kwezinye , uya kukwazi kakuhle ukululawula , mhlawumbi kwanokuluguqula .
Ukuba uyakwazi ukuyilawula , okanye kwanokuyiphelisa , impembelelo enganqwenelekiyo , unokuba ngumntu owahlukileyo , oziphethe kakuhle ngakumbi ngokuhlobene nabanye .
Kambe ke , oko kulucelomngeni .
Kodwa ekubeni iimpembelelo ezininzi kangaka kwiimpawu zakho zobuqu ziye zanyanzeliswa kuwe ngabanye abantu okanye ziimeko ongakwazanga ukuzilawula , kutheni ungaqalisi uze wenze okuthile ngale meko wena siqu ?
Ukuba kufuneka uphucule , kutheni ungaluguquli nje uhlobo lomntu onguye ?
