Izenzo neemvakalelo zomfazi okhulelweyo zinokumchaphazela umntwana wakhe ongekazalwa
Kutheni Ufanele Wenze Inguqulelo ?
BAMBALWA kuthi abafane bavume ukuba sineentsilelo ezibalaseleyo .
Hayi indlela ayinyaniso ngayo amazwi embongi yaseSkotlani uRobert Burns athi : “ Akwaba besinganamandla esipho sokuzibona njengoko abanye besibona . ”
Ewe , sikufumanisa kulula ukubona iziphako zabanye yaye kusenokuba lula ukubacebisa nokubabonisa indlela yokuphucula .
Kodwa naliphi na icebiso lokuba nathi kufuneka siguqule iimpawu zethu zobuntu linokusicaphukisa .
Ngaba wena liya kukucaphukisa ?
Makhe sinqumame kancinane size sibe nombono wehlabathi elifezekileyo apho bonke abantu bacocekileyo khona , besempilweni , bonwabile yaye benyanisekile ; apho kwanabo baphetheyo ingabantu abanobubele nabanovelwano , benomdla wokubenzela okulungileyo abanye ; apho kungekho kubawa yaye kungekho bani uxhaphaza abanye abantu ; apho abantwana babathobelayo abazali babo abanothando nabanenyameko ; apho kungekhoyo khona ukubhabhazela ngumsindo ​ —⁠ kungekho bundlobongela , lwaphulo - mthetho nokuziphatha okubi ; apho abantu ngokwemvelo unokubathemba yaye kuluyolo ukuba nabo ; apho unokunandipha ubomi uziva unqabisekile yaye uhleli kakuhle .
Ngaba unokuzibona ukufanelekele ukuphila kwihlabathi elinjalo , ukuba ihlabathi elifezeke ngolo hlobo linokuze libekho ?
Ewe , iindaba ezilungileyo eziseBhayibhileni zezokuba ihlabathi elinjalo liyeza kulo mhlaba kungekudala .
Ngoku ke umbuzo obalulekileyo ngulo : Ngaba unazo naziphi na iimpawu zobuntu ezinokukubangela ukuba ungakufanelekeli ukuphila kwihlabathi elihle ngolo hlobo ?
Ucinga ukuba bekuya kubanzima kangakanani na ukwenza umgudu ofanelekileyo wokuphila kwiparadisi enjalo ? ​ —⁠ Isaya 65 : ​ 17 - 25 ; 2 Petros 3 :⁠ 13 .
Kwanangoku , ngaphambi kokufika kwehlabathi elitsha elinjalo , ngaba ubomi bakho bunokuphuculwa ukuba wenza okuthile ngeempawu zakho zobuntu nangesimo sakho sengqondo ?
Ngoko , ukuba kunjalo , kutheni ungenzi inguqulelo efunekayo ?
Oko kunako ukwenzeka .
Khumbula ukuba , ekuqaleni iimpembelelo ezithile ziye zabumba zaza zakha ubuntu bakho , ngoko ngokuzilawula nangomdla ongakumbi , unokukwazi ukubakha kwakhona ubuntu bakho kwanangoku .
Noko ke , usenokubuza uthi : ‘ Kodwa ngaba ngokwenene ndinokuyenza inguqulelo ?
Ndizamile ngaphambili , izihlandlo ezininzi ndaza andaphumelela .
Ndidalwe ngolu hlobo , yaye akukho nto ndinokuyenza ngako oku ! ’
Khawucinge ngoPawulos , umpostile kaYesu Kristu .
UPawulos waguquka ekubeni ngumchasi wamaKristu ondlongondlongo nozingcayo waza waba ngumKristu .
Wayenza inguqulelo kuba ngokwenene wayefuna ukuyenza .
Akazange ayekelele umxakatho ngenxa yeentsilelo okanye iimpembelelo zemfuza .
Akazange akholelwe kwelokuba ubuntu bakhe obudala babungenakuguqulwa .
Kwafuneka enze umgudu omkhulu .
Kodwa wafumana uncedo olukhulu . ​ —⁠ Galati 1 : ​ 13 -⁠ 16 .
Lwaluvela phi olu ncedo ?
Iindlela Ezingalunganga Zokwenza Inguqulelo
WAKUBE uziqonda kakuhle iimpawu zobuntu bakho , unokuyenza njani inguqulelo ?
Ngubani onokuphethukela kuye yaye ziziphi iindlela ezinokusetyenziswa ukwenza uphuculo oluhlala luhleli ?
Makhe siqwalasele amanyathelo athile angawona asetyenziswayo namhlanje .
Ingcinezelo Yobupolitika
Izigidi zabantu namhlanje ziphila phantsi kolawulo olufuna ukulawula iimbono nemithetho engokokuziphatha .
Oorhulumente abanjalo basebenzisa igunya labo ukunyanzela abantu ukuba benze inguqulelo ​ —⁠ bambi ngobuqhophololo , bambi ngegunya .
Basebenzisa amacebo enkohliso , ngokufuthi kuquka ukuboyikisa , ukubavalela entolongweni nokubathuthumbisa .
Balawula amaziko eendaba nezinye iinkqubo zemfundo , bafuna ukuthabathel ’ indawo zonke iingcamango ezamiselwa kwangaphambili ngezo zinqwenelwa zizihandiba ezithile ezisemagunyeni ngoku .
Kusetyenziswa amandla ukuchitha konke ukungevani .
Nabani na ozingqina engakulungele ukufundiswa kwakhona unokufumana impatho eyoyikekayo ngokufuthi edandathekisayo .
Utyando Lobuchopho Nesivuseleli Sombane
Imimandla ethile yobuchopho iye yaphawulwa njengechaphazela izimo zengqondo ezithile neempawu ezithile zobuntu .
Utyando lobuchopho lubandakanya ukususwa kokoqobo okanye ukutshatyalaliswa kobuchopho ngokwabo kuloo mmandla wobuchopho .
Bakube bususiwe , loo nxalenye yobuchopho bakho ayinakuze isebenze kwakhona , ibe naluphi na uphawu lobuntu ebuluchaphazela luyaphela .
Kuthiwa kuye kwenziwa olu hlobo lotyando kumawaka abantu , ngokukodwa kubantu abaneempawu zobuntu ezingaqhelekanga neziyingozi ngokuphathelele isini .
Bambi baye baneengcingo zombane ezincinane ezifakwe phakathi ebuchotsheni babo , yaye xa amandla ombane asetyenziswa , avuselela okanye athintela ukusebenza kobuchopho kuloo mmandla .
Kuthiwa oku kuguqula iintshukumisa ezichaphazela iimpawu zobuntu ezilawulwa yiloo nxalenye yobuchopho .
Iziyobisi
Ukusetyenziswa kweziyobisi ekunyangeni izifo zengqondo kwandile ngokwenene yaye kufuneka ngokufuthi .
Kukho iziyobisi zokuthomalalisa , iziyobisi ezibangela ubuthongo , iziyobisi ezenza umntu akhululeke neziyobisi ezilungisa ukungalungelelani okungokwemichiza engqondweni .
Kukwakho neziyobisi eziye zasetyenziselwa ukohlwaya ezintolongweni nakwamanye amaziko okulungisa izimilo zabantu .
Iziyobisi ezinjalo ezimbini yiapomorphine neAnectine .
Iapomorphine iye yasetyenziswa kumabanjwa ayeneempawu zobuntu ezazigqalwa njengezingamkelekanga .
Ibangela isicaphucaphu nokuhlanza okubi .
Ibanjwa liyaxelelwa ukuba ukuba liphinda liziphathe kakubi kwakhona , liya kunikwa iapomorphine engakumbi .
Olu lukwabizwa ngokuba lunyango lokuguqula imikhwa emibi .
IAnectine ibangela umbefu , imvakalelo yokurhaxwa kwibanjwa eliziphethe kakubi .
Licinga ukuba liza kufa .
Ukuba liziphatha kakubi kwakhona , lifumana iAnectine engakumbi .
Ngaba ezi ziindlela obuya kuzisebenzisa ukuguqula iimpawu zobuntu bakho ?
Inkoliso yezi ndlela zingasentla ziphelisa inkululeko yokuzikhethela .
Zikwabandakanya impembelelo yabantu abanamandla phezu komnye umntu kodwa kungasoloko kucingwa ngeengenelo zaloo mntu .
Ngaba igunya lezobupolitika lifuna ukulungelwa kwalo okanye okomnye umntu ?
Kutyando lobuchopho , ngubani ophethe incakuba kagqirha yokutyanda ?
Ngubani olawula isixhobo sokuvula nokucima xa isivuseleli sombane sisetyenziswa ?
Unyango lokwenza inguqulelo kwimikhwa emibi luhlala ixesha elingakanani ?
Ngaba umntu owenza olu nyango unokuthenjwa ?
Makhe siqwalasele enye inkqubo eyamkeleke ngakumbi .
Indlela Onokubuguqula Ngayo Ubuntu Bakho
YINTONI engakhankanywanga ngoxa bekuxutyushwa ngeendlela zokwakha iimpawu zobuntu ezifanelekileyo nezokwenza inguqulelo ?
Yiminqweno yomntu nokunamathela kuzimiselo lwakhe !
Ukusebenzisa inkululeko yakhe yokuzikhethela ngokhetho lobuqu ekuqonda okubandakanyekileyo .
Ngamafutshane , into engakhankanywanga kukuzeyisa kwakhe !
Abo banikela unyango kwiimpawu zobuntu bafumanise ukuba baba nethuba elihle lokufumana imiphumo ehlala ihleli xa umntu onyangwayo enelungelo lokwenza isigqibo ngohlobo lweempawu zobuntu azinqwenelayo .
UVance Packard ubhala oku kwincwadi yakhe ethi The People Shapers : “ Kucacile ukuba ngesiluleko esincinane , nawuphi na umntu oqiqayo nokrelekrele ngoku unokuzilungisa ngokwakhe iimpawu zakhe zobuntu . ”
Oku kubizwa ngokuba kukuzilawula .
Ngamany ’ amazwi , xa kusetyenziswa umlinganiselo othile wokuzeyisa kuye kwabonwa iinguqulelo ezibalaseleyo .
AmaKristu awatsali nzima xa kufuneka esebenzise ukuzeyisa , kuba aye afunda ukukubonakalisa njengesinye seziqhamo ezisithoba zomoya oyingcwele kaThixo .
Oku kuthetha ukuba amandla asebenzayo kaThixo uSomandla anokuziguqula iimpawu zobuntu bakho aze akuncede uphumelele .
Ngoko , yintoni ofuna ukuyenza ngeempawu zakho zobuntu ?
Ngaba ngokwenene uyafuna ukuziguqula ?
Ukuba uyafuna , ufuna ukuziguqula zisuka entwenini ?
Uziguqulela entwenini ?
Yaye ngoba ?
Ngaba unethemba lokuba ungazenzela oku ngamandla akho ?
Unokulufumana phi uncedo oluvelisa ezona ngenelo zifunekayo ?
Makhe sihlolisise ezinye iindlela nezinto zokuguqula iimpawu zobuntu .
Inyathelo 1 : Fumanisa Oko Ukuko Ngokwenene
Usisiqalelo soko ufuna ukuba kuko .
Ubuntu bakho obutsha bufanele bakhiwe ngokuguqula ubuntu bakho obudala .
Ngoko ufanele uzazi ngokuchanileyo .
Ngaba unokuzichaza iinkalo zeempawu zakho zobuntu obungathanda ukuziguqula ?
Ekubeni kunzima ukuzihlolisisa iimpawu zakho zobuntu , kufuneka ufune umthombo ohlonelwayo nonokuthenjwa .
IBhayibhile Engcwele iyanconyelwa koku .
Sebenzisa iBhayibhile , yaye uya kuziqonda ngendlela ekusenokwenzeka ukuba akuzange uziqonde ngayo ngaphambili .
Usekwanokungakuthandi oko kuboniswayo ngawe , kodwa unokuqiniseka ukuba iya kuba ngumfanekiselo ochanileyo .
IBhayibhile iye yafaniswa nesipili , yaye abantu bayabongozwa ukuba baqondele kuyo .
“ Ngokuba umntu , ukuba ungumphulaphuli nje welizwi , engemenzi walo , lowo ufana nendoda eqiqa [ ejonga ] ubuso bayo bobuntu esipilini ; kuba iyaziqiqa [ iyazibona ] , imke , ilibale kwaoko ukuba ibinjani na .
Ke yena oqondele emthethweni ogqibeleleyo wayo inkululeko , ahlale ehleli kuwo , lowo , ethe nje akaba ngumphulaphuli olibalayo , esuke waba ngumenzi womsebenzi : yena uya kuba noyolo ekwenzeni kwakhe . ”
IBhayibhile , xa iqondwa yaye isetyenziswa ngokuchanileyo , inamandla amakhulu okuhlalutya nacacileyo angayi kubonakalisa kuphela uhlobo lomntu onguye kodwa akwatyhila iintshukumisa nesimo sengqondo sakho .
Ngenxa yoko , uPawulos wabhala wathi : “ Ilizwi likaThixo liphilile , liyasebenza , libukhali ngaphezu kwamakrele onke antlangothi mbini ; . . . linokugweba iingcingane nezicamango zentliziyo . ”
ILizwi likaThixo likwahlabela mgama ngokunikela ukhokelo ngokuphathelele oko kulungileyo ngokwenene noko kuphosakeleyo ngokwenene . ​ —⁠ Hebhere 4 : ​ 12 ; 5 :⁠ 14 .
IBhayibhile inokukwenzela zonke ezi zinto kuba iliLizwi likaYehova , uThixo oyinyaniso noqondayo .
Ngokutsho kweNdumiso 139 , uThixo uyakugocagoca aze enze uhlalutyo oluchanileyo ngoko ukuko .
Kunjengokuba indinyana 1 isithi : “ Yehova , undigocagocile , wandazi . ”
UThixo ebekuhlola ukususela ekukhawulweni kwakho .
Ukwazi ukusuka nokuhlala .
Uye walungiselela ukuba eBhayibhileni kubhalwe inkcazelo engazo zonke iindidi zobomi babantu .
Uya kuzifumana uchaziwe ndaweni ithile eBhayibhileni , enoba kungecala elihle okanye elibi .
Ngoko , unokufumanisa oko ukuko ngokwenene ​ —⁠ ukuba uyafuna .
Inyathelo 2 : Gqiba Ngoko Ufuna Ukuba Kuko
Ukuba uza kwenza inguqulelo , qiniseka ukuba wenza inguqulelo eyimfuneko .
Qinisekisa ukuba oko koko ukufunayo yaye kulunge ngakumbi kunoko unako ngoku .
Luluphi usukelo lweempawu zobuntu eziphuculiweyo ofanele uzibekele lona ?
Ungalifumana phi icebiso elilungileyo lokufumana iimpawu zobuntu ozinqwenelayo ?
Kwakhona , kunconyelwa ukuba usebenzise iBhayibhile kule nkalo .
IBhayibhile ikubongoza ukuba uguqukele kokulungileyo , wamkele “ ubuntu obutsha . ”
UPawulos waluleka : “ Nithi ngakwihambo yangaphambili nimlahle umntu omdala , owonakaliswayo ngokokweenkanuko zokulukuhla ; . . . nimambathe umntu omtsha [ “ ubuntu obutsha , ” NW ] , othe ngokukaThixo wadalelwa ebulungiseni , nasebungcweleni benyaniso . ”
IBhayibhile ikubonisa oko ezi mpawu zilunge ngakumbi zikuko .
Ngaba uyalikhumbula ihlabathi elifezekileyo elichazwe ngaphambilana ?
Ukuba ufuna ukuphila kwelo hlabathi , ufanele uyibone imfuneko yokuvelisa iimpawu ezichazwe kwabaseKolose 3 : ​ 12 - 17 , iimpawu ezinjengemfesane , ububele , ukuthobeka , ubulali , umonde , ukuxolela , uthando , uxolo nombulelo .
Ngoko wakube uyihlolisisile iBhayibhile , zimisele usukelo .
Lubhale phantsi .
Sukelo ngalunye lubeke kwindawo yokuqala .
Sebenzela kulo !
Inyathelo 3 : Funa Imizekelo Efanelekileyo
Ubukhulu becala iimpawu zakho zobuntu ziye zaphenjelelwa kukulandela kwakho umzekelo wabanye ​ —⁠ abahlobo , izinxulumani , abazali , abafundisi - ntsapho .
Ngoko , kutheni ungathi emva kokwenza isigqibo ngosukelo lwesimilo lweempawu zobuntu ozinqwenelayo , ukhangele umntu oziphethe ngendlela ofuna ukuyilandela ?
Emva koko funa uncedo lwaloo mntu .
Umzekeliso weBhayibhile ubonisa ubulumko boku xa usithi : “ Ohamba nezilumko uba sisilumko naye . ” ​ —⁠ IMizekeliso 13 :⁠ 20 .
IBhayibhile iqulethe ingxelo engobomi boyena mntu ungumzekelo ubalaseleyo esifanele sonke siwulandele , uYesu Kristu .
Funda indlela awaziphatha ngayo kuzo zonke iimeko , ihambo yakhe yokuziphatha , ukuqonda nobulumko bakhe , ukundiliseka kwakhe , ulwazelelelo nobubele bakhe obubalaseleyo nokuba nenkxalabo ngabantu awayephila kunye nabo .
Hayi indlela ekuhlaziya ngayo ukumva esithi : “ Yizani kum nonke nina nibulalekayo , nisindwayo ngumthwalo , ndoninika ukuphumla .
Thabathani idyokhwe yam niyithwale , nifunde kum ; ngokuba ndinobulali , ndithobekile ngentliziyo ; noyifumanela ukuphumla imiphefumlo yenu .
Kuba idyokhwe yam imnandi , nomthwalo wam ulula ” ! ​ —⁠ Mateyu 11 : ​ 28 -⁠ 30 .
Izigidi kuwo onke amazwe sele ziphethukele kuKristu njengomzekelo ezifanele ziwulandele ibe zenza konke okusemandleni azo ukulandela emanyathelweni akhe , kanye njengokuba naye wahamba ngendlela awayiyalelwa nguYise wasemazulwini , uYehova uThixo .
Ezi zigidi , zidiniwe ziimpawu zabantu ezimbi eziqhelekileyo ehlabathini namhlanje , ziye zaphethukela kumabandla asekuhlaleni amaNgqina kaYehova ukuze zifumane uncedo nokhokelo ibe azikhange zidaniswe .
KwiiHolo zawo zoBukumkani , kukho abantu abaninzi abayimizekelo ebalaseleyo enjengekaKristu , ibe uncedo olungakumbi luye lwanikelwa kwabo bafuna ukuphucula iimpawu zabo zobuntu .
Kambe ke , amaNgqina aneentsilelo eziqhelekileyo kuluntu olungafezekanga ; kodwa akwanawo namandla omoya osebenzayo nophembelela ukuqiqa kwawo . ​ —⁠ Efese 4 :⁠ 23 .
Inyathelo 4 : Fumana Amandla Okuphumelela
Kuya kuba yintuthuzelo kwabo banqwenela ukuguqula iindlela zabo ukwazi ukuba uncedo luyafumaneka .
“ Ubuntu obutsha ” buchazwa ‘ njengobudalwe ngokokuthanda kukaThixo ebulungiseni benyaniso nokunyaniseka . ’
Oku kuyasiqinisekisa ukuba uThixo uya kunikela uncedo olungaphaya kolomntu kwabo balunqwenelayo .
Unokulufumana njani uncedo lukaYehova uThixo ?
Olunye lolona ncedo luphambili ngumthandazo wobuqu .
Umthandazo uyindlela ebalulekileyo yokunxibelelana noMthombo wamandla afunekayo ukuguqula iindlela zakho .
Umthandazo ukunika ithuba lokuthetha ngokukhululekileyo nangokungafihlisi nangaliphi na ixesha , kwanaphakathi kwamaxesha anzima .
Ilungelo elinjalo lokufuna uncedo kuThixo wokwenene nonenyameko kuwodlula lee amalungelo okufuna uncedo lwakhe nawuphi na umntu ibe lisebenza ngokukhawuleza .
Ngenxa yoku , umpostile uYohane wayenokubhala aze athi : “ Kuko oku ukungafihlisi esinako kuye : Ukuba sithi sicele into ngokokuthanda kwakhe , uyasiva . ”
Ibe amazwi omprofeti uIsaya ayasikhuthaza : “ Funani uYehova esenokufunyanwa ; mbizeni esekufuphi .
Ongendawo makashiye indlela yakhe , indoda enobutshinga mayishiye iingcingane zayo , ibuyele kuYehova : Woba nemfesane kuyo ; ibuyele kuThixo wethu ngokuba woxolela ngokukhulu . ” ​ —⁠ Isaya 55 : ​ 6 , 7 .
Kwakhona ufundisiso lweBhayibhile luyomeleza , luya kuhlaziya , lukwenze ukuba imihla ngemihla ukhangele kusukelo lwakho .
IBhayibhile ikunika amandla afanelekileyo njengoko uzabalazela ukufikelela usukelo lweempawu zobuntu ozinqwenelayo .
Ngaphezu koko , ishukumisa imvakalelo yokuzicekisa iindlela zakho zangaphambili .
Ukungenisa yonke imihla ulwazi lweBhayibhile noko ikuquletheyo kuya kukunceda nasekushenxiseni nayiphi na ingcamango engafanelekanga ebinokungena ivela kumaziko osasazo ehlabathi nakwiinkqubo zalo zemfundo .
Iintlanganiso zamaKristu , eziqhutyelwa kwiHolo yoBukumkani yasekuhlaleni yamaNgqina kaYehova , azinikeli kuphela imfundiso ngemilinganiselo yeBhayibhile kodwa kuzo ukwafumana nenkxaso yeqela nokulolana okuluncedo ekuphuculeni iimpawu zakho zobuntu .
Le nkxaso elungiselelwe ngebandla iye yanceda abaninzi baphumelela ekuguquleni iimpawu zabo zobuntu .
Kutheni ungaxubushi ngoncedo olunjalo nomntu olifumene kuye eli phephancwadi ?
Inyathelo 5 : Ukuhlangabezana Nokuvukwa Likakade
Abaninzi baye bazama ukuphucula iindlela zabo kodwa baye badimazeka ngenxa yokuvukwa likakade okusenokubonakala kungaphepheki .
Umphumo uye waba kukuba abathile banikezele ngokupheleleyo .
Abanjalo badla ngokucinga ukuba ukuba oko babekugqala njengethemba labo ngoku kusilele , akukho themba limbi konke konke .
Ngoko basenokuziyekelela ekubeni ngamaxhoba eempembelelo zehlabathi .
Ngokufuthi imeko yabo iba mandundu kunokuba babenjalo ngaphambi kokuba bazame ukwenza inguqulelo .
Hlala uziqinisekisa ukuba naliphi na ikhondo langaphambili elinganqwenelekiyo lifanele ukuphetshwa .
Umpostile uPawulos wabhekisela kwiimpawu zakhe zobuntu zangaphambili nendlela yokuphila njengeziyinkunkuma .
Ngoko ukuba wena , ekwenzeni inguqulelo , uphazanyiswa ngumqobo othile okanye kukuvukwa likakade , qula , uze uqhubekele phambili .
Zingisa !
Yilwa !
Kuya kuwufanela loo mgudu !
Khumbula ukuba , iindlela nemizila yakho emininzi yanyanzelwa kuwe ngamandla angaphandle nangaphaya kokhetho okanye ulawulo lwakho ngelo xesha .
La mandla asasebenza .
Ngaba uza kuwavumela akukhokelele koko kuthandwa ngawo ?
Akunjalo ?
Ngoko ungaze unikezele !
Izigidi zabantu ezineemvelaphi ezahlukahlukeneyo ​ —⁠ kwanezikrelemnqa nabantu ababebandakanyeke ngokunzulu ekuziphatheni okubi⁠ — ​ ziye ngokunempumelelo zaziguqula iimpawu zazo zobuntu .
Ziye zayilondoloza imilinganiselo yazo ephuculiweyo kude kube namhlanje , uninzi lukwenze oku kangangamashumi eminyaka , zinamathele kwiindlela zazo ezilunge ngakumbi nakukhetho lwazo oluhle lokugcina ingqibelelo .
Kodwa nguThixo owazinika amandla nentshukumisa yokwenza oko .
Kunjengokuba umpostile uPawulos wathi : “ Ndinokuzenza izinto zonke , ndikulowo undomelezayo . ” ​ —⁠ Filipi 4 :⁠ 13 .
Ziyaphumelela kumlo wokwenza okulungileyo .
Nawe unokuyenza inguqulelo ukuba ngokwenene uyafuna yaye unokunandipha ubomi kwihlabathi elitsha likaThixo . ​ —⁠ INdumiso 37 : ​ 29 ; 2 Petros 3 :⁠ 13 .
