Zinokundinceda Njani Iintlanganiso ZamaKristu ?
“ Andiqondi ukuba iicawa ziyakunceda ukuba uqhubele phambili ngokomoya .
Ndithetha ukuba , kuxhomekeke emntwini ukuba ngozixhalabeleyo izinto zokomoya okanye akunjalo . ” ​ —⁠ UKevin oneminyaka eli - 19 ubudala .
UKEVIN uchanile kwiinkalo ezininzi .
Ngokwenene kuxhomekeke kumntu ngamnye ukugqiba “ enoba uyafuna ukuba ngozixhalabeleyo izinto zokomoya okanye akunjalo . ”
Kodwa ekubeni ufunda eli nqaku , kusenokwenzeka ngokungakumbi ukuba ubuncinane ufune ukuba ngozixhalabeleyo izinto zokomoya .
Noko ke , usenokugaqiniseki ncam , ngohlobo alulo umntu ozixhalabeleyo izinto zokomoya okanye into onokuyenza ukuze ube nguye .
Ngokwentetho eqhelekileyo , umntu ozixhalabeleyo izinto zokomoya ngulowo uvumela iingcinga , izimvo , nezenzo zakhe ukuba zikhokelwe nguThixo Osenyangweni , uYehova .
Ucinga ngoMdali wakhe xa esenza izigqibo zemihla ngemihla , emisela usukelo lwakhe , okanye ecwangcisa izinto eziza kuqala ebomini bakhe .
Ngamany ’ amazwi , umntu ozixhalabeleyo izinto zokomoya utyekele kuThixo .
Njengosekwishumi elivisayo , usenokufumanisa ukuba “ ixhala leli phakade ” liyayibambezela indlela okhula ngayo ngokomoya .
Ukunxulumana imini yonke namaqabane esikolo ‘ asenokutyekela ekwenzeni okubi ngalo lonke ixesha ’ kusenokukudimaza .
Abanye basenokude “ bathethe ngokubandezela , benobubi , ” bekwenza kube nzima ngawe ukuba uzikise ingqondo kokulungileyo .
Yaye ukuba abazali bakho okanye amanye amalungu entsapho abavumelani nawe ngokholo lwakho , basenokukukhuthaza kancinane ngokomoya ukuba phofu baya kukukhuthaza .
Yintoni onokuyenza ukuthintela ezi mpembelelo zilandulayo uze ukhule ngokomoya ?
Into onokuyenza kukuya rhoqo ezintlanganisweni kwiHolo yoBukumkani yamaNgqina kaYehova .
Ngokungafaniyo neenkonzo zecawa , iintlanganiso eziqhutyelwa apho ziya kukukhuthaza ukuba ‘ uziqhelise ukuhlonela uThixo ’ zize zikuncede ekukhuleni kwakho ngokomoya ukususela ebusaneni ukuya ebudodeni bokomoya . ​ —⁠ 1 Timoti 4 :⁠ 7 ; Efese 4 : ​ 13 , 14 .
Iintlanganiso Ezikunceda Ukuba Ufunde
Kumabandla angaphezu kwama - 63 000 ehlabathini lonke , amaNgqina kaYehova alandela umyalelo weBhayibhile ‘ wokubizelwa ndawonye kwabantu , amadoda , nabafazi , nabantwana ukuze beve nokuze bafunde . ’
Ngoko uya kufumana abaninzi abangangawe phakathi kwamaNgqina .
AmaNgqina kaYehova kulo lonke ihlabathi alandela inkqubo yemfundo efanayo .
Le nkqubo ibunjwa ziintlanganiso ezintlanu ngeveki , nganye kuzo imalunga neyure ubude .
Ezi ntlanganiso zintlanu zezi :
Intlanganiso Yesidlangalala ​ —⁠ intetho yeBhayibhile ebalaselisa umxholo weBhayibhile .
ISifundo SeMboniselo ​ —⁠ sisifundo esingena ngokunzulu kwiimfundiso zeBhayibhile ekusetyenziswa kuso iphephancwadi IMboniselo , impapasho ebalaseleyo yamaNgqina kaYehova .
ISikolo Sobulungiseleli Sobuthixo ​ —⁠ sifundisa ubuchule bokuthetha kubulungiseleli bobuKristu .
INtlanganiso Yenkonzo ​ —⁠ ibalaselisa iingxubusho nemiboniso ngeendlela ezinempumelelo zokufundisa kwindlu ngendlu nakubulungiseleli bezifundo zeBhayibhile .
ISifundo Sencwadi Sebandla ​ —⁠ ingxubusho yemibuzo neempendulo esiqhutywa ngamaqela amancinane kusetyenziswa amancedo okufundisisa iBhayibhile ​ —⁠ ngokuqhelekileyo emakhayeni abantu .
Iinkqubo zemfundo kwezi ntlanganiso zinokukunceda ukuba ufunde “ neenzulu zikaThixo . ”
Phofu ke , zikho nezinye iingenelo zokuya ezintlanganisweni .
“ Njengesinyithi Silola Isinyithi ”
UMichelle oneminyaka eli - 15 ubudala uthi : “ Kulula ukuba ngumKristu phakathi kwabo bakhonza uThixo .
Kodwa xa usahamba isikolo kunzima ngakumbi kuba amaqabane akho esikolo anemilinganiselo neenjongo ezahlukileyo . ”
Ngoko ke , enye ingenelo yokuya ezintlanganisweni , lithuba lokunxulumana namakholwa esikhonza kunye nawo .
UKumkani uSolomon owayesisilumko wathi : “ Isinyithi silola isinyithi , indoda ilola ubuso bowayo . ”
Maxa wambi , “ ubuso ” bethu bokomoya , oku kuthetha ukuthi ulwazi nokuqonda kwethu kokomoya , lufuna ukulolwa .
Kwanjengokuba ukulola isitshetshe sokoqobo kufuna ubuchule nezixhobo ezifanelekileyo , ngokukwanjalo ufanele unxulumane nabantu abalungileyo , abo banokukwazi ‘ ukukwabela sibabalo sithile sisesomoya . ’ ​ —⁠ Roma 1 :⁠ 11 .
KwiHolo yoBukumkani , uya kubafumana abantu abanjalo , abakubudala obahlukahlukeneyo , iintlanga nezizwe ezahlukahlukeneyo .
Kuyaqondakala ukuba , unokutsaleleka koontanga bakho .
Noko ke , nikela ingqalelo ekhethekileyo , kwabo baye bachitha iminyaka emininzi bekhonza uYehova ngokuthembeka .
Amava abo ebomini kwakunye nolwazi lwabo olunzulu lweBhayibhile anokuba luncedo olukhulu kuwe .
Unokubazi njani abanjalo ?
Zama ukubabuza imibuzo , enjengale , ‘ Wayifumana njani inyaniso ?
Okanye , ‘ Yayinjani inkonzo yasentsimini ngoxa wawuselula ? ’
Banokukwazi kakuhle ukukwabela isibabalo sokomoya !
Kuyinyaniso ukuba , xa uqala ukuthetha nabanye ebandleni , ekuqaleni usenokuvakalelwa njengoCraig oneminyaka eli - 12 ubudala , othi : “ Ndandidla ngokoyika ukuthetha nabantu abakhulileyo .
Ndandicinga ukuba ukuba ndithetha into ephosakeleyo , ndandiya kululekwa . ”

Ngoku uCraig ucacisa esithi : “ Ndikhululekile ukuthetha nabo ngoku . ”
Kutheni ungenzi umzamo ofanayo wokunxulumana nabo bakhulileyo ngokomoya ebandleni ?
